NK019(dza)007:0: 'dus pa mdo'i sgrub khog rin chen 'od kyi snang ba zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK019(dza)007:1: 'dus pa mdo'i sgrub khog bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i
NK019(dza)007:2: don gsal bar byed pa rin chen 'od kyi snang
NK019(dza)007:4: bla ma dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK019(dza)007:5: mchog tu mi 'gyur lhan skyes bde chen nyid //
NK019(dza)007:6: sgrib bral bla med yon tan kun rdzogs pas //
NK019(dza)007:7: rigs brgya'i 'khor lor dbang sgyur rdo rje 'chang //
NK019(dza)007:8: bka' drin mnyam med gter chen bla mar 'dud //
NK019(dza)007:9: gang zhig bsten na mchog thun dngos grub kun //
NK019(dza)007:10: tshe 'di nyid la thob byed 'dus pa mdo'i //
NK019(dza)007:11: bsnyen sgrub yan lag rnam bzhi'i don gsal byed //
NK019(dza)007:12: rin chen 'bar ba'i 'od kyi snang ba spro //
NK019(dza)007:14: gang la dmigs pa'i yul bsgrub bya /
NK019(dza)007:18: lam rkyen dang 'phrad na 'bras bu'i yon tan rnams 'byung rung du nges pas brod pa bskyed de /
NK019(dza)007:19: thob bya'i dngos grub don gnyis phun sum tshogs pa de nyid dmigs yul du byas nas /
NK019(dza)007:20: sgrub byed lam la 'bad pas gzhi'i steng du dri ma sbyong dgos pa'i phyir /
NK019(dza)007:21: dmigs yul ni sbyangs 'bras dngos grub bo //
NK019(dza)007:22: de lta mod kyi bsgrub bya sgrub byed kyi gnad sgrub gzhi nges pa la rag las pas na /
NK019(dza)007:24: chos thams cad kyi gshis lugs sems nyid dkyil 'khor
NK019(dza)007:25: rnam gsum ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gnas pa ste
NK019(dza)007:27: thams cad bdag nyid der gcig pas //
NK019(dza)007:28: ye nas sangs rgyas bde chen nyid //
NK019(dza)007:29: skye 'gag med pa'i snying po yin //
NK019(dza)007:30: bya byed med pa'i dkyil 'khor gsum //
NK019(dza)007:31: ye nas grub zin lhun gyis grub //
NK019(dza)007:33: gnyis pa gang gis sgrub byed thabs la spyi don gsum ste /
NK019(dza)007:34: phun sum tshogs pa lngas sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba /
NK019(dza)007:35: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung bsrang ba dang 'drel bar chu bo bzhi'i dbang bskur ba /
NK019(dza)007:36: rjes don brgyad kyis mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK019(dza)007:38: slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las tho las /
NK019(dza)007:39: dang po phun sum tshogs ldan te //
NK019(dza)007:40: tshad phyin rab 'byams slob dpon gyis //
NK019(dza)007:41: snod dang ldan pa'i 'khor bsdus nas //
NK019(dza)007:42: gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas dag tu //
NK019(dza)007:43: sa chog rdzogs byas gnas khang ldan //
NK019(dza)007:44: dgos pa tshang ba'i yo byad rdzogs //
NK019(dza)007:45: dus cha bzhi yi dang po la //
NK019(dza)007:46: nyi zla gza' skar tshes grangs brtag /
NK019(dza)007:47: ces pa ltar phun sum tshogs pa lnga las /
NK019(dza)007:48: dang po gang gis sgrub cing ston pa'i slob dpon ni /
NK019(dza)007:49: lta dgongs spyod pa rnam par dag pa'i yon tan gyi gter du gyur cing /
NK019(dza)007:50: mkhyen pa zad mi shes pa /
NK019(dza)007:51: khungs kyi dbang lung man ngag rdzogs shing dam tshig dang ldan pa /
NK019(dza)007:52: bshad sgrub rkyen khar mi gtong bas gzhan rjes su
NK019(dza)007:53: 'dzin pa'i thabs mkhas thugs rjer ldan pa sogs gsang
NK019(dza)007:54: sngags kyi las rab 'byams la dbang 'byor bas slob
NK019(dza)007:55: dpon gyi yon tan rnams tshad du phyin pa ste
NK019(dza)007:57: bla ma rdo rje 'khor lo rgyal //
NK019(dza)007:58: yon tan mchog gi gter gyur cing //
NK019(dza)007:59: srid par zhus kyang zad mi shes //
NK019(dza)007:60: rkyen thub dbang lung rdzogs pa bzung //
NK019(dza)007:62: gnyis pa gang dang lhan cig sgrub pa dang nyan pa'i 'khor ni /
NK019(dza)007:63: spyir brtan zhing dul la dad brtson shes rab che
NK019(dza)007:64: ba dam tshig dang sdom pa la yid rton pa'i
NK019(dza)007:65: 'khor dang / bye brag tu slob dpon dang dgongs
NK019(dza)007:66: pa cha 'dra zhing 'chad mkhas pa'i rdo rje rgyal
NK019(dza)007:67: 'khor dang / theb / sbyor ba'i sgyu rtsal shes shing brtse gdung che ba'i gzungs ma /
NK019(dza)007:68: dpa' brtul che ba'i rdo rje king+ka ra /
NK019(dza)007:69: drod 'dzin pa'i rdo rje bya rog /
NK019(dza)007:70: mthong bzlog nus pa'i rdo rje spyan pa /
NK019(dza)007:71: skad snyan zhing phrin las kyi go rim mkhas pa'i las mkhan /
NK019(dza)007:72: g.yos mkhas shing kha ska ba'i rdo rje byan po /
NK019(dza)007:73: phyi nang brda sbyor mkhas pa'i rdul phyag skyes bu
NK019(dza)007:74: la sogs pa tshom bur 'brel ba'i 'khor rnams te
NK019(dza)007:76: rdo rje can gyi gzungs 'dzin ma //
NK019(dza)007:78: las kyi phreng ba rdzogs byed pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:79: zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan no //
NK019(dza)007:80: gsum pa gang du sgrub pa'i gnas ni /
NK019(dza)007:81: yi dwags gdug pa can gyi 'gyu srang dang gcan gzan dgra rkun sogs kyi gnod pa med cing /
NK019(dza)007:82: rgyal bas zhabs kyis bcags pas byin che ba /
NK019(dza)007:83: gong mas grub pa brnyes pas bkra shis pa /
NK019(dza)007:84: gnam sa bar snang gi dpyad legs pas yid du 'ong zhing /
NK019(dza)007:85: khyad par gzhung dang mthun pas sgrub thag nye ba
NK019(dza)007:86: sogs gnas kyi mtshan nyid rnams legs par tshang ba
NK019(dza)007:87: ste / bshad rgyud rngam glog las /
NK019(dza)007:88: ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse rnams dang //
NK019(dza)007:89: tsan+dana nags tshal me tog tshal //
NK019(dza)007:90: yid 'ong bkra shis nyams dga' ba'i //
NK019(dza)007:91: gnas su dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
NK019(dza)007:92: gnam dang sa dang bar snang rnams //
NK019(dza)007:93: legs par brtags te las rnams bya //
NK019(dza)007:95: de lta bu'i bkra shis dge mtshan dang ldan pa'i
NK019(dza)007:96: gnas der sa chog sngon du 'gro bas tshom bu'i
NK019(dza)007:97: grangs dang 'tshams pa'i gnas khang mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK019(dza)007:99: bzhi pa gang la brten nas sgrub pa'i yo byad ni /
NK019(dza)007:101: der ni yo byad phun sum tshogs //
NK019(dza)007:102: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar lha sgrub pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi rten rab gnas can dang /
NK019(dza)007:103: dngos grub sgrub pa'i rdzas thun mong ma yin pa rnams dang /
NK019(dza)007:104: rmad du byung ba'i dam rdzas bam gtsang ma sogs te sgrub rdzas gsang ba'i yo byad /
NK019(dza)007:105: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan dang sman gtor rak+ta sogs phyi
NK019(dza)007:106: nang gi mchod pa rol mo'i bye brag sogs te
NK019(dza)007:107: mchod rdzas dag pa'i yo byad /
NK019(dza)007:108: nad sel ba'i sman dang sman pa /
NK019(dza)007:110: bgegs bzlog gi nyul le bskrad pa'i chas sogs te bar chad rkyen bzlog gi yo byad /
NK019(dza)007:111: bza' btung gos stan sogs 'tsho ba nyer mkho'i yo byad /
NK019(dza)007:112: gzhan las sgrub chos phun sum tshogs pa zhes bshad
NK019(dza)007:113: pa ltar nyams len la the tshom gcod pa'i yo
NK019(dza)007:114: byad spyi dang bye brag gi rgyud lung man ngag
NK019(dza)007:115: rnams te dgos pa mchog gi yo byad rnams kyang
NK019(dza)007:116: 'du bya ba'o // lnga pa gang gi tshe sgrub pa'i dus ni /
NK019(dza)007:118: dpyid dbyar ston dgun te dus bzhir phye ba re
NK019(dza)007:119: re la'ang rab 'bring tha gsum gyi dang po rab
NK019(dza)007:120: bzhi po phrin las bzhi'i dus la dge bar gsungs
NK019(dza)007:121: shing / khyad par sgrub pa 'go rtsom pa'i dus
NK019(dza)007:122: kyang de bzhi bzang bar las tho las bshad pa
NK019(dza)007:123: shing / ltar / bde 'dus dbang byang las kyang /
NK019(dza)007:124: dus ni dbyar dgun ston dpyid kyi //
NK019(dza)007:125: ra ba dag la rab tu shis //
NK019(dza)007:126: brgyad nas nya yi bar la gtad //
NK019(dza)007:127: bkra shis gza' skar shis pa blang //
NK019(dza)007:128: zhes pas dus cha bzhi'i dang po ste ra ba bzhi dang /
NK019(dza)007:129: de'i nang nas kyang nyi ma 'phel ba'i dus byang bgrod /
NK019(dza)007:130: zla ba 'phel ba'i dus yar ngo //
NK019(dza)007:131: de las tshes grangs brgyad nas bco lnga'i bar dge
NK019(dza)007:132: ba la rgyal phur 'dzom pa lta bu'i gza' skar
NK019(dza)007:135: 'di ltar sbyar ba'i dus chen yang //
NK019(dza)007:136: nges par brtags te mdo bzung la //
NK019(dza)007:137: rig byed dag gi yan lag las //
NK019(dza)007:138: shes par bya ste legs sbyar ba //
NK019(dza)007:139: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma dang //
NK019(dza)007:140: 'byor dang dus tshigs bzang po rnams //
NK019(dza)007:141: 'jig rten mtshan ma'i rtog pa ste //
NK019(dza)007:142: brtags na bkra shis mtshan ma 'byung //
NK019(dza)007:144: yang sgrub pa ji tsam byed pa'i dus ni /
NK019(dza)007:145: smin slob kyi dbang du byas na lo'am zla ba
NK019(dza)007:146: drug la sogs pa dngos grub kyi mtshan ma gtan
NK019(dza)007:147: la ma phebs kyi bar de srid du sgrub cing
NK019(dza)007:148: / ma grub na spogs chog dang bcas pas mtha' gcig tu ma nges la /
NK019(dza)007:149: mos slob la ni zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gam /
NK019(dza)007:150: zhag bcu gcig lta bu la bsnyen sgrub bzhi tshang bar nyams su len pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:151: bye brag dbang bskur ba'i dus ni /
NK019(dza)007:152: bsnyen pa rdzogs nas lhag pa'i sems bskyed pa'i dus te /
NK019(dza)007:154: dang po sems bskyed 'dug dus su //
NK019(dza)007:155: rdzas kyi dbang bcu rdzogs par byin //
NK019(dza)007:157: spyi don gnyis pa bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhis gzhung bsrang zhing dbang bskur ba la'ang gnyis te /
NK019(dza)007:158: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gnyis phyed pa'i ched du so so'i tho byang smos pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:159: de gnyis da lta'i dus kyi phyag len ltar gcig tu dril nas sgrub pa'i cho ga bshad pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:161: rgyud lugs mdo rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la brten pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:162: man ngag gi lugs yan lag dang yan lag can
NK019(dza)007:163: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor so sor phye ba mdo yongs
NK019(dza)007:166: rje bla ma dam pas dkyil chog dri med 'od
NK019(dza)007:167: phreng gi mjug tu drang bar mdzad pa'i sgrub byang
NK019(dza)007:168: gi sdams kyis bsdus pa ste /
NK019(dza)007:169: de la bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i /
NK019(dza)007:170: dang po bsnyen pa la'ang gnyis las /
NK019(dza)007:171: sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:172: rtsa rgyud kyi le'u dgu pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:173: spyi'i cho gas zhi khro gnyis kyi bsnyen pa bya ba'o //
NK019(dza)007:174: bya ba las kyi bsnyen pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:175: bshams pa nas gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i bar don
NK019(dza)007:176: bcu gnyis kyis bsdus pa rim pa shoms dang 'brel
NK019(dza)007:177: ba ste / rtsa ba'i sgrub byang las /
NK019(dza)007:178: he ru ka yi sgrub thabs la //
NK019(dza)007:179: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi gsungs pa las //
NK019(dza)007:180: rim pa shoms kyis 'brel ba'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:181: bsnyen pa zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK019(dza)007:183: de la don bcu gnyis te /
NK019(dza)007:187: ro bsal zhing gter bcug la stegs bu rtsig pa'i sgo nas sbyang pa /
NK019(dza)007:188: de'i tshe ngan na sngags rgya ting nge 'dzin nam sbyin sreg gis mtshan ma zil gyis mnan pa /
NK019(dza)007:189: 'khrugs sdebs kyi rim pas der dkyil 'khor bskyed nas
NK019(dza)007:190: gsol gdab bgegs bskrad sogs kyis sa bzung zhing bsrung
NK019(dza)007:191: ba ste nub dang po sa'i cho ga'o //
NK019(dza)007:192: nang par byin gyis brlab pa ni yan lag dang yan lag can gyi lhag gnas so //
NK019(dza)007:193: de nas phyi mtshams rgyal tho dang nang mtshams 'bar ba lta ba'i mtshams sogs bzhi bcad /
NK019(dza)007:194: bar mtshams dam sri mnan pa dang ye shes lha'i sgo byang gdags /
NK019(dza)007:195: bsod nams kyi dpung bskyed phyir skabs 'di dang sgrub
NK019(dza)007:196: pa thog mar 'go 'dzugs pa'i dus su tshogs bsag
NK019(dza)007:197: ci nus bya / dbang bsgyur gyi ting nge 'dzin
NK019(dza)007:198: gyis der gzhal yas khang bskyed pas gnas byin gyis
NK019(dza)007:199: ci nus bya / brlab cing / de dang rjes
NK019(dza)007:200: 'brel du phyag rgya dang tshogs chen 'dus pa'i ting
NK019(dza)007:201: 'dzin gyis 'khor dang yo byad brlab pa rnams so
NK019(dza)007:202: ci nus bya / brlab cing / // gnyis pa nye bsnyen ni /
NK019(dza)007:203: thig tshon gyis bri ba nas mchod pa byin rlabs kyi bar don bcu bdun gyis bsdus pa ste /
NK019(dza)007:206: gsang sgor zhugs nas byin ldan phyir //
NK019(dza)007:207: nye ba'i bsnyen par de brjod do //
NK019(dza)007:209: de la don bcu bdun te /
NK019(dza)007:210: dmigs rten gyi dkyil 'khor thig tshon gyis bris la /
NK019(dza)007:211: phyir cha gsum gtor ma btang /
NK019(dza)007:213: nang du dkyil 'khor dang rdzas rnams sbyang zhing /
NK019(dza)007:214: bskyed pas byin gyis brlabs te /
NK019(dza)007:215: rnam pa dang rgyan rdzas rnams dgod //
NK019(dza)007:216: de nas 'khrugs sdebs kyi rim pas dkyil 'khor byin dbab /
NK019(dza)007:217: gleng gzhi bshad pa spro ba bskyed nas /
NK019(dza)007:218: bsnyen par gnang ba'i dbang bskur /
NK019(dza)007:219: brda sgo phye sde brda phyag btsal la /
NK019(dza)007:226: mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa rnams so //
NK019(dza)007:228: sgrub gzhung bsrang ba sogs don bcus smin slob la
NK019(dza)007:229: dngos grub kyi mtshan ma gtan la ma phebs kyi
NK019(dza)007:230: bar dang / mos slob la dus ji ltar rigs kyi bar du sgrub pa ste /
NK019(dza)007:232: rdo rje rigs kyi sgrub pa la //
NK019(dza)007:233: gang yang bar chad mi g.yeng phyir //
NK019(dza)007:234: dam pa'i gzhung nyid 'dzin pas na //
NK019(dza)007:235: sgrub pa zhes byar de brjod do //
NK019(dza)007:238: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor thun mong dang thun min gang
NK019(dza)007:239: byed skabs babs kyis dus drug tu zhi khro'i gzhung
NK019(dza)007:240: bsrang / gsal ba gsum gyi dzapa bya /
NK019(dza)007:242: gtor ma gsar rnying mtshams sbyar la lhag ma btang /
NK019(dza)007:243: las gang la dmigs pa de'ang spyi tsam du rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg bya /
NK019(dza)007:244: bskang bshags kyis bzod par gsol /
NK019(dza)007:245: 'dug pa'i tshe rang gi stan byin gyis rlob cing 'gro na phreng bas bsrung du gzhug /
NK019(dza)007:246: gnas kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis ta na sgrol ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:247: ga na sbyor ba byin gyis brlab cing skabs dang sbyar te mchod /
NK019(dza)007:248: dus drug tu nyul le bzlog pa rnams so //
NK019(dza)007:250: rtags nas gnas bsrung ba'i bar don bcu gcig gis
NK019(dza)007:251: bsdus pa nub tha ma dngos grub len cing dbang
NK019(dza)007:254: khrag 'thung las kyi rim pa las //
NK019(dza)007:256: don mchog mngon du bya ba'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:257: sgrub pa chen po zhes su brjod //
NK019(dza)007:259: de la don bcu gcig ste /
NK019(dza)007:260: grub pa'i rtags mtshan gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:261: nub tha ma dngos grub kyi rdzas bsham /
NK019(dza)007:263: rang don du dngos grub blang zhing /
NK019(dza)007:264: gzhan don slob ma la rgyud lugs kyi dbang chu
NK019(dza)007:265: bo bzhis bsdus pa'i sum cu rtsa drug skal ba
NK019(dza)007:269: gtor ma cha gsum du bgos la zhi ba'i sregs blugs dang phyi rol du gtor skyong bya /
NK019(dza)007:271: mtshams dgrol ba sogs dkyil 'khor bsdu ba'i rim pa rnams byas te /
NK019(dza)007:272: zhag gcig gnas bsrung ba rnams so //
NK019(dza)007:273: gnyis pa man ngag gi lugs yan lag dang yan
NK019(dza)007:274: lag can rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor so sor phye ba
NK019(dza)007:275: mdo yongs rdzogs la brten pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:276: slob dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las tho'i dgongs pa ste /
NK019(dza)007:277: smin mos kyi khyad par ni /
NK019(dza)007:278: 'dir nye bsnyen dang sgrub pa gnyis la zhag bdun
NK019(dza)007:279: phrag re'i zhal gsal yod pas mos slob gtso che
NK019(dza)007:280: zhing / de gnyis zhag grangs mnyam par mdzad pa sgyu 'phrul ba'i lugs dang 'dra na'ang /
NK019(dza)007:281: 'dir de dang de rgyud dang lung gi dkyil 'khor
NK019(dza)007:282: so so ba yin pa'i phyir khyad che bas ma
NK019(dza)007:283: 'dres par bya'o // de la thog mar rdo rje
NK019(dza)007:284: slob dpon gzhi'i bsnyen pa kha skongs dang bcas pa
NK019(dza)007:286: slob ma bzung zhing rang gi bsnyen pa kha gsos nas /
NK019(dza)007:288: de la bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi las /
NK019(dza)007:289: dang po bsnyen pa'i yan lag phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo bskur ba'i rim pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:297: bsrung ba rnams dkyil chog ltar las /
NK019(dza)007:298: dkyil 'khor khang pa gsar rnying gi khyad kyi 'dor len shes par byas rjes /
NK019(dza)007:299: dang po phyi dbang rgyud chu bo //
NK019(dza)007:300: mtshan nyid sde gsum lugs dag tu //
NK019(dza)007:303: ces pa'i bar gsungs pa ltar bsod nams kyi dpung
NK019(dza)007:304: bskyed pa'i phyir nye'u 'don pa nas dpang skong gi
NK019(dza)007:308: cha gsum dang ma mo gling bzhi'i mdos kyi dkyil 'khor bsham mchod kyis thugs dam bskang /
NK019(dza)007:309: phyag rdor ngan song gnas 'dren gyi dkyil 'khor du
NK019(dza)007:310: spyi dbang chen po'i gleng gzhi dang 'brel bar mchog
NK019(dza)007:311: dbang bcu drug gis rgyud sbyangs te snod rung du
NK019(dza)007:312: bsgrubs pas sgo dbye ba rnams ni nub dang po'i
NK019(dza)007:313: bya ba'o // de nas nub gnyis pa nas bzung
NK019(dza)007:314: phyi dbang rnams kyi zhag grangs rgyas bsdus skabs dang
NK019(dza)007:315: bya ba'o // sbyar te / phyi dbang gi dkyil 'khor drug las /
NK019(dza)007:319: byang sems bzhi ni sngar drangs pa'i /
NK019(dza)007:321: ces pa bar gyi gsal byed yin pas 'dir yang sbyar te /
NK019(dza)007:322: de bzhi'i dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub song ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:323: las dang po pa rnams rang rang gi nges par
NK019(dza)007:324: 'byung ba'i tshul bzhis so so'i sdom pa phog pas
NK019(dza)007:326: kri yog gnyis la rang rang gi sta gon sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)007:327: kri ya rtsa ba'i lha rigs gsum nyi shu rtsa gcig gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK019(dza)007:328: yo ga la rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor so
NK019(dza)007:329: so'i lugs ltar bzhengs sgrub der 'jug pa rnams byas
NK019(dza)007:330: rjes / phyi dbang rtsa ba bcu la yan lag
NK019(dza)007:331: rags pa brgya rtsa brgyad du phye nas so so'i
NK019(dza)007:332: dbang 'dor len gyi gnad kyis bskur bar bya ba
NK019(dza)007:333: rjes / yin no // gnyis pa nye bsnyen gyi
NK019(dza)007:334: yan lag nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bskur ba'i
NK019(dza)007:335: rjes / yin no // rim pa ni / dpang skong bklag /
NK019(dza)007:336: zhi gzhung bsrangs la tshogs dang sbyin sreg dbul /
NK019(dza)007:337: yan lag dang yan lag can gyi rab gnas rnams bya /
NK019(dza)007:338: sang nangs par cha gsum dang gser skyems btang /
NK019(dza)007:339: rgyal chen dang phyogs skyong gi thos phyi mtshams /
NK019(dza)007:340: khro bcu'i mtshams dang dam sri mnan pas bar mtshams /
NK019(dza)007:341: lta ba'i mtshams sogs bzhis nang mtshams bcad /
NK019(dza)007:342: ting 'dzin gsum gyis gnas 'khor yo byad brlab /
NK019(dza)007:343: stegs bu la go ma ye btang /
NK019(dza)007:344: gzungs ma brlabs te thig gdab pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:345: tshon bkye bas tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dren pa'i las byang che le ltar bris la /
NK019(dza)007:346: phyag rgya'i rnam pa dang mchod rdzas sgrub rdzas sogs rgyan bkod byas nas /
NK019(dza)007:347: dus drug tu zhi khro'i las gzhung bsrang zhing /
NK019(dza)007:350: tshul des zhag bdun rdzogs pa'i tha ma la slob
NK019(dza)007:351: dpon bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du rig pas zhugs rjes
NK019(dza)007:353: nang dbang rtsa ba bcu gcig la yan lag drug brgya dang drug tu phye nas bskur ro //
NK019(dza)007:354: gsum pa sgrub pa'i yan lag sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bskur ba'i rim pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:355: phyi nang bar gsum gyi mtshams sngar ltar bcad /
NK019(dza)007:356: khyad par bar mtshams la gshin rje gshed kyi sgo byang gdags /
NK019(dza)007:358: stegs bur go ma ye btang /
NK019(dza)007:359: thig g.yog brlabs te rang bzhin ting 'dzin gyi gnam thig dang /
NK019(dza)007:360: gzugs brnyan las kyi sa thig gdab cing /
NK019(dza)007:361: tshon bkye bas rtsa rgyud kyi tshogs chen 'dus pa'i sgrub lugs kyi le'u ltar /
NK019(dza)007:362: dkyil 'khor dur khrod gsang ba'i lugs su bzhengs pa la /
NK019(dza)007:363: phyag rgya'i rnam pa sgrub rten mar me /
NK019(dza)007:364: mchod rdzas dang dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan rnams dgod /
NK019(dza)007:365: de nas brda sgo phye la /
NK019(dza)007:373: bskang bshags te las kyi phreng ba rdzogs par byas la /
NK019(dza)007:374: dkyil 'khor bskyed drangs mchod bzlas te las rnam bzhis bsnyen sgrub kyi gzhung bsrang /
NK019(dza)007:375: lha'i rkang 'don du stong tshigs kyis mchod cing bstod /
NK019(dza)007:378: nyul le bzlog pa rnams dus drug tu bya /
NK019(dza)007:379: tshul des zhag bdun rdzogs pa'i tha ma la /
NK019(dza)007:380: slob dpon bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs te /
NK019(dza)007:381: lha dang rdzas las dngos grub blangs rjes /
NK019(dza)007:382: slob bu dkyil 'khor du bcug ste /
NK019(dza)007:383: sgrub dbang rtsa ba bcu gsum la yan lag brgya dang bco lngar phye nas bskur ro //
NK019(dza)007:384: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po'i yan lag gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo bskur ba'i rim pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:385: 'di dngos grub chen po yum gyi mkha' las blang ba nyid yin pas sgrub chen te /
NK019(dza)007:386: de la brda'i dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub byas la /
NK019(dza)007:387: kun rdzob dang don dam byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor du bcug nas /
NK019(dza)007:388: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo rnam pa gnyis bskur ba yin no //
NK019(dza)007:389: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs gnyis so so'i tho byang mdo tsam bshad zin to //
NK019(dza)007:393: zla nyi rlung sems 'gyur ba'i sgrib pa bzhi //
NK019(dza)007:394: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhis gtan med bcom las slar //
NK019(dza)007:395: dri bral rdo rje bzhi yi rgyal thabs la //
NK019(dza)007:396: dbang bsgyur sku bzhi'i bdag nyid bla mar 'dud //
NK019(dza)007:397: rgyud lung man ngag lugs gnyis gcig dril gyis //
NK019(dza)007:398: chu bo bzhi'i dbang bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi yi //
NK019(dza)007:399: chos kyi sgroms su bcug nas bskur ba'i chings //
NK019(dza)007:400: nyung gsal rdzogs pa'i dpal 'di de ring byin //
NK019(dza)007:401: da ni gnyis pa rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs
NK019(dza)007:402: gnyis da lta'i dus kyi phyag len ltar gcig tu
NK019(dza)007:403: dril nas sgrub pa'i cho ga la /
NK019(dza)007:405: rdo rje tshogs te bsnyen pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:406: nye ba dang ni sgrub pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:407: sgrub pa chen por sbyar bar bya //
NK019(dza)007:409: dang po bsnyen pa'i yan lag la gsum ste /
NK019(dza)007:410: slob dpon gyis sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa /
NK019(dza)007:411: slob ma bzung zhing rang gi bsnyen pa kha gso ba /
NK019(dza)007:412: bsnyen pa'i yan lag dngos so //
NK019(dza)007:413: dang po la'ang smin mos gnyis las /
NK019(dza)007:414: tshogs sgrub mtshan nyid pa'i sngon du bya ba'i bsnyen pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:416: lta ba dbyings ye shes gnyis med du rtogs pas /
NK019(dza)007:417: don dang yi ge'i rjes su 'jug pa'i ting nge
NK019(dza)007:418: 'dzin rim gyis sam gcig char gang rung gi sgo
NK019(dza)007:419: nas brtan pa thob par byed pa ste /
NK019(dza)007:420: mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa la'ang gsum gyi rab yin no //
NK019(dza)007:421: gal te ting nge 'dzin spyi'i rnam pa lam du
NK019(dza)007:422: byed pa'i tshogs sgrub mos sgom la brten pa dang
NK019(dza)007:423: dbang bskur ba tsam gyi ched du bya ba'i bsnyen
NK019(dza)007:424: pa ni / mos slob kyis kyang rung ste /
NK019(dza)007:425: dben pa'i gnas su mtshams ba cad la /
NK019(dza)007:426: rang gzhi lus kun bzang dang che mchog la /
NK019(dza)007:427: zhi khro lus dkyil du bkod pa a nu rang
NK019(dza)007:428: gzhung gi sgrub lugs ltar nyams su blangs pas mtshan
NK019(dza)007:430: tha na'ang dus dang grangs kyi bsnyen pa gang rung
NK019(dza)007:431: kha skongs kyi sbyin sreg dang bcas pa bya ba'o
NK019(dza)007:433: de ltar rtsa bsnyen thems pa'i bla ma la /
NK019(dza)007:434: dad gus dang ldan pa'i slob mas gsol ba lan gsum du btab cing /
NK019(dza)007:435: rus kyang 'dod don dri ba sogs kyis mtshan nyid legs par brtags te /
NK019(dza)007:436: snod rung du mthong na gnang ba byin la /
NK019(dza)007:437: ting nge 'dzin gyis bu'i bgegs sbyang zhing bsrung ba byas te /
NK019(dza)007:438: rgyud sbyang ba'i man ngag bstan nas slob dpon bdag
NK019(dza)007:439: nyid lha la gnang ba zhu ba'i don du bsnyen
NK019(dza)007:441: de'i tshe 'grub na mdo rtsa ba'i rnam bum sta gon bzhin du 'du byas la /
NK019(dza)007:442: thun mjug rnams su bum pa'i bskyed bzlas kyang ci nus bya /
NK019(dza)007:443: de'i bar du bus kyang lus srog gi bar chad
NK019(dza)007:444: du 'gro ba'i gnas rnams su 'gro 'dug sogs spangs
NK019(dza)007:446: sgrub mchod dang dbang gi yo byad sogs 'dir dgos pa'i cha rkyen thams cad tshogs par bsag go //
NK019(dza)007:450: bye brag yan lag dang yan lag can rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i bsnyen pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:452: dkyil 'khor khang pa gsar pa'i phyogs la ras bris
NK019(dza)007:453: dang rdul tshon gang la brten kyang rung sa'i cho
NK019(dza)007:455: 'di la phyag len phal che bar /
NK019(dza)007:456: sa sbyang ba yan chad las mi mdzad pa'i srol snang na'ang /
NK019(dza)007:457: rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs kyi las tho gnyis ka las de 'dra'i dmigs 'byed ma gsungs pas /
NK019(dza)007:458: dkyil chog ltar sa'i cho ga tshang bar bya ba la legs shing /
NK019(dza)007:459: gal te dkyil 'khor khang pa rnying pa lta bu yin kyang /
NK019(dza)007:460: las dang bya ba'i sgo nas brtag sbyang ma gtogs
NK019(dza)007:461: lhag ma rnams phyag bzhes mi nub pa'i ched du
NK019(dza)007:462: mdzad pa'i lugs kyang snang ste /
NK019(dza)007:466: phyi nang gi thugs dam skong ba /
NK019(dza)007:467: tshogs las kyis nyams chag skong ba /
NK019(dza)007:468: ma 'dres pa bsre zhing 'dres pa bsnan pa /
NK019(dza)007:469: zab mo'i chos bshad dang 'brel bar sgo 'byed kyi dbang bskur ba'o //
NK019(dza)007:471: sgrub pa la 'jug pa'i gong nas kyang /
NK019(dza)007:476: sman dang bza' btung sbyin gtong /
NK019(dza)007:479: ri rgya klungs rgya bsdam pa /
NK019(dza)007:481: lam 'phrang bsal ba sogs gnas de nyid dam gzhan du'ang rung ste /
NK019(dza)007:482: rang ngam grogs la bcol nas rgyab rim ci 'grub sngon du gtong zhing /
NK019(dza)007:483: khyad par gnas de nyid du slob ma 'dus pa rnams kyis /
NK019(dza)007:488: lang+kara gshegs pa ste 'bum sde lnga'am /
NK019(dza)007:497: khrus dang gtsang sbra sngon du 'gro bas yi dam
NK019(dza)007:498: gyi sngags bzla bzhin du s+aats+tsha gdab pa sogs ci
NK019(dza)007:500: rgyud 'byongs shing bar chad mi 'byung ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK019(dza)007:503: spyir mgron rnam pa bzhi la sgrub thabs ltar cha gsum gyi cho gas thugs dam bskang /
NK019(dza)007:504: khyad par dkon mchog mchod cing gsol ba gdab /
NK019(dza)007:505: srung ma thugs dam can spyi sgos thams cad la mchod gtor phul nas sgrub pa'i stongs grogs zhu /
NK019(dza)007:506: 'jig rten gyi lha 'dre thams cad la phud gtor btang la bar chad mi byed par bka' bsgo /
NK019(dza)007:507: bye brag gnyug mar gnas pa'i gzhi bdag la gser
NK019(dza)007:508: skyems dang gtor ma byin nas stongs grogs bcol lo
NK019(dza)007:510: ma mo bzhi bskang ba ste /
NK019(dza)007:511: de la phyi ma mthun sprul pa'i ma mo bskang ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:513: ma grub na ma mo rin chen phra bkod las
NK019(dza)007:514: phyungs pa gling gi bkod pa lta bu'i mdos bzhengs
NK019(dza)007:515: nas gzhung bzhin mchod la bar chad srungs shig par
NK019(dza)007:516: thugs dam bskul / nang ting nge 'dzin gyi ma
NK019(dza)007:517: mo yig 'bru'i sgo nas bskyed cing spyan drangs bstim
NK019(dza)007:518: la mchod bstod 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba gdab
NK019(dza)007:519: thugs dam bskul / / gsang ba thig le'i ma mo /
NK019(dza)007:520: tsan+da l+ai'i man ngag gis rtsa rlung gcun /
NK019(dza)007:521: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi ma mo mkha' klong gnyis med du la bzla bar bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:523: man+dala la nyi zla byang sems kyis chag chag btab
NK019(dza)007:524: pa'i steng du yi dam gyi sku bzhugs su gsol
NK019(dza)007:525: ba'am yang na tshom bu lnga bkod /
NK019(dza)007:526: de'i mdun du dam rdzas su 'os pa'i yo byad bshams la /
NK019(dza)007:527: las mkhan gyis zhi khro'i las gzhung srong ba'am ma grub na /
NK019(dza)007:528: stong pa'i ngang las srung 'khor gyi dbus su bskyed
NK019(dza)007:529: sngags brjod pas rdo rje gzhon nu'am zhe sdang rdo
NK019(dza)007:530: rje lta bu gnyug ma'i lha phyag rgya gcig pa'i
NK019(dza)007:531: skur langs la / cha gsum gyi dri chab kyis bsangs te /
NK019(dza)007:532: las gzhung ltar tshogs byin gyis rlob cing /
NK019(dza)007:533: tshogs zhing rnams spyan drangs pa man+dala la bzhugs su gsol te /
NK019(dza)007:536: tha mas stob pa bya zhing /
NK019(dza)007:537: de dang sbrel nas dam sri'i ling+ga bcas pa la dgug bstim byas te phur bus gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:539: dang po ma 'dres pa rnams bsre ba'i cho ga ni /
NK019(dza)007:540: gsar bu rnams snod rung du bya ba'i phyir /
NK019(dza)007:541: rdo rje slob dpon sangs rgyas dpal //
NK019(dza)007:542: zhes sogs rgyun bshags lan gsum byed du bcug la /
NK019(dza)007:544: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta badz+ra yak+sha kro d+ha ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:545: ces pas bdud rtsi byin gyis brlabs la /
NK019(dza)007:547: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK019(dza)007:548: byang chub sems dang rdo rje 'dzin //
NK019(dza)007:549: de bzhin sgrub po rnal 'byor pa //
NK019(dza)007:550: de dag la ni snying ring na //
NK019(dza)007:551: rdo rje yak+sha gnod sbyin gyis //
NK019(dza)007:552: khyod kyi snying la bzhos te 'thung //
NK019(dza)007:553: snying la yang dag gnas pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:554: 'di ni sems can dmyal ba'i chu //
NK019(dza)007:555: dam tshig nyams pa sreg par byed //
NK019(dza)007:556: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK019(dza)007:559: bdud rtsi h+aum yig rer gyur nas so so'i snying
NK019(dza)007:560: dkyil du thim pas shes pa h+aum du gyur pas
NK019(dza)007:561: mos la / +aahh+aum zhes rdo rjes bdud rtsi thigs pa gsum lce la bzhag /
NK019(dza)007:563: badz+ra sa ma ya i dan+te na ra kan /
NK019(dza)007:565: gnyis pa 'dres zin bsnan pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:566: mched gsar rnying thams cad kyi lce la bdud rtsi bzhag cing gnas gsum du thig le byas la /
NK019(dza)007:567: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swab+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK019(dza)007:568: de bzhin du w+aa ka dang tsit+ta la'ang sbyar /
NK019(dza)007:569: de nas dam tshig bsrung thabs kyang mdo tsam bshad nas /
NK019(dza)007:570: deng phyin chad mched gsar rnying skal ba mnyam par gyur pa yin no //
NK019(dza)007:571: zhes brda sprad la gral basre'o //
NK019(dza)007:573: sgrub thabs ltar phyag rdor ngan song gnas 'dren gyi dkyil 'khor bsham sgrub sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)007:574: dbang chog ltar zab mo'i chos dang gleng gzhi bshad nas sgo 'byed kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK019(dza)007:575: de rjes dpon slob thams cad tshogs la rol zhing lhag gtor btang /
NK019(dza)007:576: yo byad ma tshogs pa kun de'i nyin mo 'dzom par bsag go //
NK019(dza)007:577: de yan chad nub dang po'i cho ga ste /
NK019(dza)007:578: spyi'i sngon 'gros gzhi bzung ba tshar ro //
NK019(dza)007:579: gsum pa yan lag dang yan lag can rtsa ba'i
NK019(dza)007:580: dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i bsnyen pa la gnyis las
NK019(dza)007:581: / dang po yan lag gi dkyil 'khor la brten pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:582: man ngag gi lugs kyi phyi dbang drug bskur ba'i bya ba ste /
NK019(dza)007:583: de la lha rje sh+aaka mgon phyi dbang rnams la'ang
NK019(dza)007:584: zhag re re mdzad par grags pa mdo dbang rgyas
NK019(dza)007:585: pa zhag nyer gcig pa'i lugs yin la /
NK019(dza)007:586: 'dir 'bring po zhag bcu gcig pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK019(dza)007:587: lha rje 'gar dang glan chen po rdo rje 'od kyi phyag bzhes 'gos kyi las tho ltar /
NK019(dza)007:588: nub gnyis pa la lha mi /
NK019(dza)007:592: sngon 'gro tshar ba'i nub mo las mkhan gyis stegs
NK019(dza)007:593: bu dri dang ba byung gis chag chag btab pa
NK019(dza)007:594: de thig gis gling bzhir bcad nas /
NK019(dza)007:598: byang shar du byang sems kyi dkyil 'khor bsham zhing /
NK019(dza)007:599: sang nyin sgrub mchod so so dang /
NK019(dza)007:600: gtor chog gcig tu bsdu zhing /
NK019(dza)007:601: dbang bzhi po rim par bskur /
NK019(dza)007:602: de nub kri ya'i sta gon byas nas /
NK019(dza)007:603: nyin gsum pa la dkyil 'khor bzhengs sgrub 'jug pa dbang bskur rnams bya /
NK019(dza)007:604: de tshar ba dang yo ga'i sta gon byas te /
NK019(dza)007:605: nyin bzhi pa la dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod dang /
NK019(dza)007:606: der slob ma bcug nas dbang bskur bya ba rnams te /
NK019(dza)007:607: de dag gi cho ga'i las rim ni sgrub thabs
NK019(dza)007:608: dngos grub 'dod 'jo dang dbang chog las shes par
NK019(dza)007:609: bya zhing / sngon 'gro'i dus gyi tshogs las kyi nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor ma bsdus par bzhag nas /
NK019(dza)007:610: de bar nub re bzhin las mkhan gyis zhi khro'i
NK019(dza)007:611: gzhung bsrangs te tshogs mchod dang lhag ma gtong zhing
NK019(dza)007:612: / srung ma'i gtong chog re yang mdzad do //
NK019(dza)007:613: man ngag gi lugs kyi bsnyen pa'i yan lag phyi dbang bskur ba'i rim pa tshar ro //
NK019(dza)007:614: gnyis pa yan lag can rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor la brten pa'i bsnyen pa'i yan lag ni /
NK019(dza)007:615: sa'i cho ga gong du song bas /
NK019(dza)007:616: 'dir nub lnga pa'i chog khrigs la /
NK019(dza)007:621: spro na zhi ba'i sbyin sreg kyang bya /
NK019(dza)007:626: thod chu ste yan lag gi rab gnas dang /
NK019(dza)007:627: yan lag can la stegs bur go ma ye btang
NK019(dza)007:628: ste gnam sa'i thig btab nas lha sta gon dang
NK019(dza)007:629: / rnam bum bshams nas bum pa sta gon byas la bcas rnams bsgrigs te /
NK019(dza)007:630: dbang chog ltar slob ma sta gon byas rjes /
NK019(dza)007:632: gtor ma btang nas rnal 'byor dang ldan pas nyal /
NK019(dza)007:633: rmi lam ngan na nang par bzlog pa'i cho ga bya ba rnams so //
NK019(dza)007:634: nub drug pa'i chog khrigs la /
NK019(dza)007:635: snga dro rmi lam ngan bzlog gi zhi drag gang rung gi sbyin sreg byed dgos na /
NK019(dza)007:636: bdag bskyed des go chu rug tu 'gro mod /
NK019(dza)007:637: de mi dgos na nang par snga bar langs la /
NK019(dza)007:638: bdag bskyed rgyas bsdus ci rigs gsal btab ste /
NK019(dza)007:639: dkyil chog ltar sta gon gyi lha btegs nas /
NK019(dza)007:641: dang por slob dpon gyis cung zad bris rjes /
NK019(dza)007:642: slob ma gzhan dag kyang 'brir bcug la /
NK019(dza)007:643: phyi dro las mkhan gyis cha gsum gyi gtor chog byas la /
NK019(dza)007:644: cha gsum pa phyir gtor ba dang mnyam du drag sngags bzla zhing thun gyis brab /
NK019(dza)007:645: lce bog nag po'i dud pas bdug /
NK019(dza)007:646: rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pa'i tsham rngams bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:647: de nas mtshams bcad pa la gsum las /
NK019(dza)007:649: sgrub khang nas phyi rol gom pa bdun cu gzhal
NK019(dza)007:650: ba'i phyogs bzhir dri'i man+dala pad 'dab brgyad pa re'i
NK019(dza)007:651: steng du las dang mthun pa'i dbyibs mdog can gyi
NK019(dza)007:653: rgyal chen so so'i sku rab gnas can rgyal mtshan dang bcas pa btsugs /
NK019(dza)007:654: so so'i mdun du mchod pa lnga dang /
NK019(dza)007:655: gtor ma shar du dris brgyan pa'i dkar zlum /
NK019(dza)007:656: lhor nya dang sha khrag gis brgyan pa'i gru gsum nag po /
NK019(dza)007:657: nub tu 'o ma dang me tog gis brgyan pa'i zla gam dmar po /
NK019(dza)007:658: byang du shing thog dang dar sna rat+na sogs kyis brgyan pa'i gru bzhi ser po rnams bsham zhing /
NK019(dza)007:660: cha dang po ltar mchod pa 'bru gsum dang gtor ma brtag pa bzhis byin gyis brlab /
NK019(dza)007:662: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum zhes brjod pas tho pho
NK019(dza)007:663: brang du gyur pa'i nang du d+h+ri ta r+aash+t+aa ya
NK019(dza)007:664: s+w+aa h+aa / zhes brjod pas shar du rgyal po
NK019(dza)007:665: chen po yul 'khor srung sku mdog dkar po zhi
NK019(dza)007:666: zhing brjid pa'i chas can pi wang bsnams pa 'khor
NK019(dza)007:668: rang gi snying ga nas 'od zer 'phros pas ri
NK019(dza)007:669: rab kyi shar phyogs nas rgyal po chen po yul
NK019(dza)007:670: 'khor srung 'khor bcas badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs spyan drangs
NK019(dza)007:672: d+h+ri ta r+aash+t+aa sa pa ri w+aa ra push+pe nas /

NK019(dza)007:675: btags pas gtor ma phul bas mnyes nas ci bcol
NK019(dza)007:677: ri rab gling bzhi'i shar phyogs nas //
NK019(dza)007:678: rdo rje gsang bdag dbang gi mthus //
NK019(dza)007:679: 'jig rten skyong ba'i tha tshig can //
NK019(dza)007:680: mthu chen mgon po yul 'khor srung //
NK019(dza)007:681: shar phyogs bgegs rigs 'dul la mkhas //
NK019(dza)007:682: chos skyong longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK019(dza)007:683: zhi ba'i phrin las mthar phyin pas //
NK019(dza)007:684: rigs kyi kha dog dkar zhing gsal //
NK019(dza)007:685: rang rtags lha yi pi wang thogs //

NK019(dza)007:688: rang gi 'khor rnams thub par mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:690: d+h+ri ta r+aash+t+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK019(dza)007:691: zhes bzla zhing tish+tha badz+ra zhes brtan bzhugs bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:692: phyogs gzhan gsum yang des rigs 'gre ba las /
NK019(dza)007:694: bi r+au d+ha ka ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK019(dza)007:695: zhes brjod pas lhor rgyal po chen po 'phags skyes
NK019(dza)007:696: po sku mdog sngon po cung zad khro nyams brjid
NK019(dza)007:697: pa'i chas can ral gri bsnams pa ri rab kyi
NK019(dza)007:698: lho phyogs nas rgyal po chen po 'phags skyes po

NK019(dza)007:702: ri rab gling bzhi'i lho phyogs nas //

NK019(dza)007:730: byang du rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras sku
NK019(dza)007:731: mdog ser po bzhad cing brjid pa'i chas can be
NK019(dza)007:732: con dang ne'u le bsnams pa 'khor dang rang gi
NK019(dza)007:733: snying ga nas 'od zer 'phros pas ri rab kyi
NK019(dza)007:734: byang phyogs nas rgyal po chen po rnam thos sras

NK019(dza)007:746: phrin bcol ba'i rtsa rgyud du /
NK019(dza)007:747: ri rab gling bzhi phyogs phyogs nas //
NK019(dza)007:748: zhes sogs bzhi ka sdebs su gsungs kyang 'dir sgos chos sgyur nas kha phral ba yin no //
NK019(dza)007:749: yang phyogs skyong tho sdom rtsa rgyud du ma gsung kyang /
NK019(dza)007:750: bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las thor bshad pa ltar /
NK019(dza)007:753: steng shar stod dang 'og nub smad du tho brtsegs par so so'i sku'am sngags byang btsugs /
NK019(dza)007:754: mdun du mchod pa lnga dang /
NK019(dza)007:755: gtor ma re bshams pa'i byin gyis rlobs /
NK019(dza)007:756: stong pa'i ngang las tho pho brang du gsal ba'i nang du in+d+r+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK019(dza)007:757: zhes pas shar du dbang po bskyed /
NK019(dza)007:758: in+d+r+aa ya h+aum dzahs spyan drangs /
NK019(dza)007:759: dzah h+aum bam hoh sa bstim /
NK019(dza)007:760: in+d+r+aa ya sa pa ri w+aa ra push+pe nas shap+da'i bar dang /
NK019(dza)007:761: rang sngags la nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags btags pas gtor ma phul /
NK019(dza)007:762: dbang po rdo rje sogs sh+lo ka gcig gi mthar /
NK019(dza)007:763: 'khor dang bcas pa ma lus kun //
NK019(dza)007:765: bdag cag rnal 'byor rtsal sbyong gis //
NK019(dza)007:766: rang gi 'khor rnams thub par mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:768: tish+tha badz+ra zhes brtan bzhugs bya /
NK019(dza)007:769: de bzhin du phyogs gzhan rnams rigs 'gre ba las /
NK019(dza)007:771: stong pa'i ngang las ag+ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK019(dza)007:773: ag+na ye h+aum dzahs spyan drangs /
NK019(dza)007:775: ag+na ye sa pa ri w+aa ra push+pe sogs kyis mchod cing gtor ma phul /
NK019(dza)007:776: me ste bsreg bya sogs kyi mthar /

NK019(dza)007:778: rnal 'byor rang gi 'khor rnams ag+na ye s+w+aa h+aa
NK019(dza)007:781: stong pa'i ngang las ya m+aa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK019(dza)007:783: ya m+aa ya h+aum dzahs drangs /
NK019(dza)007:785: ya m+aa ya sa pa ri w+aa ra push+pe sogs kyis mchod cing gtor ma phul /
NK019(dza)007:786: gshin rje be con sogs kyi mthar /
NK019(dza)007:787: 'khor dang bcas pa phyi 'khor skyong ba'i bdag cag
NK019(dza)007:788: rnal 'byor rang gi 'khor rnams ya m+aa ya s+w+aa

NK019(dza)007:793: nee tri t+ya ya h+aum dzahs drangs /
NK019(dza)007:795: nee tri t+ya ya sa ri w+aa ra push+pe sogs kyis mchod cing gtor ma phul /

NK019(dza)007:798: rnal 'byor rang gi 'khor rnams nee tri t+ya ya

NK019(dza)007:837: stong pa'i brah+ma na s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK019(dza)007:839: brah+ma na s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra ya h+aum dzahs drangs /

NK019(dza)007:843: 'khor dang phyi 'khor bdag cag rang gi brah+ma na s+aur+ya tsan+d+ra ya s+w+aa h+aa /
