NK019(dza)007:850: pri thi w+ai b+h+yahn+aa ge b+h+yaha su re b+h+yahs pa
NK019(dza)007:851: ri w+aa ra push+pe sogs kyis mchod cing gtor ma
NK019(dza)007:852: phul / 'og gi klu ste sogs kyi mthar /
NK019(dza)007:853: 'khor dang phyi 'khor bdag cag rang gi pri thi w+ai b+h+yahn+aa ge b+h+yaha su re b+h+yahs+w+aa h+aa /
NK019(dza)007:854: tish+tha badz+ra zhes brtan bzhugs bya /
NK019(dza)007:855: 'dir phyogs skyong gi sogs khung rnams blo rmongs 'jug
NK019(dza)007:856: bde ba'i phyir dkyus su gsal bar byas pa yin
NK019(dza)007:858: de ltar rgyal po chen po bzhi dang phyogs skyong
NK019(dza)007:859: ba bcu rang rang gi dpung dang bcas pas khor
NK019(dza)007:860: yug thams cad bar mtshams med par gtams te cis
NK019(dza)007:861: kyang mi shigs pa'i rgyal thabs kyi gur phub par
NK019(dza)007:862: bsam mo // gnyis pa bar mtshams la gsum las /
NK019(dza)007:863: dang po khro bo bcus mtshams bcas pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:864: sa bsrung ba dang 'brel bar khro bcu'i phur bu btab na /
NK019(dza)007:866: phur bu rnams gu gul gyis bdug cing mchod la /
NK019(dza)007:867: ji srid bsnyen sgrub kyi bya ba mthar ma phyin
NK019(dza)007:868: gyi bar du bgegs thams cad bzlog pa'i phrin las
NK019(dza)007:869: mdzod cig / ces bskul ba tsam gyis chog /
NK019(dza)007:870: sngar ma btab na seng ldeng gi phur bu sor
NK019(dza)007:871: brgyad pa tsan+dana gyis kha bsgyur ba dar gyi cod
NK019(dza)007:872: pan can bcu mdun du bkod la /
NK019(dza)007:873: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:874: zhes brjod pas bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje sku
NK019(dza)007:875: mdog mthing nag mthing dkar dmar ba'i zhal gsum phyag
NK019(dza)007:876: drug gi g.yas gsum rdo rje ral gri dgra s+t+wa
NK019(dza)007:877: / g.yon gsum zhags pa lcags sgrog thong gshol 'dzin pa /
NK019(dza)007:878: nyi ma 'bum gyi gzi brjid can /
NK019(dza)007:879: gar dgu'i nyams kyis sgeg cing /
NK019(dza)007:880: dur khrod rol pa'i chas kyis brgyan pa /
NK019(dza)007:881: yum kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai ma dang mnyam par sbyor ba'i skur gyur /
NK019(dza)007:882: phata phata badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la man+da la /
NK019(dza)007:884: zhes brjod pas shangs kyi h+aum ring dang /
NK019(dza)007:885: byang chub kyi sems sprin las /
NK019(dza)007:886: rdo rje ye shes kyi snang ba'i mtshon cha dang /
NK019(dza)007:887: khro bo 'chol pa'i tshogs spros pas phyogs bcu'i dregs pa can thams cad tshar bcad /
NK019(dza)007:888: gtso bo phyogs skyong bcu bkug ste /
NK019(dza)007:889: steng 'og phyogs mtshams bcur nyi ma'i gdan re re'i
NK019(dza)007:890: steng du myos shing 'gyel stabs su 'khod par gyur
NK019(dza)007:891: / slar yang khro bo'i tshogs rnams tshur 'dus /
NK019(dza)007:892: mdun du bkod pa'i phur bu rnams la thim pas khro bo bcur gyur /
NK019(dza)007:893: h+aum k+aa ra badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:894: bi dza ya ya m+aan+ta ka h+ya g+r+ai wa a
NK019(dza)007:895: mri ta kun+da li n+ai la dan+da tree lo kya
NK019(dza)007:896: bi dza ya a pa r+aa dzi ta +aar+ya a
NK019(dza)007:897: tsa la ma h+aa ba la ces khro bcu so
NK019(dza)007:898: so'i sngags mthar / g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya sarba dush+tam phata /
NK019(dza)007:899: k+ai la ya k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pam phata /
NK019(dza)007:901: badz+ra k+ai la ya badz+ra d+ha ra +aa dz+ny+aa pa
NK019(dza)007:902: ya ti sarba big+h+n+aana k+aa ya w+aa k+tsit+ta badz+ra k+ai
NK019(dza)007:907: shar du rnam par rgyal ba /
NK019(dza)007:910: lho nub tu mi g.yo ba /
NK019(dza)007:912: nub byang du 'dod pa'i rgyal po /
NK019(dza)007:914: byang shar du khams gsum rnam rgyal /
NK019(dza)007:915: 'og tu stobs po che rnams sku stod khro bo chen po zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK019(dza)007:916: smad phur bu 'bar ba'i rnam pas bgegs la gzir ba /
NK019(dza)007:917: dbyings kyi yum can sprul pa dang yang sprul mtshon
NK019(dza)007:918: cha sna tshogs pa'i sprin spro bas phyogs kun gtams
NK019(dza)007:919: te cis kyang mi shigs par bsam la /
NK019(dza)007:923: 'og nub kyi nub tu gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:924: gnyis pa dam sri mnan pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:925: ra'i sog pa'am dug shog la dam sri'i gzugs lto
NK019(dza)007:926: ba che ba yan lag rid cing 'khums pa'i snying
NK019(dza)007:927: gar tri'i mthar dngos grub la bar du gcod pa'i
NK019(dza)007:928: dam sri pho mo thams cad m+aa ra ya phata
NK019(dza)007:929: / ya ma dam sri stam+b+ha ni dzahdzah zhes bris pa thod ngan du bcug la /
NK019(dza)007:930: sgrub khang gi them pa'i phyi rol du dong gru
NK019(dza)007:931: gsum brus pa'i nang du gan rkyal du bzhag la
NK019(dza)007:933: brub khung yangs shing gting zab pa'i nang du tri
NK019(dza)007:934: las dam sri pho mo rid cing nyam thag pa'i
NK019(dza)007:937: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK019(dza)007:938: dkon mchog gsum gyi bden pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:939: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i chos can rgyu 'bras
NK019(dza)007:940: bslu ba med pa'i bcom ldan 'das bde gshegs zhi
NK019(dza)007:941: khro rab 'byams tshogs chen 'dus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi
NK019(dza)007:942: lha tshogs rnams kyi sprul pa yang sprul phyag brnyan
NK019(dza)007:943: dang bcas pa rnams kyi bden pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:944: bden pa chen po'i byin gyi rlabs kyis /
NK019(dza)007:945: dngos grub sgrub pa la bar du gcod pa'i ya
NK019(dza)007:946: ma dam sri 'khor bcas mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten
NK019(dza)007:948: tri yam dzah tri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah dzahh+aum bam
NK019(dza)007:949: hoh zhes pas dgug bstim yid ches par byas la
NK019(dza)007:950: / ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum sarba dush+t+aana ya ma dam sri m+aa ra ya h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:953: dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NK019(dza)007:955: dngos grub chu la rdul 'jug pa //
NK019(dza)007:956: khro bo h+aum chen kun 'dus nas //
NK019(dza)007:957: bsad cing mnan pa'i las bya ste //
NK019(dza)007:958: ri rab chen po'i rmang du btang //
NK019(dza)007:959: ya ma r+aa dza'i zas su sbyar //
NK019(dza)007:960: chu srin 'bar ba'i kha ru rdzangs //
NK019(dza)007:962: bdun brgyud rigs ni brlag gyur nas //
NK019(dza)007:963: nam yang ldang bar mi nus te //
NK019(dza)007:964: byang chub sems ni skyes na btang //
NK019(dza)007:965: zhes brjod cing ling+ga spyi'i tshugs su mnan /
NK019(dza)007:970: rus chen rnams btab pa'i khar /
NK019(dza)007:971: ro g.yam la rgya gram gyi steng sum bris pa ri rab tu gyur pas mnan /
NK019(dza)007:974: 'khor lo dang rgya gram gyis mnan par bsam la sas su bas /
NK019(dza)007:976: zhes rdo rje'i dbyug pa'i rgyas brdeg /
NK019(dza)007:977: ma ma p+aa sham ku ru nan /
NK019(dza)007:978: zhes bdag gis dbang du bya /
NK019(dza)007:980: zhes pas khro bo stobs po ches mnan par bsam /
NK019(dza)007:981: de'i steng du bro ra gru gsum rtse mo lhor bstan pa bcas la /
NK019(dza)007:982: lag pa bsnol nas mathe'u chung sgrel /
NK019(dza)007:984: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK019(dza)007:985: zhes pas snod bcud khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du bzhengs par bsams te /
NK019(dza)007:987: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK019(dza)007:989: thal ba'i rdul bzhin brlag nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:990: drag po'i phrin las sgrub par mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:992: ya ma dam sri m+aa ra ya phata /
NK019(dza)007:994: gsum pa sgo byang gdags pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:995: rtsa rgyud dang las thor gshin rje gshed kyi sgo byang las ma gsungs kyang /
NK019(dza)007:997: sgo byang phyi nang dgra bgegs bskrad //
NK019(dza)007:998: ces pa ltar sgo byang phyi ma lug gam rkyang gi sog pa g.yon pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:1000: yang na gnyis ka dur khrod kyi ras lta bur bris kyang rung ste /
NK019(dza)007:1001: sku'i rgyab tu so so'i sngags dang gsol byang bris la /
NK019(dza)007:1002: sgo'i ya them gyi phyi la gshin rje gshed dang /
NK019(dza)007:1003: nang ngos su rta mgrin gdags /
NK019(dza)007:1004: mchod gtor re yang bshams pa byin gyis brlab la /
NK019(dza)007:1006: stong pa'i ngang las ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1007: zhes brjod pas gshin rje gshed smug nag 'khor lo
NK019(dza)007:1008: dang be con 'dzin pa ma he'i khri la dor
NK019(dza)007:1009: stabs kyis bzhugs pa'i skur gyur /
NK019(dza)007:1010: ye shes pa badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes pas spyan drangs shing bstim la /
NK019(dza)007:1011: ya m+aan+ta ka sa pa ri w+aa ra push+pe nas shap+da'i bar gyis mchod /
NK019(dza)007:1012: mtshan sngags de nyid la nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags btags pas gtor ma phul la /
NK019(dza)007:1014: gsang chen lhun grub pho brang nas //
NK019(dza)007:1015: las kyi gshin rje'i bdag po la //
NK019(dza)007:1016: bcom ldan chos rjes bka' stsal ltar //
NK019(dza)007:1017: de bzhin rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK019(dza)007:1018: bka' gsang gzhung chen 'di sgrub cing //
NK019(dza)007:1019: yang dag don la bdag 'jug na //
NK019(dza)007:1020: 'di dag nor bu rin chen te //
NK019(dza)007:1021: 'di la gnod cing bar gcod pa'i //
NK019(dza)007:1022: lha srin 'byung po sde brgyad kun //
NK019(dza)007:1023: khyod kyi 'khor dang g.yog yin gyi //
NK019(dza)007:1024: rnam par smin pa'i chos shod la //
NK019(dza)007:1025: gsang ba mchog gi rnal 'byor pas //
NK019(dza)007:1026: bla med 'bras bu ma thob par //
NK019(dza)007:1027: sa 'di yan chad ma btang zhig /
NK019(dza)007:1028: dpal chen mi pham bka' ma 'da' //
NK019(dza)007:1029: bdag cag ye nas gnyis med de //
NK019(dza)007:1030: da tsam don gyi dbyings su gcig /
NK019(dza)007:1031: phyi 'khor skyong ba'i mu ran la //
NK019(dza)007:1032: rdo rje yal gam thub par mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:1033: badz+ra ya ma r+aa dza sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK019(dza)007:1034: zhes bzlas nas me tog 'thor zhing brtan bzhugs bya /
NK019(dza)007:1035: de nas nang gi rten bsang sbyangs /
NK019(dza)007:1036: stong pa'i ngang las ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1037: zhes brjod pas rta mgrin dmar po thod dbyug dang
NK019(dza)007:1038: sdigs mdzub can pad nyi la dor stabs kyis bzhugs
NK019(dza)007:1039: pa'i skur gyur / drangs bstim dang /
NK019(dza)007:1040: ha ya g+r+ai wa sa pa ri w+aa ra'i mthar sngags sngar bzhin sbrel bas mchod gtor phul /
NK019(dza)007:1042: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK019(dza)007:1043: mngags gzhug pho nya'i las mdzad pa //
NK019(dza)007:1044: spyan ras gzigs dbang rta mgrin gyis //
NK019(dza)007:1045: gdon bgegs sbyor ba rgyun chod cig /
NK019(dza)007:1046: h+r+aihpad+m+aan+ta krita badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK019(dza)007:1047: zhes bzla zhing brtan bzhugs bya ba'o //
NK019(dza)007:1048: gsum pa nang mtshams la bzhi las /
NK019(dza)007:1049: dang po 'bar ba lta ba'i mtshams ni /
NK019(dza)007:1050: mched kun nang du zhugs la /
NK019(dza)007:1052: zhes brjod pas rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rje 'jigs
NK019(dza)007:1053: shing rngams pa'i skur gyur pa'i mig gnyis ma dang
NK019(dza)007:1054: ta las nyi ma dang zla ba /
NK019(dza)007:1055: mig 'bras h+aum las bskal pa'i me 'bar zhing rdo
NK019(dza)007:1056: rje'i tsh+wa tsh+wa 'phro ba'i blta bas bdud bgegs log
NK019(dza)007:1057: par 'dren pa'i tshogs thams cad bsdigs bskrad brlag par
NK019(dza)007:1058: byas / rkang mthil gnyis su h+aum yig 'bar ba'i
NK019(dza)007:1059: rdo rje'i gom stabs las rdo rje 'bar ba'i sprin
NK019(dza)007:1060: 'phro bas phyogs kun gtams te cis kyang mi shigs
NK019(dza)007:1062: rdo rje yi ni nang dag tu //
NK019(dza)007:1063: seng ge'i lta bas bltas nas ni //
NK019(dza)007:1064: rdo rje'i gom pas phyogs byas nas //
NK019(dza)007:1065: khro mig 'bar bas phyir bltas te //
NK019(dza)007:1066: 'gying bag tshul du brjid pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1067: 'bar pa'i rdo rje spar nas ni //
NK019(dza)007:1068: phyi nang rdul chen gsal bar bya //
NK019(dza)007:1070: h+aum bzhi pa'i sngags brjod cing /
NK019(dza)007:1071: 'gying ba dang bcas pa'i snyems pas rdo rje gsor /
NK019(dza)007:1072: dril bu bkrol seng ge'i lta stangs kyis phyogs thams
NK019(dza)007:1073: cad du blta zhing dbang ldan nas rdo rje'i 'gros
NK019(dza)007:1074: kyis g.yas su bskor ba'i gar gyis bcag go //
NK019(dza)007:1075: gnyis pa khro bo rol pa'i mtshams ni /
NK019(dza)007:1076: rang nyid zhe sdang rdo rjer gsal pa'i thugs ka'i h+aum las khro bo'i sprin mi bzad pa spros /
NK019(dza)007:1077: gsang spyod blta bar mi dbang ba'i bgegs dang log 'dren thams cad bcom /
NK019(dza)007:1078: slar 'dus pa las khro tshogs 'bar ba'i gur gyis phyogs kun gtams par bsam la /
NK019(dza)007:1080: stong gsum stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK019(dza)007:1081: skye 'gro rtsi shing nags tshal dang //
NK019(dza)007:1082: mthong yod snang grags ji snyed pa //
NK019(dza)007:1084: rngams chen gtum thung sha thag 'bar //
NK019(dza)007:1085: dur khrod dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK019(dza)007:1087: rak+ta kro d+ha dz+wa la kha /
NK019(dza)007:1088: ha la ha la tista phata /
NK019(dza)007:1090: spro na khro bcu'i stangs stabs dang /
NK019(dza)007:1092: phra men ma'i rngams stabs sogs kyang bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:1093: gsum pa mtshon cha 'chol ba'i mtshams ni /
NK019(dza)007:1094: khro bo'i tshogs las mtshon cha mi bzad pa'i sprin spros pas phyogs kun bcings par bsam la /
NK019(dza)007:1096: rdo rje 'khrigs pa'i phreng ba dang //
NK019(dza)007:1097: tho ba lcags kyu 'bar ba dang //
NK019(dza)007:1098: 'khor lo ral gri la sogs rdzas //
NK019(dza)007:1099: kun gyi phyag rgya'i mtshan mas bskor //
NK019(dza)007:1100: rdo rje'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK019(dza)007:1101: badz+ra kro d+ha ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1103: badz+ra kro d+ha mung+ga ra a ko ta ya h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1105: badz+ra kro d+ha ang+gu sha h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1107: badz+ra kro d+ha dz+ny+aa na tsakra h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1109: badz+ra kro d+ha t+aik+sh+na sa ma ya h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1111: bzhi pa sreg byed me'i mtshams ni /
NK019(dza)007:1112: bdag gi thugs ka nas su yig 'phros /
NK019(dza)007:1113: gser gyi ri rab rtse mo rtsibs brgyad pa'i rnam
NK019(dza)007:1114: pa la lha chen brgyad 'gyel stabs su khro bo'i
NK019(dza)007:1115: dbang phyug brgyad kyis mnan pa /
NK019(dza)007:1116: de'i steng du thugs ka nas spros pa'i h+aum yig
NK019(dza)007:1117: yongs su gyur pa las bdag nyid dang gnyis su
NK019(dza)007:1118: med pa'i zhe sdang rdo rje mthing nag ma t+aam
NK019(dza)007:1120: khyab 'jug gi pags pas stod g.yogs gsol zhing /
NK019(dza)007:1121: stag dang bya rgod kyi mgo can sogs phra men dgu khris bskor ba /
NK019(dza)007:1122: 'jigs shing rngams pa'i skur gyur pa'i thugs ka dang /
NK019(dza)007:1123: spyan pa sogs pa'i h+aum yig /
NK019(dza)007:1124: mtshon cha'i gur rnams las kyang bskal pa'i me dpung
NK019(dza)007:1125: rnon po 'bar shing 'khrugs pas bgegs thams cad sregs
NK019(dza)007:1126: shing 'bar ba'i klong gis phyogs kun gtams par bsam
NK019(dza)007:1127: la / h+aum ram rdo rje me yi ri //
NK019(dza)007:1128: lhun po 'bar ba'i rtse brgyad la //
NK019(dza)007:1129: 'bar ba'i lha chen sgyel nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:1130: dbang chen rdo rje bka' sdod gnas //
NK019(dza)007:1131: shin tu mi bzad 'bar ba yi //
NK019(dza)007:1132: gtum chen ha la rngams pa'i gzugs //
NK019(dza)007:1133: lha chen khyab 'jug lpags bshus nas //
NK019(dza)007:1134: zhing chen g.yang gzhi na bzar mnabs //
NK019(dza)007:1135: gshin rje ma t+aam 'bar ba yi //
NK019(dza)007:1136: ro dbyug chen po phyag na 'phyar //
NK019(dza)007:1137: phra men dgu khri mang po dag /
NK019(dza)007:1138: 'bar ba'i tshogs ni gtibs thag bcad //
NK019(dza)007:1139: gang la cis 'dul der ston pa'i //
NK019(dza)007:1141: do shal mgur chu'i phreng ba 'dren //
NK019(dza)007:1142: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong //
NK019(dza)007:1144: nam mkha'i khams kun me dpung gtibs //
NK019(dza)007:1146: dur khrod dgon pa'i sa phyogs dag /
NK019(dza)007:1147: me yi ri bo 'bar ba la //
NK019(dza)007:1148: me yi yi dwags me dag las //
NK019(dza)007:1149: gang yang gnas par mi phod pa //
NK019(dza)007:1150: steng gi me lce 'bar ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1153: gyen du 'khyil zhing steng du thal //
NK019(dza)007:1154: me lce dgu phreng 'bar ba dag /
NK019(dza)007:1156: dur khrod me ni smug cing 'bar //
NK019(dza)007:1158: nga rgyal sreg pas ser nag 'bar //
NK019(dza)007:1160: phrag dog sregs pas ljang nag 'khrug /
NK019(dza)007:1161: gti mug sel bas smug nag 'khyil //
NK019(dza)007:1163: rdo rje me'i phyag rgya bcas pa bskor zhing /
NK019(dza)007:1167: de nas bar du gcad bya gcod byed thams cad sems kyi rtog pa ste /
NK019(dza)007:1168: sems nyid dbyings dang ye shes gnyis med rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil 'khor du rtogs pas /
NK019(dza)007:1169: bar chad kyi ming tsam yang dmigs su ma grub
NK019(dza)007:1170: pa ni mi shigs rdo rje'i mtshams gcod ces bya
NK019(dza)007:1171: ste / don la gsang ba de kho na nyid kyi mtshams so //
NK019(dza)007:1172: de nas gnas 'khor yo byad byin gyis brlab pa la gsum las /
NK019(dza)007:1173: dang po dbang bsgyur gyi ting nge 'dzin gyis gnas byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:1174: don chos nyid kyi rol pa ye shes lngar ma
NK019(dza)007:1175: 'gags par snang ba'i rtags su kun gzhi byang chub
NK019(dza)007:1176: kyi sems h+aum yig 'bar ba'i sprin las /
NK019(dza)007:1177: e yam ra sum kem ram /
NK019(dza)007:1178: zhes cho 'phrul gyi rang sgrar grags pa las yum
NK019(dza)007:1179: lnga'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa 'byung ba lnga'i
NK019(dza)007:1180: dkyil 'khor du lhun gyis grub par gyur /
NK019(dza)007:1181: slar yang b+h+r+aum zhes pa'i sgra gdangs kyi rkyen las
NK019(dza)007:1182: nam mkha' thams cad pho brang gi gzhal yas khang
NK019(dza)007:1184: brum kham tam kha ta li b+h+r+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1185: zhes brjod cing gnas khang gi phyogs kun tu bdud rtsi lngas gtor zhing byug go //
NK019(dza)007:1186: gnyis pa phyag rgya chen po'i ting 'dzin gyis 'khor brlab pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:1187: thog mar rtags gsum gdab ste /
NK019(dza)007:1188: mgrin par zhag gi zo ris zla gam du gdab cing /
NK019(dza)007:1190: chos rnams ye nas gnyis med pa'i //
NK019(dza)007:1191: byang chub sems su gcig pa'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:1192: zhag gi zo ris mtshan ma ni //
NK019(dza)007:1193: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK019(dza)007:1194: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad du //
NK019(dza)007:1195: sangs rgyas kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:1196: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig lags //
NK019(dza)007:1198: ma h+aa smri ti man+da la h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1199: dpral par thal chen gyi tshom bu rtse gsum ris su /
NK019(dza)007:1201: chos rnams ye nas gnyis med pa'i //
NK019(dza)007:1202: byang chub sems su gcig pa'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:1203: thal chen tshom bu'i mtshan ma ni //
NK019(dza)007:1204: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang //
NK019(dza)007:1205: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad du //
NK019(dza)007:1206: keng chen kun dang gcig pa'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:1207: 'di yang sngon gyi dam tshig lags //
NK019(dza)007:1209: ma h+aa kem ni ri ti dz+wa la man+da la h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1210: dpral kos mkhur tshos bzhir rak+ta'i thig le /
NK019(dza)007:1212: chos rnams byang chub rak+ta'i thig le'i mtshan ma ni //
NK019(dza)007:1213: he ru ka yi dur khrod chen mkha' 'gro kun
NK019(dza)007:1214: dang 'di yang sngon 'di yang rtags ma h+aa rak+ta
NK019(dza)007:1215: ti la ka man+da la h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1217: de nas thams cad bdud rtsi lngas khrus byas la /
NK019(dza)007:1218: slob dpon gyi phyag sor g.yas g.yon gyi nyi zla'i
NK019(dza)007:1219: dkyil 'khor la rigs lnga yab yum gyi sa bon
NK019(dza)007:1220: bkod pa'i 'od kyis mched thams cad kyi snying nang
NK019(dza)007:1221: na gnas pa'i rigs drug gi sa bon bag chags
NK019(dza)007:1224: de las byung ba'i lus ngag yul dang bcas pa sbyangs te /
NK019(dza)007:1225: sems nyid 'od kyi thig le gser zhun lta bur gyur pa las /
NK019(dza)007:1226: slob dpon gyis h+aum zhes brjod pas rigs lnga 'dus
NK019(dza)007:1227: pa'i sras mchog rdo rje sems dpa'i skur sad pa'i
NK019(dza)007:1228: gnas gsum du +aahh+aum gi rgyas btab pas byin gyis
NK019(dza)007:1229: brlabs / spyi bo ham bkod pa zhu ba'i 'od
NK019(dza)007:1230: kyis sku'i cha thams cad rdo rje'i rdul phra rab
NK019(dza)007:1232: rdor dril lag tu gtad de /
NK019(dza)007:1233: gsang ba'i spyod pa rmad du byung ba la bslab par gdams pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:1234: 'jig rten spyod tshul thams cad ni //
NK019(dza)007:1235: sgyu ma yin phyir shin tu spang //
NK019(dza)007:1237: ji ltar 'byung ba de ltar spyod //
NK019(dza)007:1239: slar yang dam pa'i tshig brjod cing gsal gdab pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:1240: e ma'o dur khrod gsang ba yi //
NK019(dza)007:1241: rmad byung zhing khams dga' tshal 'dir //
NK019(dza)007:1242: skal ldan dbang phyug rgyal ba'i sras //
NK019(dza)007:1244: e ma'o dga' mchog bde chen grogs //
NK019(dza)007:1245: dam tshig srog gi lu gu rgyud //
NK019(dza)007:1246: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba yi //
NK019(dza)007:1247: sprul pa'i gshog bu gra rgyas pas //
NK019(dza)007:1248: tshogs gnyis rtsal gyi rlabs spags nas //
NK019(dza)007:1249: chos nyid mkha' la lding bar rigs //
NK019(dza)007:1250: de nas mched kun lhar gsal ba nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du bzhag la /
NK019(dza)007:1254: khyung phrug rtsal sbyong ba bzhin nam mkha' la lding bar gyur /
NK019(dza)007:1256: zhes brjod pas mkha' las babs te so so'i gnas su 'khod pa la gnang ba byin pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:1257: de ring phan chad rgyal ba'i sras //
NK019(dza)007:1258: dbang phyug yin pas ci bder spyod //
NK019(dza)007:1260: gsum pa tshogs chen 'dus pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis yo byad brlab pa las /
NK019(dza)007:1262: stong pa'i ngang las m+aam yig yongs su gyur pa las /
NK019(dza)007:1263: yum m+aa ma k+ai sngon mo bdud rtsi'i bum pa
NK019(dza)007:1264: 'dzin pa'i skur gyur pa'i thugs ka'i m+aam las bdud
NK019(dza)007:1265: rtsi'i chu rgyun babs pas rdzas rnams sbyangs nas bdud
NK019(dza)007:1267: bye brag tu rlob pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:1268: yo byad tsho gsum du bcad la /
NK019(dza)007:1269: tsho gcig gong du nam mkha' mdzod kyi sngags rgyas
NK019(dza)007:1270: mang por spel la sngon 'gro'i dus su mchod sbyin
NK019(dza)007:1271: bya / tsho gcig mjug tu dga' ston gyi phyir gud du bzhag /
NK019(dza)007:1272: tsho gcig sgrub pa'i cha rkyen bya phyir ras sam
NK019(dza)007:1273: shing gzhong la sogs pa'i snod du blugs dur khrod
NK019(dza)007:1275: bdud rtsi lnga gtor bas sbyangs /
NK019(dza)007:1276: zhing chen po'i sha tshil gyi gsur dang gu gul gyi dud pas bdug /
NK019(dza)007:1277: 'bar ba'i lta bas khro bo'i stangs stabs kyis bskor zhing tsham rngam byas la /
NK019(dza)007:1278: yo byad thams cad dam rdzas bdud rtsi lngar gsal
NK019(dza)007:1279: ba'i steng du h+aum s+w+aa +aam h+aas mtshan pa spro
NK019(dza)007:1280: bsdus rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan du gyur /
NK019(dza)007:1281: de las 'od zer spro bsdus rdzas kyi dngos po
NK019(dza)007:1282: sbyangs te ye shes kyi bdud rtsi 'dod yon gyi
NK019(dza)007:1284: de yan chad bsnyen pa'i yan lag go //
NK019(dza)007:1285: gnyis pa nye bsnyen gyi yan lag ni /
NK019(dza)007:1286: rgyud kyi lugs 'dir dmigs rten gyi dkyil 'khor thig tshon gyis bris nas 'go 'dzin pa yin na'ang /
NK019(dza)007:1287: mos slob kyi skabs su lag len bde phyir bsnyen
NK019(dza)007:1288: pa'i yan lag gi mtshams rim gcod pa'i gong du
NK019(dza)007:1289: mdzad pa ltar bkod pa yin no //
NK019(dza)007:1290: de'ang gtor ma dang phyi nang bar gsum gyi mtshams
NK019(dza)007:1291: gcod sogs byed pa'i bar du mched 'ga' zhig gis
NK019(dza)007:1292: dkyil 'khor gyi 'phros brir bcug pa zin pa dang
NK019(dza)007:1294: sgrub dbang mchod pa'i rdzas rnams mdun du zhing lpags steng bkram la /
NK019(dza)007:1295: slob dpon gyis dkyil chog ltar bgegs bskrad sngon du 'gro bas mtshan ma byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK019(dza)007:1296: las mkhan gyis rim pa bzhin dgod par bya ste /
NK019(dza)007:1298: dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su lding khri rim pa gsum
NK019(dza)007:1299: pa bkod pa'i 'og ma'i dbus su sku rten thod
NK019(dza)007:1300: sku dang / de'i rgyab bam sku rten med na
NK019(dza)007:1301: de'i go sar gsung rten yab yum gyi snying po
NK019(dza)007:1303: thugs rten rdor dril gyis g.yas g.yon brten pa dang bcas pa /
NK019(dza)007:1305: dbyings dang ye shes ngo bo nyid //
NK019(dza)007:1307: ye shes mtshan ldan ka p+aa la //
NK019(dza)007:1308: dpal chen yab yum rdzas su bkod //
NK019(dza)007:1309: badz+ra ka p+aa la ahbo d+hi tsit+ta /
NK019(dza)007:1311: lha tsaka rnams rang rang gi sngags kyis lha gnas so sor 'god dgos na'ang /
NK019(dza)007:1312: lag len la mi bde bas zhi khro'i spyi sngags kyis thams cad sbams te 'god pa yin pas /
NK019(dza)007:1313: zhi ba dang khro bo rtsa ba'i lha rnams thod sku'i mdun dang /
NK019(dza)007:1314: de lhag sde tshan bzhir bgos pa sbams te phyogs bzhir 'god /
NK019(dza)007:1315: lding khri bar ma'i dbus su sman sgrub dang 'brel na /
NK019(dza)007:1316: sman bsdu zhing btags btsag bsre sbol gyi dgongs pa
NK019(dza)007:1317: phyag bzhes ltar byas nas gsang bum thod pa kha
NK019(dza)007:1319: ma 'brel na sman phud blugs pa che mchog gi sngags kyis bzhugs su gsol /
NK019(dza)007:1321: zhun chen gsal ba'i mar me ni //
NK019(dza)007:1322: skye med byang chub sems kyi don //
NK019(dza)007:1323: skye ba med pa'i chos dbyings nas //
NK019(dza)007:1324: ma rig mun pa sel byed pa //
NK019(dza)007:1325: ye shes gsal byed don du dgod //
NK019(dza)007:1326: ces pas gcig las med na sman gyi mdun dang /
NK019(dza)007:1327: lnga'am dgu yod na lhag rnams phyogs dang mtshams so sor dgod /
NK019(dza)007:1328: sngar lhag gnas byas pa'i bum pa rnams spos rol
NK019(dza)007:1329: gyis sna drangs te dkyil 'khor la g.yas su bskor
NK019(dza)007:1331: bum pa ma lags rgyal po lags //
NK019(dza)007:1332: rgyal po'i sngags kyis btab nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:1333: rgyal po chen po mnga' gsol gyi //
NK019(dza)007:1334: rgyal po'i tshul du bzhugs su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:1336: zhi khro'i spyi sngags brjod cing /
NK019(dza)007:1337: bum pa dagu'am lnga yod na lding khri steng mar rigs dang mthun pa'i phyogs so so /
NK019(dza)007:1338: gcig las med na dbus su dang /
NK019(dza)007:1339: las bum dkyil 'khor gyi byang shar ram rang gi mdun du dgod /
NK019(dza)007:1340: dbang rdzas gzhan rnams snod du blugs la dkyil 'khor
NK019(dza)007:1341: gyi byang shar du 'jog ces lha rje chen pos
NK019(dza)007:1343: yang na dbu rgyan sogs dbang rdzas dngos su 'byor pa rnams de bzhin dang /
NK019(dza)007:1344: de lhag nang dbang gi rig 'dzin bla ma'i lha tsaka /
NK019(dza)007:1347: sgrub dbang las khyad par gyi sgrub rdzas spyi yan
NK019(dza)007:1348: chad kyi rdzas dbang tsakli rnams sde tshan du sbams
NK019(dza)007:1349: te lding khri 'og ma'i phyogs bzhir bkod kyang mi
NK019(dza)007:1350: 'gal / bye brag sgrub sde'i dbang rdzas rnams tsakli
NK019(dza)007:1351: tsam la brten na sgrub rdzas spyi'i rjes su dang
NK019(dza)007:1352: 'gal / / dngos su bsham na dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' la 'god de /
NK019(dza)007:1353: de la phyi nang gi sgo byang gnyis dbang gi
NK019(dza)007:1354: ngus sgo'i de ka g.yar nas byed pa yin na'ang
NK019(dza)007:1355: / lag len la mi bde bas gzhan zhig bris la bskyed bstim byas nas /
NK019(dza)007:1356: phyi'i sgo byang dkyil 'khor gyi lho dang /
NK019(dza)007:1357: nang gi sgo byang nub tu 'god /
NK019(dza)007:1358: mar me snod bcud dbyings dang ye shes su rtogs
NK019(dza)007:1359: pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis brlabs te shar du 'god
NK019(dza)007:1360: / bsnyen phur byug bdug brab gsum gyis gzi byin
NK019(dza)007:1361: bskyed nas stong pa'i ngang las h+aum las rdo rje
NK019(dza)007:1362: gzhon nur bskyed cing byin gyis brlabs te byang dang
NK019(dza)007:1363: / / khro bcu'i mtshams phur bsrung ba'i dus btab
NK019(dza)007:1364: pa ltar phyogs ma 'khrul bar dkyil 'khor gyi mtha'i
NK019(dza)007:1366: ma mo'i mdos shes pa bzhi ldan ma 'dres yongs rdzogs kyi rol mor 'char zhing /
NK019(dza)007:1367: rak+ta snang ba chags zhen gyi rtog tshogs gnyis med
NK019(dza)007:1368: byang chub sems kyi mkha' klong du sgrol ba'i ting
NK019(dza)007:1369: nge 'dzin gyis brlabs te shar lhor 'god /
NK019(dza)007:1370: chos skyong spyi gtor gru gsum mtheb kyu sum cus bskor ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:1371: sman phud gnyis 'dod yon bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin du brlabs te nub byang du 'god /
NK019(dza)007:1372: e wam ma ya bzhi las bskyed pa'i las bzhi'i hom /
NK019(dza)007:1373: dmar gtor thog made'u'i dbyibs can /
NK019(dza)007:1375: gdab phur rnams dug mtshon gyi nus pa can du brlabs pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:1376: e las brub khung du nya 'o kha sbyor dbye ba byas pa rnams byang shar du 'god /
NK019(dza)007:1377: rig 'dzin spyi gtor zlum brjid pad 'dab bzhis bskor
NK019(dza)007:1378: ba gtor snod chos dbyings kyi klong du gtor rdzas
NK019(dza)007:1379: ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin rig 'dzin bla ma'i dkyil
NK019(dza)007:1380: 'khor 'dod yon gyi mchod sprin 'phro ba dang bcas
NK019(dza)007:1382: sman phud bdud rtsir brlabs te shar lhor 'god /
NK019(dza)007:1383: lnga tshan lnga dang snying po lnga'i rdzas sbyar ba'i
NK019(dza)007:1384: tshe 'brang bum gzugs tshe ril gyis gcer ba dang
NK019(dza)007:1385: / tshe chang gnyis snod gzhal yas khang du bcud
NK019(dza)007:1386: +aam p+aam las tshe dpag med yab yum dkar po
NK019(dza)007:1387: pad+ma dang tshe bum 'dzin par bskyed cing stong khams
NK019(dza)007:1388: kyi tshe srog bsdus nas bstim pa shar du ste
NK019(dza)007:1389: / / de thams cad bka' so so'i sngags brjod bzhin du 'god par bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:1390: gzhan yang sgrub rdzas spyi'i nang tshan /
NK019(dza)007:1391: dpal bshod pad+ma 'dab bzhi'i steng du zla gam kha
NK019(dza)007:1392: sbyor steng dkar 'og dmar ba'i kha rgya gram gyis
NK019(dza)007:1393: bcad cing rdo rje phyed pa'i tog can bsang sbyangs
NK019(dza)007:1394: / rang gi thugs ka nas h+aum dkar po dang
NK019(dza)007:1395: m+aum dmar po 'phros pa zhu ba las thabs shes
NK019(dza)007:1396: nyi zla kha sbyor bde chen byang chub sems kyi
NK019(dza)007:1397: ngo bo las 'dod yon longs spyod kyi sprin 'phro
NK019(dza)007:1399: dbang bshos zla gam dmar po gyen bslang nyi zla'i tog can la /
NK019(dza)007:1400: bdag gi thugs ka nas t+r+aam 'phros zhu ba las
NK019(dza)007:1401: rin po che'i mchod sdong las phyi nang gsang ba'i
NK019(dza)007:1402: mchod sprin 'byung bar brlabs la nub tu 'god /
NK019(dza)007:1403: dkar gsum mngar gsum phye dang sbyar ba'i 'brang rgyas
NK019(dza)007:1404: rtsa ba gsum gcig zlum po dang stod sum gnyis
NK019(dza)007:1405: gshog pa gnyis pa zla gam gzugs g.yas g.yon du
NK019(dza)007:1406: bkra shis kyi bya kha sprod can la gsal shing
NK019(dza)007:1407: rim pa bcu bzhi btsugs pa bza' bca' btung ba'i
NK019(dza)007:1408: dngos grub kyi rdzas mched lcam gyi grangs las lhag
NK019(dza)007:1409: pas bskor ba la 'khor 'das snod bcud kyi yon
NK019(dza)007:1410: tan ma lus pa bsdus shing bstim pas brlabs la
NK019(dza)007:1411: lhor 'god / gsol byang thod pa mtshan ldan du
NK019(dza)007:1412: dza gad bur sbrang gi 'phrad dang bdud rtsi ril
NK019(dza)007:1413: bu'i phab sbyar ba'i steng du /
NK019(dza)007:1414: rang gi thugs ka nas b+h+r+aum 'phros pas 'khor lo
NK019(dza)007:1415: mu khyud dang bcas pa'i lte bar h+aum zung dang
NK019(dza)007:1416: ha brgyad 'phros pa las dpal chen po che mchog
NK019(dza)007:1417: he ru ka yab yum la koo r+ai sogs khro
NK019(dza)007:1418: mo brgyad kyis bskor bar bskyed cing /
NK019(dza)007:1419: gnas gsum gyi yig 'bru'i 'od zer gyis zhi khro'i
NK019(dza)007:1420: lha tshogs thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi byin
NK019(dza)007:1421: rlabs bsdus te thim pas gsol byang la yi ge
NK019(dza)007:1422: 'bru gsum gyi rnam par shar bar bsam la /
NK019(dza)007:1423: +aahh+aum ci rigs bzlas nas byang du bkod pa ni
NK019(dza)007:1424: che mchog barlanga po'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya ste gsang
NK019(dza)007:1425: ba brtul zhugs spyod pa'i sgrub rdzas so //
NK019(dza)007:1426: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan ni zur bzhir mda' dar /
NK019(dza)007:1427: grwa bzhir gri dang me long /
NK019(dza)007:1428: sgo bzhi'i thad kar las bzhi'i phur bu /
NK019(dza)007:1429: zur bzhir rgyal mtshan dang phyogs bzhir ba dan rnams tshon skud kyi d+r+wa bas sbrel zhing /
NK019(dza)007:1430: gzhan yang steng du gdugs dang bla re /
NK019(dza)007:1431: phyogs kun yol ba dang lda ldi la sogs pas mdzes par brgyan /
NK019(dza)007:1433: dkyil 'khor gyi mdun du zhi gtor zlum brjid dkar po mtheb kyu zhe gnyis dang /
NK019(dza)007:1434: khro gtor dpal bshos dmar po zur gsum pa la
NK019(dza)007:1435: 'khor rang 'dra brgyad dang mtheb kyu drug cus gcer
NK019(dza)007:1436: ba / gzhan yang bka' srung dpal mgon lcam dral
NK019(dza)007:1437: sogs srung ma spyi bre brag gi gtor ma rnams
NK019(dza)007:1438: kyang ci bder sgrig cing g.yas g.yon du sman raka
NK019(dza)007:1439: ba / / dkyil 'khor gyi mthar phyi nang gi
NK019(dza)007:1440: mchod rdzas rnams ci 'byor ba bzang zhing bkod legs
NK019(dza)007:1441: par bsham pa sogs 'dir dgos pa'i yo byad thams
NK019(dza)007:1443: de nas gral bsham pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:1444: rnal 'byor pa rtogs goms kyi khyad par gyis /
NK019(dza)007:1445: dkyil 'khor gyi shar phyogs su seng ges bteg pa'i
NK019(dza)007:1446: 'khor lo'i stan nyi zla'i zhabs brten byas pa la
NK019(dza)007:1447: rdo rje rgyal po yab yum bzhugs /
NK019(dza)007:1448: lhor seng ge'i tshab tu glang chen dang zhabs brten
NK019(dza)007:1449: pad+mas byas pa la rdo rje rgyal theb yab yum
NK019(dza)007:1450: / byang du pad+ma dang rdo rjes bteg pa'i rgya gram gyi gdan la karma yab yum /
NK019(dza)007:1451: nub dang byang gi phyogs sam mtshams rnams su gzhi
NK019(dza)007:1452: gcig las byas pa'i stan rgyun ma chad pa rdo
NK019(dza)007:1453: rje rkyang pa gtams pa'i rtse mo lug rgyud du
NK019(dza)007:1454: sbrel ba'i steng du pad+ma phyogs gcig tu bstan pas
NK019(dza)007:1456: rang rang gi mtshan ma zla ba nya gang bar rdo rje rtse gsum pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:1458: phyed pa rnams kyis mtshan pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:1459: la lar zla ba phyed pa'i bcad kha nang bstan la /
NK019(dza)007:1460: rdo rje rtse gcig rno ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:1462: zla rkyang las rgyan med pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:1463: rnal 'byor pa phal pa rnams la nar ma mi'i
NK019(dza)007:1464: gdan zhes ras bal gyi stan nang tshangs can sogs
NK019(dza)007:1466: mos slob tsam la yul lugs dang 'tshams pa'i khri bshams pa la rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK019(dza)007:1467: 'khor rnams stan gyi rim pa ji ltar rigs pa la 'khod nas /
NK019(dza)007:1469: dpon slob thams cad zhwa gos dang rgyan bzang po bstar /
NK019(dza)007:1470: rnal 'byor pho rnams kyis hasta dang /
NK019(dza)007:1471: mo rnams kyis phreng bas g.yob /
NK019(dza)007:1472: sbyar spos kyis bdug cing 'bud bkrol brdung bya'i rol
NK019(dza)007:1473: mo dang gdung dbyangs spyugs glu'i sgra rnams kyis bskul
NK019(dza)007:1474: bas / zhi khro'i lha tshogs thams cad nam mkha' 'gengs pa tsam du 'thibs kyis byon nas /
NK019(dza)007:1475: bdag gnas dkyil 'khor yo byad dang bcas pa la
NK019(dza)007:1476: thim pas sku gsung thugs mi zad pa rgyan gyi
NK019(dza)007:1477: 'khor los byin gyis brlabs par mos la /
NK019(dza)007:1479: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten nas //
NK019(dza)007:1480: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK019(dza)007:1481: rgyal ba'i srung mar gyur pa'i dam tshig can //
NK019(dza)007:1482: mchod do bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK019(dza)007:1484: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:1485: bcom ldan che mchog khro rgyal 'khor dang bcas //
NK019(dza)007:1486: sngags tshig spyugs pa'i brda yis spyan 'dren gyi //
NK019(dza)007:1487: phyag rgya gar gyi brda yis g.yab 'dor na //
NK019(dza)007:1488: dpal chen yab yum thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK019(dza)007:1489: thugs dam brda la dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:1491: chos nyid bde ba chen po'i sku byung ba //
NK019(dza)007:1492: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:1493: dur khrod dregs pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK019(dza)007:1494: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:1495: ye shes 'bar ba brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:1496: goo r+ai khro mo brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:1497: chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:1498: sing+ha phra men brgyad po gshegs su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:1499: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang shed nas //
NK019(dza)007:1500: spor ma gsang yum tshogs rnams gshegs su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:1501: tshad med sgo bzhi gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:1502: rta gdong sgo ma 'khor bcas gshegs su dam tshig
NK019(dza)007:1503: lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang phyug ming sring 'khor bcas
NK019(dza)007:1504: zhe sdang 'bar ba thugs kyi dkyil khro rgyal srin
NK019(dza)007:1505: po 'khor bcas gshegs dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i
NK019(dza)007:1506: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis gshegs sgrol byed 'bar
NK019(dza)007:1507: ba las kyi rdo rje ging chen 'khor bcas ci
NK019(dza)007:1508: bgyis bka' nyan las kyi pho nya sder mo 'khor
NK019(dza)007:1509: bcas las rnams yongs su grub pa'i ye shes ma
NK019(dza)007:1510: mo'i tshogs rnams sdom pa sa la gnas pa'i rig
NK019(dza)007:1512: deng gi gnas mchog dur khrod tshogs de 'dra //
NK019(dza)007:1513: b+hany+dza gsar rnying tshogs ni rdza ltar lhags //
NK019(dza)007:1514: keng rus gsar rnying tshogs ni ri ltar spungs //
NK019(dza)007:1515: rak+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK019(dza)007:1516: m+aam sa gsar rnying tshogs ni thang ltar gdal //
NK019(dza)007:1517: zhing chen gsar rnying tshogs ni bye ltar bkram //
NK019(dza)007:1518: tsit+ta gsang rnying tshogs ni rlung ltar spungs //
NK019(dza)007:1519: byang chub sems kyi tshogs ni gangs ltar chags //
NK019(dza)007:1520: rgyan cha gsar rnying tshogs ni sprin ltar gtibs //
NK019(dza)007:1521: ta na ga na'i tshogs ni dbyings ltar rol //
NK019(dza)007:1522: rdo rje mched lcam lha dang lha mor rol //
NK019(dza)007:1523: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs ni nam mkhar 'thibs //
NK019(dza)007:1524: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la spyan 'dren na //
NK019(dza)007:1525: thugs dam brda la dgongs te gshegs nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:1526: dkyil 'khor chen po 'di la byin phob la //
NK019(dza)007:1527: sgrub pa'i rtags dang mtshan ma bstan nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:1528: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:1529: badz+ra sa ma ya sid+d+hi pheem pheem /
NK019(dza)007:1530: badz+ra yo gi n+ai sa ma ya dzah badz+ra +aa be sha ya a a /
NK019(dza)007:1532: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar byon /
NK019(dza)007:1533: pra be sha ya phata kyis sgo phye /
NK019(dza)007:1534: +aa be sha ya a as gnyis med du bstim pas /
NK019(dza)007:1535: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rnams dang bdag gnas yo
NK019(dza)007:1536: byad dang bcas pa thams cad gzi byin dang ldan
NK019(dza)007:1537: par bsam mo // de nas bsnyen par gnang ba'i dbang bskur ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:1538: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i h+aum las 'od zer 'phros /
NK019(dza)007:1539: slob ma'i sems kyi rtog pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:1540: de las byung ba'i lus ngag sbyangs te mi dmigs
NK019(dza)007:1541: pa'i ngang las h+aum zhes brjod pas dpal chen po
NK019(dza)007:1542: badz+ra he ru ka'i skur gyur pa la /
NK019(dza)007:1543: h+aum las byung ba'i ye shes kyi rdo rje lag g.yas dang /
NK019(dza)007:1544: a las byung ba'i stong nyid kyi chos sgra sgrogs
NK019(dza)007:1545: pa'i dril bu lag g.yon du gtad pas thabs shes
NK019(dza)007:1546: gnyis su med par 'brel ba'i dbang thob par bsam
NK019(dza)007:1548: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK019(dza)007:1549: thabs dang shes rab gnyis med pa'i //
NK019(dza)007:1551: chos la de bzhin dbang bskur ro //
NK019(dza)007:1553: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK019(dza)007:1554: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod rnams la rdo rje dang dril bu'i dbang bskur bas /
NK019(dza)007:1555: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen por zhugs te bsnyen sgrub
NK019(dza)007:1556: rnam bzhi'i sgo nas phrin las rnam pa bzhir longs
NK019(dza)007:1557: spyod pa la thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med
NK019(dza)007:1558: par 'brel ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK019(dza)007:1559: / badz+ra g+han+de tish+tha a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1560: zhes rdo rje gsor zhing dril bu bkrol nas snying gar gtugs la lag tu gtad do //
NK019(dza)007:1561: phur bu badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya h+aum phata
NK019(dza)007:1562: ces pas sras mchog gi skur gyur pa'i gnas gsum
NK019(dza)007:1563: du +aahh+aum gi 'phro 'dus rdo rje gsum du byin
NK019(dza)007:1564: gyis brlabs pa lag tu gtad la /
NK019(dza)007:1566: mi g.yo chos sku yon tan mchog mnga' ba //
NK019(dza)007:1567: sdug bsngal log par 'khyams pa'i sems can rnams //
NK019(dza)007:1568: thugs rjes gnyis med dbyings su sgrol mdzad pa //
NK019(dza)007:1569: khro rgyal 'bar ba'i dbang 'di khyod la byin //
NK019(dza)007:1571: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK019(dza)007:1572: skal ldan rig pa 'dzin pa khyod rnams la phur
NK019(dza)007:1574: bar du gcod pa'i bgegs dang log 'dren ya ma
NK019(dza)007:1575: dam sri thams cad 'dul ba'i dbang dam pa thob
NK019(dza)007:1576: par gyur cig / badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big+h+n+aana bam h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1578: zhes phur bu snying gar gtug cing bgegs la sgril lo //
NK019(dza)007:1579: phreng ba a tsan+d+ra zhes pas zla ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK019(dza)007:1580: la gnas pa'i t+r+aam yig zung lngar gyur pa'i 'od
NK019(dza)007:1581: zer gyis de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsung
NK019(dza)007:1582: rdo rje'i yon tan thams cad bsdus te thim pa
NK019(dza)007:1583: las phreng bar gyur pa gtad la /
NK019(dza)007:1585: rdo rje ru dra bzhad pa che //
NK019(dza)007:1586: khur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin pa //
NK019(dza)007:1587: 'brug gi sgra ltar zab pa yi //
NK019(dza)007:1588: ru lu ru lu'i sgra sgrog bzhad //
NK019(dza)007:1589: phyag rgya 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK019(dza)007:1591: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin bshegs pa skal ldan
NK019(dza)007:1592: rig pa 'dzin pa khyod rnams la phreng ba'i dbang
NK019(dza)007:1593: bskur bas lha'i thugs dam bskul ba'i dzapa bzla ba
NK019(dza)007:1594: dang sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung sgra dbyangs mi
NK019(dza)007:1595: zad pa'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:1596: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1597: zhes phreng ba snying gar gtug cing ru lu'i dzapa cung zad bzlar gzhug go //
NK019(dza)007:1598: rnga nyi ma la gnas pa'i h+aum yig /
NK019(dza)007:1599: badz+ra tsa ma ra dzah ma ra ya h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1600: zhes pas skye med kyi sgra sgrog pa'i ye shes kyi rngar gyur pa gtad la /
NK019(dza)007:1602: chos sku mchog mnga' ye shes kyi cho 'phrul ldan //
NK019(dza)007:1603: dpal gyi phyag rgya ye shes tsa ma ra //
NK019(dza)007:1604: rigs kyi bu mchog khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK019(dza)007:1605: ma mo mkha' 'gro thams cad dbang sdud cing //
NK019(dza)007:1606: thugs dam gnad nas bskul bas bran bzhin du //
NK019(dza)007:1607: 'khol ba'i dbang mchog dam pa thob par shog /
NK019(dza)007:1609: phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i de bzhin gshegs pa skal ldan
NK019(dza)007:1610: rig pa 'dzin pa khyod rnams la ye shes kyi
NK019(dza)007:1612: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro dbang du sdud cing bran
NK019(dza)007:1613: du 'khor ba'i dbang dam pa thob par gyur cig
NK019(dza)007:1614: / badz+ra tsa ma ra dzahm ra ya a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1615: zhes snying gar gtug cing brdung ngo //
NK019(dza)007:1616: de nas brda sgo dbye zhing brda phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:1617: dkyil chog gi rnam pa 'god pa'i cho ga'i sa bcad gsum pa ltar bgyis pas kyang rung mod /
NK019(dza)007:1618: 'dir phyag bzhes su tshigs su bcad pa dang bcas te mdzad pas /
NK019(dza)007:1619: phyogs bzhi nas rdo rje nang bsdams phyir dgrol ba sgo dbye ba'i rgyas /
NK019(dza)007:1621: ye nas mnyam nyid mi 'ad'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:1622: gzung 'dzin bsnol bas sgo bcad de //
NK019(dza)007:1623: bdag med mi gnas ye shes kyis //
NK019(dza)007:1624: yul las 'das pa'i sgo phye zhig /
NK019(dza)007:1625: badz+ra tsakra man+da la pra be sha ya phata /
NK019(dza)007:1627: dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs bzhi'i sgo rim rnams shag gis
NK019(dza)007:1628: bye bas lha rnams kyi zhal mngon du gyur par
NK019(dza)007:1631: shar lho nub byang sgo bzhi nas //
NK019(dza)007:1632: ye shes bzhi yi sgo phye ste //
NK019(dza)007:1633: zhi khro gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK019(dza)007:1634: rnal 'byor mchog gis phyag bgyid do //
NK019(dza)007:1635: a la la hoh zhes phyag btsal bas lha dang
NK019(dza)007:1636: bdag rang rig pa'i ngang du dbyer ma phyed par
NK019(dza)007:1637: bsam mo // de nas sgrub thabs ltar las kyi dbu drang ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)007:1643: dkyil 'khor gyi byang shar du chos 'byung me ri dang bcas pa bris pa'i dbus su /
NK019(dza)007:1644: thal chen dang bsres pa'i 'jim pa'am ngar zan la
NK019(dza)007:1645: ma t+aam gyi gzugs sngo skya khro bzhin can skra
NK019(dza)007:1646: 'bal ba byas pa mgo lho nub la bstan te
NK019(dza)007:1648: badz+ra he ru ko&a ham zhes pas bdag nyid dpal
NK019(dza)007:1649: chen po zhe sdang rdo rje khro gtum bzod par
NK019(dza)007:1650: dka' ba'i gzi byin 'bar bar gyur /
NK019(dza)007:1651: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK019(dza)007:1653: ma t+aam ru dra gdug pa can thams cad mtshan
NK019(dza)007:1654: ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par gyur cig
NK019(dza)007:1655: / ma t+aam ru dra ang+ku sha dzah dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes lan gsum brjod pas /
NK019(dza)007:1656: bdag gi sku las 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu
NK019(dza)007:1657: 'phros log par lta ba'i sdig can gdug pa can
NK019(dza)007:1658: thams cad 'ub kyis 'dus te mdun gyi rten la
NK019(dza)007:1659: thim par gyur / kha t+w+aam ka'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK019(dza)007:1661: dregs pa ru dra sdig can 'di //
NK019(dza)007:1662: nam yang bsgral ba'i zhing yin te //
NK019(dza)007:1663: thugs rje chen po'i thabs kyis bsgral //
NK019(dza)007:1664: kha t+w+aam phyag rgyas bsgyel nas ni //
NK019(dza)007:1665: ma rig mun pa'i sgo phye nas //
NK019(dza)007:1666: rnam shes a ru byin rlabs te //
NK019(dza)007:1667: gsang chen thugs kyi klong du bstim //
NK019(dza)007:1668: sbubs ni gzhal yas 'bar bar gyur //
NK019(dza)007:1669: dzahh+aum bam hohm h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ma t+aam ru dra ha ha pra bi sha phata /
NK019(dza)007:1670: ces bsnun pas gyad kyis sdong gog skyur ba bzhin
NK019(dza)007:1671: lho nub ru mgo phyogs pas gan rkyal du 'gyel
NK019(dza)007:1672: / gzugs phung khrol gyis zhig pas ma rig pa'i sbubs dral nas /
NK019(dza)007:1673: shes pa skye med kyi rang bzhin a dkar po
NK019(dza)007:1674: 'bar bar gyur pa bdag nyid dpal chen po'i thugs
NK019(dza)007:1676: khog pa gzhal yas khang dang gnyis med du gyur par mos la /
NK019(dza)007:1677: yan lag rnams so sor phral te /
NK019(dza)007:1685: pho mtshan byang rnams su bkod pa dur khrod gnas brgyad du bsam mo //
NK019(dza)007:1686: de nas khro bcu'i stangs stabs kyi bgegs dang dam sri brdung ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:1687: bdag nyid dpal chen por gsal ba las khro tshogs dpag tu med pa spros /
NK019(dza)007:1688: nam mkha'i khams thams cad khyab /
NK019(dza)007:1689: gdug pa can thams cad rdo rje'i stangs stabs kyis gzir zhing tshar bcad par gyur /
NK019(dza)007:1690: lag pa thal sbyar gyen du sgreng //
NK019(dza)007:1691: rkang pa phral nas brkyang bskum bya //
NK019(dza)007:1692: gom pa'i stabs kyis gar byed pa //
NK019(dza)007:1693: 'di ni h+aum mdzad phyag rgya yin //
NK019(dza)007:1694: badz+ra kro d+ha h+aum ka ra h+aum gardza gardza h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1695: rkang pa g.yon gyis g.yas la 'khyud //
NK019(dza)007:1696: lag pa gar stabs bskor nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:1697: thal mo drag tu brdab pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1698: rnam par rgyal ba'i phyag rgya yin //
NK019(dza)007:1699: badz+ra kro d+ha bi dza ya h+aum ha na ha na h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1700: lag pa g.yas pa'i mthe bo yis //
NK019(dza)007:1701: mathe'u chung sen mo'i mthil du mnan //
NK019(dza)007:1702: gdengs pa'i stabs su sgreng ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1703: dbyug pa sngon po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK019(dza)007:1704: badz+ra kro d+ha n+ai la dan+da h+aum da ha da ha h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1705: lag pa g.yas pa khu tshur ni //
NK019(dza)007:1706: brdeg pa'i stabs su gdengs pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:1707: g.yon pa dku la brten pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1708: gshin rje 'joms pa'i phyag rgya yin //
NK019(dza)007:1709: badz+ra kro d+ha ya m+aan+ta ka h+aum pa tsa pa tsa h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1710: lag pa g.yas pa'i thal mo ni //
NK019(dza)007:1711: brdeg pa'i stabs su gdengs pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:1712: g.yon pas 'dzin pa ltar byed pa //
NK019(dza)007:1713: mi g.yo mgon po'i phyag rgya yin //
NK019(dza)007:1714: badz+ra kro d+ha +aar+ya a tsa la h+aum ban+d+ha ban+d+ha h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1715: lag pa thal mo sbyar nas ni //
NK019(dza)007:1716: mdzub mo rgyab tu bsnol bar bya //
NK019(dza)007:1717: mthe bong gnyis kyang phral te sgreng //
NK019(dza)007:1718: spyi bor bzhag pa g+r+ai wa'i rgya //
NK019(dza)007:1719: badz+ra kro d+ha ha ya g+r+ai wa h+aum hu lu hu lu h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1720: rkang pa g.yas pa mthur du zug /
NK019(dza)007:1721: lag pa g.yas pa gyen du sgreng //
NK019(dza)007:1722: g.yon gyi rkang pa 'phyar ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1723: gzhan gyis mi thub phyag rgya yin //
NK019(dza)007:1724: badz+ra kro d+ha a pa r+aa dzi ta h+aum tish+tha tish+tha h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1725: lag pa g.yas g.yon dkur brten te //
NK019(dza)007:1726: rkang pa gshibs te mchong ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1727: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i phyag rgya zhes //
NK019(dza)007:1728: dpa' po chen pos yang dag bshad //
NK019(dza)007:1729: badz+ra kro d+ha a mri ta kun+da li h+au ts+tshi n+da ts+tshin+da h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1730: lag pa g.yas g.yon gsnol ba dang //
NK019(dza)007:1731: rkang pa brkyang bskum byas pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1732: khams gsum rnam rgyal phyag rgya zhes //
NK019(dza)007:1733: mgon po dpa' bos yang dag bshad //
NK019(dza)007:1734: badz+ra kro d+ha tree lokya bi dza ya h+aum b+hin+da b+hin+da h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1735: rkang phral mthil ni mthur du zug /
NK019(dza)007:1736: lag pa phral nas gar byed cing //
NK019(dza)007:1737: stabs su mchong bar byed pa ste //
NK019(dza)007:1738: 'di ni stobs chen phyag rgya yin //
NK019(dza)007:1739: badz+ra kro d+ha ma h+aa ba la h+aum s+pho ta s+pho ta h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:1740: ces so so'i phyag rgya bcas la bskor zhing 'gying bar bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:1741: khro bo'i tshogs rnams slar 'dus pa las phyogs kun gtams te cis kyang mi shigs par gyur /
NK019(dza)007:1742: de nas mchod pa byin rlabs nas brtsams te /
NK019(dza)007:1743: sgrub thabs ltar las gzhung bsrang la /
NK019(dza)007:1744: dzapa kyang tshang bar bzla zhing /
NK019(dza)007:1746: lhag chog byas la ske tshang du bsag ste /
NK019(dza)007:1747: zhag drug pa'i phrin las so //
NK019(dza)007:1748: de nas nam langs pa dang ras bris gsar pa'am
NK019(dza)007:1749: rdul tshon gyi phyogs la zur 'debs ltar dkyil 'khor
NK019(dza)007:1750: rab gnas kyi cho ga bya ba ste /
NK019(dza)007:1751: de yan chad nye bsnyen yin la /
NK019(dza)007:1752: gzhan du rab gnas sngon song gi ras bris yin
NK019(dza)007:1753: na zhag drug pa'i phrin las kyi mchod pa byin
NK019(dza)007:1754: rlabs yan chad nye bsnyen gyi yan lag go //
NK019(dza)007:1755: gsum pa sgrub pa'i yan lag ni /
NK019(dza)007:1756: sgrub pa zhag grangs ji tsam byed pa'i dkyil 'khor zhag gi chog khrigs kyi rim pa ste /
NK019(dza)007:1757: de yang 'dir mdo dbang 'bring po zhag bcu gcig pa'i dbang du byas pa la /
NK019(dza)007:1758: dkyil 'khor rab gnas mi dgos na /
NK019(dza)007:1759: zhag drug pa'i nub mo'i phrin las kyi dngos gzhi
NK019(dza)007:1760: ting 'dzin gsum gyis khog dbub pa nas sgrub pa'i
NK019(dza)007:1762: rab gnas dgos pa'i phyogs la zhag bdun pa'i nub mo'i phrin las nas 'go brtsams pa yin pas /
NK019(dza)007:1763: gang ltar kyang zhag dgu pa'i phrin las kyi bar du'o //
NK019(dza)007:1764: de la zhag bdun pa'i chog khrigs ni /
NK019(dza)007:1765: rab gnas zin pa'i dgong mo /
NK019(dza)007:1766: cha gsum btang rjes tho gso bar bya ste /
NK019(dza)007:1767: de gnyis nub dang po khyad par ro //
NK019(dza)007:1768: de nas rgyun du mchod gtor gsos la /
NK019(dza)007:1769: gral phyag dang tshul phyag sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)007:1770: las kyi dbu drang ba nas /
NK019(dza)007:1771: byin 'bebs yan chad song ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:1772: nub dang po la rtags gsum 'dir gdab /
NK019(dza)007:1773: de rjes mchod pa byin rlabs nas bzlas pa'i bar sgrub thabs ltar gzhung bsrang /
NK019(dza)007:1774: spro zhing nus na bzlas pa'i dus su /
NK019(dza)007:1776: rig pa gsung gi sogs dzapa bskul dang rjes kyi bstod pa /
NK019(dza)007:1777: khro bo la ston pa kun tu bzang po gnas
NK019(dza)007:1778: gyur pa sogs so so'i gnas gyur gyis bstod pa
NK019(dza)007:1779: rnams zur 'debs ltar sbyar bar bya /
NK019(dza)007:1780: de ltar bzlas pa zin pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:1781: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK019(dza)007:1784: zhes pas bdag nyid ting 'dzin dam tshig gi dkyil
NK019(dza)007:1785: 'khor du gnas pa nyid slar yang gsal btab la
NK019(dza)007:1786: / de nyid gdod nas rang bzhin gyis rnam par
NK019(dza)007:1787: dag pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo rdzogs pa'i nges
NK019(dza)007:1788: / shes bskyed nas / mdun bskyed ye shes kyi
NK019(dza)007:1789: 'khor lo'i dbus kyi snying po'i dkyil 'khor rnams bdud
NK019(dza)007:1790: rtsi bde ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa
NK019(dza)007:1791: / shes bskyed nas / ni / pho brang 'og
NK019(dza)007:1792: ma'i dbus kyi gru chad bzhi glo 'bur gyis mdzes
NK019(dza)007:1793: pa'i steng 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa'i lte bar /
NK019(dza)007:1794: bdud rtsi'i snod b+hany+dza 'bar bar bcud sha lnga bdud
NK019(dza)007:1795: rtsi lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor gnas pa'i phyi
NK019(dza)007:1796: rol rtsibs brgyad la mthar byed brgyad /
NK019(dza)007:1797: de'i steng gi phyogs bzhir rigs kyi he ru ka
NK019(dza)007:1798: bzhi gnas pa'i dbu badz+ra he ru ka'i zhabs bzhis
NK019(dza)007:1799: bardzisa pa / de'i steng na yum gnam zhal ma
NK019(dza)007:1800: dbu dgu phyag bco brgyad pa zhabs bzhis badz+ra he
NK019(dza)007:1801: ru ka'i g.yas g.yon gyi dbu bardzisa shing /
NK019(dza)007:1802: rtsa zhal gyi dbu ma'i spyan b+ha gar phyed nub tsam du tshud pa /
NK019(dza)007:1803: de'i steng du che mchog he ru ka dbu nyi shu rtsa gcig /
NK019(dza)007:1804: rtse mo rta zhal gyi rnam par ston pa /
NK019(dza)007:1805: phyag zhe gnyis kyis zhi ba'i lha tshogs bsnams pa /
NK019(dza)007:1806: gsang ba'i rdo rje dang zhabs brgyad yum gyi zhal dgu dang sbyor bar bsgoms la /
NK019(dza)007:1807: zhal byang gis gsal gdab pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:1808: e ma'o dpal chen che mchog he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1809: nyi shu rtsa gcig dbu yis sa rnams lhun gyis grub //
NK019(dza)007:1810: sgrib sbyong ye shes dbu ni khro chen stobs po che //
NK019(dza)007:1811: dang po rab tu dga' ba'i sa ni non pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:1812: skyon med ye shes dbu ni khro chen khams gsum rgyal //
NK019(dza)007:1813: gnyis pa dri ma med pa'i sa ni non pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:1814: bdud 'joms ye shes dbu ni khro chen bdud rtsi 'khyil //
NK019(dza)007:1815: gsum pa 'od 'phro ba yis ni non pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:1816: rtog 'joms ye shes dbu ni khro chen 'dod pa'i rgyal //
NK019(dza)007:1817: bzhi pa 'od byed pa yi sa ni gzir mnan ye shes dbu ni khro chen rta mchog dpal //
NK019(dza)007:1818: lnga pa sbyang dka' ba yi sa ni rnam dag ye shes dbu ni khro chen mi g.yo mgon //
NK019(dza)007:1819: drug pa mngon du gyur pa'i sa ni thabs mkhas ye shes dbu ni khro chen gshin rje gshed //
NK019(dza)007:1820: bdun pa ring du song ba'i sa ni stobs ldan ye shes dbu ni khro chen dbyug sngon can //
NK019(dza)007:1821: brgyad pa mi g.yo ba yi sa ni mkhyen ldan ye shes dbu ni khro chen rnam par rgyal //
NK019(dza)007:1822: dgu pa legs pa'i blo gros sa ni brjid gnon ye shes dbu ni khro chen h+aum k+aa ra //
NK019(dza)007:1823: bcu pa chos kyi sprin gyi sa ni mngon shes ye shes dbu ni yak+sha he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1824: bcu gcig kun tu 'od kyi sa ni kun mkhyen ye shes dbu ni gu h+ya he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1825: bcu gnyis rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa ni byams mgon ye shes dbu ni sa nu he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1826: bcu gsum rdo rje 'chang gi sa ni rngams brjid ye shes dbu ni rak+sha he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1827: bcu bzhi stug po bkod pa'i sa ni sprul pa ye shes dbu ni karma he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1828: bco lnga pad+ma can gyi sa ni chags med ye shes dbu ni pad+ma he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1829: bcu drug 'khor lo tshogs chen sa ni yid bzhin ye shes dbu ni rat+na he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1830: bcu bdun de ba ko sha'i sa ni 'bar 'phro ye shes dbu ni bud+d+ha he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:1831: bco brgyad kun bzang dbye ba med pa'i sa ni
NK019(dza)007:1832: stobs ldan ye shes dbu ni badz+ra he ru ka
NK019(dza)007:1833: / bcu dgu rdzogs pa bla ma'i sa ni khyab
NK019(dza)007:1834: brdal ye shes dbu ni che mchog nyid kyi dbu
NK019(dza)007:1835: / // nyi shu srid gsum ngang rdzogs sa ni
NK019(dza)007:1836: 'ub chub ye shes dbu ni rta skad nam mkhar
NK019(dza)007:1837: / // 'tsher // rtsa gcig ye shes bla ma'i sa ni non pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:1838: g.yas kyi zhal gdangs mche ba gtsigs pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1839: 'khor ba'i skye shi rtsad nas gcod par mdzad //
NK019(dza)007:1840: g.yon gyi zhal gdangs mche ba gtsigs pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1841: 'khor ba'i nyon mongs sdug bsngal zad par byed //
NK019(dza)007:1842: dbus kyi dbu rnams zhal gdangs mche ba gtsigs //
NK019(dza)007:1843: chos nyid klong du thams cad rdub par mdzad //
NK019(dza)007:1844: g.yas spyan bzlog pas bdud bgegs thal bar rlog /
NK019(dza)007:1845: g.yon spyan bzlog pas ngan song sdug bsngal bsal //
NK019(dza)007:1846: dbus spyan bzlog pas chos dbyings sa ler gzigs //
NK019(dza)007:1847: mche ba dkar po zangs yag gtsigs pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1848: 'khor ba'i bag chags skye shi rtsad nas gcod //
NK019(dza)007:1849: ral pa dmar po gyen du bardzesa pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1850: chos dbyings ye shes mthar thug 'gran zla med //
NK019(dza)007:1851: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis phyag ni mngon sangs rgyas //
NK019(dza)007:1852: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi dang po ni //
NK019(dza)007:1853: kun tu bzang po mnyam pa'i phyag rgya can //
NK019(dza)007:1854: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi dang po na //
NK019(dza)007:1855: kun tu bzang mo thal mo mnyam sbyor phyag /
NK019(dza)007:1856: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi gnyis pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1857: rnam par snang mdzad gser gyi 'khor lo bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1858: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi gnyis pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1859: sangs rgyas spyan ma gser gyi dril bu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1860: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi gsum pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1861: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1862: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi gsum pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1863: rdo rje dbyings phyug shel gyi dril bu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1864: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bzhi pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1865: rin chen 'byung ldan rin chen zur brgyad bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1866: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bzhi pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1867: m+aa ma k+ai ni g.yu yi dril bu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1868: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi lnga pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1869: snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma 'dab brgyad bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1870: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi lnga pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1871: na bza' dkar mo byu ru'i dril bu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1872: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi drug pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1873: don yod grub pa rdo rje rgya gram bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1874: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi drug pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1875: dam tshig sgrol ma mthing gi dril bu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1876: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bdun pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1877: sa yi snying po rin chen myu gu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1878: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bdun pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1879: l+aa s+ye dkar mo me long rgya gram bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1880: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi brgyad pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1881: nam mkha'i snying po gcod byed ral gri bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi brgyad pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1882: m+aa l+ye sngon mo rin chen phreng ba bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1883: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi dgu pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1884: spyan ras gzigs dbang pad+ma dkar po bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1885: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi dgu pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1886: g+airti dmar mo lcags sgrog pi wang bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1887: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1888: phyag na rdo rje rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1889: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu pa na //
NK019(dza)007:1890: nirti ljang gu dar gyi cod pan bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1891: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu gcig na //
NK019(dza)007:1892: mgon po byams ba klu shing gun+d+he bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1893: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu gcig na //
