NK019(dza)007:1895: sgrib pa rnam sel gsung rab pusti bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu gnyis na //
NK019(dza)007:1896: lha mo push+pe ma ni me tog bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1897: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu gsum na //
NK019(dza)007:1898: kun tu bzang po rin chen snye ma bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1899: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu gsum na //
NK019(dza)007:1900: lha mo +aa lo ke ni mar me bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1901: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu bzhi na //
NK019(dza)007:1902: 'jam dpal gzhon nu me tog ut+pala bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1903: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu bzhi na //
NK019(dza)007:1904: lha mo gan+d+he ma ni dri chab bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1905: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bco lnga na //
NK019(dza)007:1906: gshin rje gshed po thod dbyug gdengs pa bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1907: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bco lnga na //
NK019(dza)007:1908: 'gugs byed lcags kyu ma ni lcags kyu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1909: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu drug na //
NK019(dza)007:1910: shes rab mthar byed rdo rje rtse lnga bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1911: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu drug na //
NK019(dza)007:1912: 'ching byed zhags pa ma ni zhags pa bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1913: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu bdun na //
NK019(dza)007:1914: pad+ma mthar byed thod dbyug sbrul dkris bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1915: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu bdun na //
NK019(dza)007:1916: sdom byed nyi zla ma ni lcags sgrog bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1917: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bco brgyad na //
NK019(dza)007:1918: bgegs rnams mthar byed rdo rje rgya gram bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1919: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bco brgyad na //
NK019(dza)007:1920: thal byed dril bu ma ni dril bu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1921: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi bcu dgu na //
NK019(dza)007:1922: lha dbang brgya byin sgra brnyan pi wang bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1923: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi bcu dgu na //
NK019(dza)007:1924: par+na sha ba ri ni pusti bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi nyi shu na //
NK019(dza)007:1925: sh+aakya thub pa gseg shang par bu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1926: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi nyi shu na //
NK019(dza)007:1927: kha 'bar de wa rin chen sgrom bu bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yas kyi tha ma na //
NK019(dza)007:1928: lha min thag bzang ris ni go cha bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1929: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis g.yon gyi tha ma na //
NK019(dza)007:1930: a wa glang mgo bsil drod me chu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1931: ting 'dzin zhabs kyis khro mo'i dbu brgyad bardzisa //
NK019(dza)007:1932: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi dang po bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1933: thig le chen po'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK019(dza)007:1934: yengs pa med pa chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:1935: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi gnyis pa bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1936: bde ba chen po'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK019(dza)007:1937: klong du gyur pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:1938: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi gsum pa bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1939: rdo rje lta bu'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK019(dza)007:1940: skye shi med pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:1941: zhabs brgyad g.yas kyi tha ma bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1942: thams cad 'byung gnas ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK019(dza)007:1943: zad pa med pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:1944: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi dang po bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1945: chags pa med pa'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK019(dza)007:1946: ye nas dag pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:1947: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi gnyis pa bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1948: 'da' bar dka' ba'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK019(dza)007:1949: mthong ba med pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:1950: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi gsum pa bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1951: dmigs su med pa'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK019(dza)007:1952: rang bzhin med pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:1953: zhabs brgyad g.yon gyi tha ma bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:1954: skye shi med pa 'i ting 'dzin chen po dang //
NK019(dza)007:1955: 'du 'bral med pa'i chos kyi dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:1956: dbu skra kham nag gyen du 'khyil ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1957: srid pa gsum las rnam par rgyal ba'i rgyan //
NK019(dza)007:1958: rta mgo ljang khu rta skad sgrogs pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1959: snang srid thams cad dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1960: smin mtshams khro gnyer glog ltar 'gyu ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1961: ma rig rmongs pa'i mun pa sel ba'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1962: tshangs pa'i g.yang gzhi na bzar gsol ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1963: longs spyod rdzogs sku mngon du bstan pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1964: sku mdog mthing nag 'jigs par bstan pas ni //
NK019(dza)007:1965: chos kyi sku la 'gyur ba med pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1966: sku smad stag gi sham thabs mnabs pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1967: sprul pa sku yis cir yang don mdzad rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1968: sku stod glang chen ko rlon gsol ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1969: theg pa rim dgus 'gro don mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1970: zhing chen g.yang gzhi sku la gsol ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1971: thugs rje tshad med bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1972: thod pa skam pos dbu la brgyan pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1973: dus gsum rgyal bas bsnyen bkur mdzad pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1974: sbrul nag stong gi gdengs kas brgyan pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1975: klu rgyal rigs bzhi dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1976: khrag zhag thal ba'i thig les brgyan pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1977: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbang du sdud pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1978: bskal pa'i me dpung klong na bzhugs pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1979: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer 'phro ba'i rgyan //
NK019(dza)007:1980: rdo rje'i gshog pa nam mkhar gdengs pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1981: stong gsum 'jig rten zil gyis gnon pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1982: 'bar ba chen po'i gar dgus sgeg pa ni //
NK019(dza)007:1983: che btsan dper bya kun las 'das pa'i rtags //
NK019(dza)007:1984: khro rgyal che mchog 'bar ba'i zhabs 'og na //
NK019(dza)007:1985: shin tu rngams pa'i khro mo gnam zhal ma //
NK019(dza)007:1986: sku gdog dud kha sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK019(dza)007:1987: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK019(dza)007:1988: rnam thar dbu brgyad gyen du byung ba ni //
NK019(dza)007:1989: gsang ba'i thugs rje thabs dang shes rab ldan //
NK019(dza)007:1990: byang chub sems ni bdud rtsi ga 'ur skyil //
NK019(dza)007:1991: 'jam dpal gzhon du bdud rtsi'i pho brang bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:1992: rta mgrin yab yum bdud rtsi'i pho brang skyil //
NK019(dza)007:1993: stong pa bco brgyad phyag ni mya ngan 'das //
NK019(dza)007:1994: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis //
NK019(dza)007:1995: b+hany+dza rak+tasa bkang ba rdo rjes dkrug /
NK019(dza)007:1996: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi dang 'og na //
NK019(dza)007:1997: goo r+ai b+han dmar zhing gi dbyug to 'phyar //
NK019(dza)007:1998: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi dang 'og na //
NK019(dza)007:1999: sim ha mu kh+ai kha ro seng ge mgo //
NK019(dza)007:2000: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi gsum pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2001: tsoo r+ai ser mo mda' gzhu 'gengs pa'i tshul //
NK019(dza)007:2002: bco brgyad gi g.yon gyi gsum pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2003: b+y+aa g+h+ri mu kh+ai gnas lta rta mgo can //
NK019(dza)007:2004: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi bzhi pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2005: pra mo dmar mo chu srin rgyal mtshan 'phyar //
NK019(dza)007:2006: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi bzhi pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2007: sh+ri g+aal byis ro lces ldag wa mgo can //
NK019(dza)007:2008: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi lnga pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2009: be ta byis za rdo rje rtse dgu 'phyar //
NK019(dza)007:2010: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi lnga pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2011: sh+aa na 'dral lta spyang ki'i mgo bo can //
NK019(dza)007:2012: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi drug pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2013: puk+ka dmar ser zhing chung rgyu ma 'dren //
NK019(dza)007:2014: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi drug pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2015: grid+d+ha dmar mo rgyu 'dren rgod gdong can //
NK019(dza)007:2016: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi bdun pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2017: g+hasma ljang khu dung khrag rdo rjes dkrug /
NK019(dza)007:2018: bco brgya phyag gi g.yon gyi bdun pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2019: kam ka zhing phrag dur bya'i mgo can dmar //
NK019(dza)007:2020: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi brgyad pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2021: sma sha mthing nag byis ro'i snying za ma //
NK019(dza)007:2022: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi brgyad pa na //
NK019(dza)007:2023: k+aa ka kha ro b+han gri bya rog mgo //
NK019(dza)007:2024: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yas kyi tha ma na //
NK019(dza)007:2025: tsan+da ser skya mchog lus 'dral bar byed //
NK019(dza)007:2026: bco brgyad phyag gi g.yon gyi tha ma na //
NK019(dza)007:2027: u lu k+aa mthing 'ug gdong lcags kyu bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:2028: zhabs bzhi bgrad pas rigs bzhi'i dbu nas bardzisa //
NK019(dza)007:2029: zhabs bzhi g.yas kyi dang po bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:2030: klong du gyur pa gsang ba'i b+ha ga dang //
NK019(dza)007:2031: bde ba chen po'i byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:2032: zhabs bzhi g.yon gyi dang po bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:2033: zad stong med pa gsang ba'i b+ha ga dang //
NK019(dza)007:2034: thams cad 'byung ba'i byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:2035: zhabs bzhi g.yas kyi gnyis pa bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:2036: 'du 'bral med pa gsang ba'i b+ha ga dang //
NK019(dza)007:2037: skye shi med pa'i byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:2038: zhabs bzhi g.yon gyi gnyis pa bgrad pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:2039: gdod nas dag pa gsang ba'i b+ha ga dang //
NK019(dza)007:2040: rdo rje lta bu'i byang chub sems su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:2041: khro mo gnam zhal 'bar ba'i zhabs 'og na //
NK019(dza)007:2042: sku gdung 'bar ba'i dpal chen yab yum bcu //
NK019(dza)007:2043: sngo nag smug nag ser nag dmar nag dang //
NK019(dza)007:2044: ljang nag zhal gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NK019(dza)007:2045: rdo rje khor yug dung chen gang ba dang //
NK019(dza)007:2046: rang gri thong gshol dgra s+t+wa la sogs bsnams //
NK019(dza)007:2047: sbrul dang thod phreng glang chen ko rlon dang //
NK019(dza)007:2048: zhing chen g.yang gzhi stag lpags sham thabs dang //
NK019(dza)007:2049: thal chen zhag dang rak+ta'i thig les brgyan //
NK019(dza)007:2050: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs //
NK019(dza)007:2051: gnas yul khro mo bcu drug brjid pa'i tshul //
NK019(dza)007:2052: phyag rgya'i khro mo bzhi yis sgo bzhi bsrung //
NK019(dza)007:2053: spor ma brgyad dang dbang mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK019(dza)007:2054: rang rang stan dang lag cha sna tshogs thogs //
NK019(dza)007:2055: ci bgyi zhes gsol chas te gnas par gyur //
NK019(dza)007:2056: de ltar rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas //
NK019(dza)007:2057: d+aa ki ma sring king dang pho nyar bcas //
NK019(dza)007:2058: snang srid thams cad 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK019(dza)007:2059: phyogs bcu rgyal ba'i 'khor lor sangs rgyas nas //
NK019(dza)007:2060: 'jigs byed chen po'i dkyil 'khor bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK019(dza)007:2061: skad cig gcig la bde gshegs skur ston la //
NK019(dza)007:2062: byin rlabs mchog dang ldan par mdzad du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2063: zhes dkyil 'khor sgyur zhing gsal gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:2068: bdud rtsi rlob cing gsang gtor rnams dang /
NK019(dza)007:2070: rten dang brten pa bskyed cing bskur rlob sngon du btang nas /
NK019(dza)007:2071: zhal byang gyer ba'i mjug tu /
NK019(dza)007:2074: sman rkyang sgrub bam yang na /
NK019(dza)007:2075: lung gi zhi ba gzhung bsrangs rjes /
NK019(dza)007:2076: khro bo 'di nyid kyis khog dbub pa'i dbang du mdzad par snang la /
NK019(dza)007:2077: des na yi ge'i rgyun mi nub pa'i phyir lugs
NK019(dza)007:2078: de'i chog khrigs kyang zur 'debs su 'dri bar bya
NK019(dza)007:2079: zhing / 'dir lung gi zhi khro bzlas pa'i bar gzhung bsrangs nas /
NK019(dza)007:2080: skabs 'dir khro dkyil gyi snying po'i dkyil 'khor zhal
NK019(dza)007:2081: bsgyur ba tsam yin pas cho ga'i spros pa gzhan
NK019(dza)007:2084: rang gi thugs ka'i sngags phreng las byung ba'i 'od zer dang /
NK019(dza)007:2085: mtheb srin rta mgrin yab yum du mnyam par rol
NK019(dza)007:2086: pa'i byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gzungs thag rdo
NK019(dza)007:2087: rje lu gu rgyud kyi khong gseng nas song ba
NK019(dza)007:2088: bdud rtsi'i pho brang la phog /
NK019(dza)007:2089: des bdud rtsi sbyangs bzhu sbar ba'i rlangs pas dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs thams cad thugs rgyud bskul /
NK019(dza)007:2090: rjes chags kyis rol pa'i byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK019(dza)007:2091: zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas 'khor 'das kyi bdud rtsi
NK019(dza)007:2093: yab yum dgyes par rol pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK019(dza)007:2094: rgyun babs pa dang lhan cig bdud rtsi la thim
NK019(dza)007:2095: pas zhu zhing 'dres nas ye shes kyi bdud rtsi'i
NK019(dza)007:2097: rdzogs pa'i ye shes rmad po che //
NK019(dza)007:2098: zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen dbang //
NK019(dza)007:2099: shar gyi phyogs su kha bltas nas //
NK019(dza)007:2101: mchod khang yid bzhin rin po che //
NK019(dza)007:2103: phar 'phros pas ni thugs dam bskul //
NK019(dza)007:2104: slar 'dus pas ni dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2105: 'di yang bsnyen pa'i mchog yin te //
NK019(dza)007:2106: nam yang nyams pa'i dus mtha' med //
NK019(dza)007:2107: dug gsum dbyings su sbyong bar mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:2109: g.yon pa'i mtheb srin gyis gzungs thag la 'jus te /
NK019(dza)007:2110: gu h+ya bco lnga pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:2111: ru lu 'bru brgyad pa gnyis gtso bor bzla /
NK019(dza)007:2112: mjug tu badz+ra a mri ta +aahh+aum h+r+aihsh+thazhesa pa'ang cung zad bzlas la /
NK019(dza)007:2114: bstod bshags dzapa khang bsdu ba gsum dang /
NK019(dza)007:2115: tshogs mchod rnams sgrub thabs ltar bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:2116: 'di ni cho ga rgyas pa'i khrigs te /
NK019(dza)007:2119: dbye gzhi'i dkyil 'khor skad cig gis gsal btab nas dzapa khang phye la /
NK019(dza)007:2120: zhi ba rigs drug gi sngags dang /
NK019(dza)007:2121: khro bo che mchog dang rgyud lung gi he ru
NK019(dza)007:2122: ka bcu gcig gi sngags la ru lu sbrel ba
NK019(dza)007:2124: sgo gsum lha sngags 'od gsal gyis rgyas btab nas
NK019(dza)007:2125: gtso bor spyi sngags gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na la dril
NK019(dza)007:2126: nas bzlas rjes dzapa khang bsdus la tshogs mchod dbul
NK019(dza)007:2127: / tho rengs khams gsum dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lor gsal btab la /
NK019(dza)007:2130: thun mong du gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na la dril zhing tshogs dbul /
NK019(dza)007:2131: nam langs pa dang las mkhan gyis lhag gtor bsngosa la gtor ma ske tshang du bsag go //
NK019(dza)007:2132: de nas nyin mo'i cho ga la /
NK019(dza)007:2133: snga dro cho ga 'bring po ste /
NK019(dza)007:2134: gral phyag nas bzung dzapa khang dbye ba'i bar sgrub thabs ltar las /
NK019(dza)007:2135: byin 'bebs kyi rjes su rtags gsum gdab /
NK019(dza)007:2136: dzapa la zhi ba la rigs drug dang /
NK019(dza)007:2140: he ru ka dgu rnams dang ru lu /
NK019(dza)007:2141: zhi khro thun mong du guh+ya dz+ny+aa na bzla zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2142: spro na dzapa dbyangs dang bcas te dzapa bskor yang byas la /
NK019(dza)007:2144: slar yang phata dzahs bum pa'i dkyil 'khor logs su phye nas mdun gyi nam mkhar bzhugs pa la /
NK019(dza)007:2146: sta gon ltar dzapa dmigs gsal btab nas gu h+ya
NK019(dza)007:2147: dz+ny+aa na ci 'grub bzlas la 'od zhu bya zhing
NK019(dza)007:2151: khro bcu'i sngags kyis mtshams bcad /
NK019(dza)007:2152: ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK019(dza)007:2153: kun tu bzang pos dam bca' /
NK019(dza)007:2155: mchod pa rnams kyang sngags kyis rlob /
NK019(dza)007:2156: rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor yang so so'i bskyed sngags brjod pa tsam gyis gsal btab la /
NK019(dza)007:2160: sman gtor rak+ta rnams sngags mchod tsam gyis phul /
NK019(dza)007:2161: zhi khro so so la bo d+hi tsit+ta dang ru lu'i dzapa dang /
NK019(dza)007:2162: spyir gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bzlas la /
NK019(dza)007:2163: brjod med shes rab kyis bstod /
NK019(dza)007:2164: tshogs bsang sbyangs 'bru gsum gyi brlabs la /
NK019(dza)007:2165: drang mchod bshags stob thams cad sngags tsam gyis bya zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2166: 'di ni chung ngu'i las khrigs te /
NK019(dza)007:2167: lung tshig gis gsal gdab pa dang na mo h+aum gis gzi byin bskyed pa'ang mi mdzad do //
NK019(dza)007:2168: de dag ni dkyil 'khor zhag gi cho ga ste /
NK019(dza)007:2169: sgrub pa zhag grangs du byed kyang de ltar bya ba yin no //
NK019(dza)007:2170: de ltar thun drug tu byed pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:2171: bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las thor //
NK019(dza)007:2172: zhi khro las rim gzhung bsrangs bskyed //
NK019(dza)007:2173: spyan drangs mchod bstod sbyin sreg dbul //
NK019(dza)007:2174: bzlas dang bsnyen sgrub tshogs mchod bya //
NK019(dza)007:2175: zhag bdun dus drug rdzogs pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:2176: zhes gsungs pa'i dgongs pa yin pas ci 'grub bya dgos mod /
NK019(dza)007:2178: gung gnyis dor nas thun bzhir bsdu zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2179: de ltar gyi tshe phyi dro yang chog khrigs 'bring po dang /
NK019(dza)007:2180: tho rengs chung ba la brten na legs so //
NK019(dza)007:2181: sbyin sreg ni thun thams cad la gsungs kyang 'grub
NK019(dza)007:2182: dka' bas phyi nang gi sbyin sreg tshogs la rol
NK019(dza)007:2183: ba tsam gyis sa khongs bzung /
NK019(dza)007:2184: rab gnas dgos na de'i tshe rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg 'byung mod /
NK019(dza)007:2185: mi dgos na sgrub pa'i de'i khongs su nyin gung
NK019(dza)007:2186: gi dus gnad dang bstun la phrin las thung ba
NK019(dza)007:2187: dang sbrel nas rgyas pa'i sbyin sreg lan gcig nges
NK019(dza)007:2188: par bya / gtor ma btang ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:2189: dgong thun gyi mjug tu las mkhan gyis cha gsum 'go'i 'das gtor dang /
NK019(dza)007:2190: legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po sogs srung ma rnams kyi gtor chog /
NK019(dza)007:2191: 'jig rten pa'i cha gsum gtor ma rnams gtong /
NK019(dza)007:2193: 'gos kyi las thor thun thams cad la bya bar bshad na'ang 'grub dka' bas /
NK019(dza)007:2194: thun gang rung gcig dang sbrel nas /
NK019(dza)007:2195: sngar tshe bsham pa'i dus kyi dmigs pa de nyid gsal btab la /
NK019(dza)007:2196: b+h+r+aum badz+ra +aa yu she h+aum ah zhes brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas la /
NK019(dza)007:2197: h+r+aih nub phyogs pad+ma dbang gi gzhal yas nas //
NK019(dza)007:2198: bcom ldan rigs lnga yab yum tshe dpag med //
NK019(dza)007:2199: sems dpa' sems ma sgo mar bcas rnams kyis //
NK019(dza)007:2200: tshe dang ye shes dgug pa'i las mdzod cig /
NK019(dza)007:2201: n+ri b+h+r+aum h+aum +aa yu she dzahdzahh+aum a /
NK019(dza)007:2203: de nas dbang bskur ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:2204: +aam badz+ra +aa yu she a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:2205: badz+ra +aa yu she s+w+aa badz+ra +aa yu she h+aum
NK019(dza)007:2206: badz+ra +aa yu she h+aa badz+ra a yu she a
NK019(dza)007:2207: b+hi shiny+tsa h+aum / zhes tshe 'brang g.yas bskor du spyi bor bzhag cing /
NK019(dza)007:2208: tshe chang g.yon bskor du 'thung du bcug pas snying
NK019(dza)007:2209: ga'i tshe rten la bstim pa'i mthar zung 'jug 'chi
NK019(dza)007:2210: med gnyug ma'i ngang la dar gcig mnyam par bzhag
NK019(dza)007:2211: pas tshe sba zhing rgyas gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:2213: dus drug las phreng tshogs mchod snyeg /
NK019(dza)007:2214: dus drug bskang gso'i cho ga bya //
NK019(dza)007:2215: dus drug bar gcod nyul le bzlog /
NK019(dza)007:2217: sngar las khrigs su bshad ma thag pa ltar thun thams cad la ci 'grub bya zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2218: gal te mi 'grub na srod thun dang zhog thun gyi mthar bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:2219: gang ltar kyang lhag ma rnams bsdus pa nang par
NK019(dza)007:2220: lhag chog gcig gis bsngosa nas sgrub pa ma grol
NK019(dza)007:2221: bar ske tshang du bsag pa phyag len no //
NK019(dza)007:2224: sman gtor rak+ta mar me lnga'i skongs dag gyur dang
NK019(dza)007:2225: bcas pa dong sprugs ltar thun thams cad la ma
NK019(dza)007:2226: 'byor yang nyin zhag gi khongs su lan re bya'o
NK019(dza)007:2229: bar chad byed pa'i bgegs chen yang //
NK019(dza)007:2230: 'jigs pa med pa'i sems kyis bzlog /
NK019(dza)007:2231: dngos grub sbyin pa'i gzungs can yang //
NK019(dza)007:2232: re dang dogs dang dga' ba yi //
NK019(dza)007:2233: ngan pa'i don gyis sems mi dbyung //
NK019(dza)007:2234: zhes pas spyir re dogs kyi snyems bcad nas ci yong ba shog /
NK019(dza)007:2235: gang dga' ba gyis snyam du thag bcad par bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:2236: bye brag dus drug gi nyul le ngos bzung nas rang rang gi gnyen pos bzlog pa'i thabs ni /
NK019(dza)007:2237: galpo'i brtag pa bco lnga pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:2238: bka' brgyad kyi dus kyi bsnyen pa'i sgrub khog sogs las shes par bya zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2239: 'dir ni spyi tsam du nyul le'i ling+ga bcas la brub khung du bcug /
NK019(dza)007:2241: brub khung yangs shing gting zab pa'i nang du tri
NK019(dza)007:2242: las dngos grub la bar du gcod cing log par
NK019(dza)007:2243: 'dren pa'i 'byung po nyams len bdud kyi rigs su
NK019(dza)007:2244: gyur pa thams cad 'dus pa'i ngo bo rid cing
NK019(dza)007:2245: nyam thag pa'i lus can du gyur /
NK019(dza)007:2248: dngos grub la bar du gcod cing nas /
NK019(dza)007:2249: bdud kyi rigs su gyur pa thams cad mtshan ma rdzas kyi rten 'di la mchis par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:2250: tri yam dzah tri badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah dzahh+aum bam hohs dgug bstim byas la /
NK019(dza)007:2251: byug bdug brab gsum gyis gzi byin bskyed pa'i phur
NK019(dza)007:2252: bu stong pa'i ngang las h+aum las byung ba'i sras
NK019(dza)007:2254: e yi tshogs kyi sogs tshigs bcad gnyis kyi mthar
NK019(dza)007:2255: ru lu'i sham bur sarba big+h+n+aana dush+t+aana m+aa ra ya
NK019(dza)007:2257: thun dang mtshon cha'i char dbab /
NK019(dza)007:2258: de ni gnas skabs kyis bzlog pa zhes bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:2259: yang shin tu gal che na bde gshegs spyi dril gyis bsrung zhing bzlog par bya ste /
NK019(dza)007:2260: sngags pa drag po'i chas su zhugs la /
NK019(dza)007:2261: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:2263: bdag nyid dpal chen po che mchog he ru ka
NK019(dza)007:2264: 'jigs shing rngams pa'i skur bskyed pa'i spyi bor gshin
NK019(dza)007:2265: rje gshed dkar po 'khor lo dang sdigs mdzub /
NK019(dza)007:2266: mgrin par rta mgrin dmar po sbrul zhags dang sdigs mdzub /
NK019(dza)007:2267: snying gar badz+ra he ru ka mthing ga rdor dril /
NK019(dza)007:2268: lte bar rdo rje gzhon nu ljang khu phur bu dang sdigs mdzub /
NK019(dza)007:2269: de thams cad kyi sku las rdo rje mtshon cha'i
NK019(dza)007:2270: char dang bskal pa'i me'i tsh+wa tsh+wa rnon po 'bar
NK019(dza)007:2271: zhing 'khrug pas bgegs thams cad bsregs bcom bskrad par
NK019(dza)007:2272: bsam zhing / rdo rje srin po'i ngur sgras /
NK019(dza)007:2273: pad+ma kro d+h+ai shwa r+ai badz+ra k+ai la ya ma
NK019(dza)007:2274: h+aa yak+sha karma ram ram badz+ra dz+wa la ram ram
NK019(dza)007:2275: h+aum phata / ces drag tu bzla zhing spos rol dang thun brab kyis tsham rngams bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:2276: de ltar nyul le 'dul ba thun thams cad kyi
NK019(dza)007:2277: mtha' 'am mi nus na thun tha ma kho na'i
NK019(dza)007:2278: rjes su lan re nges par bya zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2279: gang ltar kyang dus der dngos grub ster ba'i pho
NK019(dza)007:2280: nya re'ang 'ong bas nyul le bskrad pa'i rjes de
NK019(dza)007:2281: ma thag tu byin 'bebs kyang bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:2282: khyad par bzlas brjod thun drug gam bzhi'i dus su
NK019(dza)007:2283: byed par ma zad bsnyen grogs yod na gsung mi
NK019(dza)007:2284: chag par khor yug tu bzlar 'jug cing /
NK019(dza)007:2285: lcogs na spyi sngags kyi sngags rgyun dang /
NK019(dza)007:2286: gzhan zhig gis bdud rtsi bde ba chen po'i dkyil
NK019(dza)007:2287: 'khor du sgyur nas gzungs thag la 'jus te sman
NK019(dza)007:2288: dzapa kyang gsung mi chag tu 'grub na legs so
NK019(dza)007:2289: // gal te mtshan bcas spros pa'i cho gas ngal
NK019(dza)007:2290: zhing dub pa'i dus su mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs
NK019(dza)007:2291: rim gyi don nyams su blang zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2292: mdor na gnas skabs kun tu lha sngags 'od gsal
NK019(dza)007:2293: gyi 'khor los byed spyod thams cad la rgyas gdab
NK019(dza)007:2294: par bya'o // de yan chad ni sgrub pa'i yan lag go //
NK019(dza)007:2295: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po'i yan lag ni /
NK019(dza)007:2296: smin slob la grub pa'i rtags mtshan yid ches par byung ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:2297: nub tha ma dngos grub blang bar bya ba yin mod /
NK019(dza)007:2298: 'dir mos slob zhag bcu gcig pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK019(dza)007:2300: smyal pa zhag bcu 'gro ba'i dgong mo nas 'go
NK019(dza)007:2301: 'dzin par mdzad na'ang lag len la mi bde bas
NK019(dza)007:2302: / 'dir glan rdo rje 'od kyi phyag bzhes 'gos
NK019(dza)007:2303: kyi las tho ltar zhag dgu 'gro ba'i dgong thun
NK019(dza)007:2304: la phrin las thung ba dang sbrel nas dbang gi
NK019(dza)007:2305: / sbyin sreg bya / de nas rtsa rgyud las /
NK019(dza)007:2306: rmad byung sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK019(dza)007:2307: 'jug dang dngos grub gsol ba dang //
NK019(dza)007:2308: dbang bskur ba yi las rnams bya //
NK019(dza)007:2309: zhes pa'i don rin chen phreng bar /
NK019(dza)007:2310: slob ma dkyil 'khor du bcug nas dngos grub blang /
NK019(dza)007:2311: de nas dbang bskur mdzad pa ni cung zad rtsings pa ste /
NK019(dza)007:2312: 'dir 'jug dang dngos grub gsol ba dang //
NK019(dza)007:2313: zhes pa'i 'jug pa ni slob dpon bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas dngos grub blangs la /
NK019(dza)007:2314: gzod slob ma dkyil 'khor du bcug ste dbang bskur ba la dgongs pa yin gyi /
NK019(dza)007:2315: slob ma dkyil 'khor du bcug nas dngos grub len pa'i don ma yin no //
NK019(dza)007:2316: de ltar yang bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las thor /
NK019(dza)007:2317: zhag bdun tha mar slob dpon 'jug /
NK019(dza)007:2318: dngos grub rnam bzhi rim gyis blangs //
NK019(dza)007:2320: des na rgyud dang man ngag gi dgongs pa'i gnad ni /
NK019(dza)007:2321: bsgrub pa'i rtags mtshan ci rigs pa mthong nas slob dpon dkyil 'khor du zhugs la /
NK019(dza)007:2322: bdag nyid tshom bu'i 'khor dang bcas te rang don du dngos grub blangs rjes /
NK019(dza)007:2323: gzhan don slob mar dbang bskur ba'i phrin las la sbyar bar bya ba yin pa'i phyir /
NK019(dza)007:2324: tshom bur 'brel ba'i ston 'khor mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK019(dza)007:2325: pas smin slob kyi sgrub chen la 'jug na lta
NK019(dza)007:2326: ci smos / gzhan du ston 'khor cha 'dra 'dus
NK019(dza)007:2327: pas mos slob sgrub pa'i zhag grangs khrigs bcad ma
NK019(dza)007:2328: bdun yan chad tsam byed kyang rung ste /
NK019(dza)007:2329: de dang de'i tshe gzhung bzhin bya ba legs mod /
NK019(dza)007:2330: 'on kyang da lta'i dus su sgrub pa'i phyag bzhes
NK019(dza)007:2331: ston pa'i ched du dbang zhu mi rnams kyang sgrub
NK019(dza)007:2332: chen gyi khongs su 'du ba'i phyag len ltar na
NK019(dza)007:2333: / sngar 'di nyid kyi dkyil 'khor du dbang ma thob par ma zad /
NK019(dza)007:2334: rigs mthun bla med rgyud lung gzhan gyi dbang yang
NK019(dza)007:2335: ma thob pa'i slob bu gsar pa 'byung srid pas
NK019(dza)007:2336: / de dag kyang grub pa'i 'bras bu dngos grub
NK019(dza)007:2337: len pa'i spyod pa rmad du byung ba la 'jug
NK019(dza)007:2338: rung gi skal pa can du sgrub pa'i phyir /
NK019(dza)007:2339: mos slob kyi'ang 'dra 'bag lta bu'i skabs 'dir dbang
NK019(dza)007:2340: skur byas zin pa'i rjes su dngos grub len pa'i
NK019(dza)007:2341: lugs lag len la bde bas /
NK019(dza)007:2343: dbang gi sbyin sreg grub rjes dgong thun gyi 'phros kyi gtor chog dang /
NK019(dza)007:2344: srod thun dang gung thun sngar ltar bya /
NK019(dza)007:2345: thor thun la las gzhung 'bring po bsrangs nas bum bzlas 'od zhu'i bar grub rjes /
NK019(dza)007:2346: tshogs byin rlabs nas tha ma stob pa'i bar dkyus ltar dang /
NK019(dza)007:2347: tshogs la rol ba dbang gi mthar mdzad pa phyag len yin pas bzhag la /
NK019(dza)007:2348: nangs par zhag bcu pa'i nyi ma shar khar dbang
NK019(dza)007:2349: chog ltar slob dpon bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du 'jug
NK019(dza)007:2350: pa'i cho ga rgyas bsdus ji ltar ri gas pa
NK019(dza)007:2351: dang / slob ma 'jug par gnang ba zhu zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2352: dgongs pa bskul ba'i glu blang ba rnams sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)007:2353: slob ma dkyil du bcug nas phyi nang sgrub gsang
NK019(dza)007:2354: bzhis bsdus pa'i dbang sum cu rtsa drug bskur ba'i
NK019(dza)007:2356: lhag chog dang gtor chog rnams bya ste /
NK019(dza)007:2357: de yan nyin mo tshar na /
NK019(dza)007:2358: nub mo yan lag gi dkyil 'khor du gsang dbang
NK019(dza)007:2359: sher dbang ste kun rdzob byang sems kya zab dbang
NK019(dza)007:2360: gnyis bskur ba dus gnad dang 'brel la /
NK019(dza)007:2361: gal te rtsa dbang nyin mo ma zin pa'am rang dgos kyi gshoms bkod sogs ma grub na /
NK019(dza)007:2362: de nub mtshan mo'i thun gyi cho ga'i babs sngar ltar las /
NK019(dza)007:2363: srod thun la chog khrigs rgyas pa ma grub na
NK019(dza)007:2364: bsdus pas gzhung bsrangs nas bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor du
NK019(dza)007:2365: bsgyur ba sogs bya ba yin no //
NK019(dza)007:2366: de nas zhag bcu gcig pa'i snga dro rtsa ba'i
NK019(dza)007:2367: dkyil 'khor gyi mdun lta bu ci bder yan lag
NK019(dza)007:2368: gi dkyil 'khor rnams sgrub thabs ltar bshams sgrub tshar
NK019(dza)007:2369: ba dang / dbang chog ltar byang sems rnam gnyis kyi gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo gnyis sam /
NK019(dza)007:2370: nub mo kun rdzob byang sems kyi dbang song na 'dir don dam byang sems kyi dbang dang /
NK019(dza)007:2371: skabs su bab na gtad rgya'ang byas rjes /
NK019(dza)007:2372: mtha' rten gyi tshe'i dbang bskur zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2373: so so'i rjes chog rnams kyang sgrub thabs bzhin bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:2374: de nas dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:2375: phyi dro dkyil 'khor gyi mdun ngos su stegs ji
NK019(dza)007:2376: ltar rigs pa la 'bras s+aa lu'i phyes rdo rje
NK019(dza)007:2377: rgya gram bris pa'i steng du dngos grub kyi rdzas
NK019(dza)007:2379: de'ang sngar dkyil 'khor gyi mthar bkod pa'i dngos grub kyi rdzas rnams phab la /
NK019(dza)007:2380: stegs kyi dbus many+dzi nyis gshibs kyi g.yas par gsal
NK019(dza)007:2381: shing rim pa bcu bzhi btsugs pa'i 'brang rgyas zla
NK019(dza)007:2382: gam dang / g.yon par gsol byang gi sman thod bkod /
NK019(dza)007:2383: de dag gi phyi'i shar du dpal bshos nyi zla kha sbyor /
NK019(dza)007:2385: nub tu dbang bshos zla gam /
NK019(dza)007:2386: byang du dza gad kyi snod rnams dang /
NK019(dza)007:2387: gzhan yang rdo rje tshe ste zan /
NK019(dza)007:2389: dza gad dam dpa' byed de chang //
NK019(dza)007:2390: 'jam des sam zla ba dkar ba de mar /
NK019(dza)007:2391: zla rgyas te zho dang khur ba /
NK019(dza)007:2392: zla khrom ste thud dang khrum /
NK019(dza)007:2393: gal phyis te spod sna tshogs kyi g.yos /
NK019(dza)007:2398: sham mo ste sing po sogs bza' bca' btung ba'i
NK019(dza)007:2399: bye brag tshogs tshad gsar du'ang 'du byas pas mtha'
NK019(dza)007:2400: bskor du gcer / de rnams kyi steng nas shing
NK019(dza)007:2401: sgroms la brten pa'i dar ram ras dkar rdo rje
NK019(dza)007:2403: dkyil 'khor gyi lding khri bar pa la mar me dgu bkod yod na /
NK019(dza)007:2404: che mchog gnyis dang rgyud lung khro bo'i mar me gsum des go chod /
NK019(dza)007:2405: lnga yod na gtso bo dang rgyud kyi khro bo /
NK019(dza)007:2406: gcig las med na che mchog /
NK019(dza)007:2407: dbang mchog badz+ra he ru ka ste /
NK019(dza)007:2408: gang ltar yang de rnams spar /
NK019(dza)007:2409: phyi ma'i dbang du byas na /
NK019(dza)007:2413: phra men phan chad khyams dgu dang //
NK019(dza)007:2414: khor yug rig 'dzin rnams kyi gnas su mar me re re ste khyon bcu bzhi bkod /
NK019(dza)007:2415: yang ras bris chung ngu lta bu la brten te
NK019(dza)007:2416: lha gnas so sor bkod mi thub na bcu bzhi
NK019(dza)007:2417: po thams cad lding khri bar pa'am dkyil 'khor gyi
NK019(dza)007:2418: phyi rol du bkod pa las 'os med do //
NK019(dza)007:2419: de nas sgrub pa po rnams rgyan gos bzang po bstar la /
NK019(dza)007:2420: las kyi dbu drang ba nas bzung bum dzapa dor
NK019(dza)007:2421: ba ma gtogs gzhan las khrigs 'bring po ltar zhi
NK019(dza)007:2422: khro'i gzhung tshogs tha ma'i bar bsrangs la /
NK019(dza)007:2423: de nas dngos grub len pa la 'jug ste /
NK019(dza)007:2425: 'byung po lta nyan tshar gcod pa'i phyir khro bcu'i sngags kyis mtshams bcad /
NK019(dza)007:2426: lha dang 'khon gcugs sbyong ba'i phyir ye nas mnyam nyid kyis bshags /
NK019(dza)007:2428: kun tu bzang po bla na med pa yi //
NK019(dza)007:2430: rang nyid gzi byin bskyed phyir bab drug 'das bzhis byin dbab /
NK019(dza)007:2431: dngos grub kyi rdzas dpal bshos /
NK019(dza)007:2433: zla gam bza' btung gi longs spyod dang bcas pa /
NK019(dza)007:2434: gsol byang thabs shes kyi tshe rdzas rnams dkyil 'khor
NK019(dza)007:2435: la 'god dus kyi so so'i dgongs pa gsal btab
NK019(dza)007:2436: nas / dang po gsum la gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i sham bur /
NK019(dza)007:2440: tshe rdzas la b+h+r+aum badz+ra +aahyu she h+aum +aah zhes
NK019(dza)007:2441: pa rnams bdun bdun bzlas pas rdzas rnams nus ldan
NK019(dza)007:2445: dngos grub rnam bzhi rim gyis blang //
NK019(dza)007:2446: dzapa bskor dang pos thugs dam bskul //
NK019(dza)007:2447: bar du sbyin sreg mchod pa bya //
NK019(dza)007:2448: tha ma gnad la dbab pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:2449: gshegs shing gsol byang bstim par bya //
NK019(dza)007:2451: dang po dzapa kyis thugs dam bskul ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:2452: dkyil mchog ltar dzapa khang dbye ba'i cho gas mdun bskyed ye shes pa'i ngo bor phye la /
NK019(dza)007:2454: lha tshogs rnams kyi gnas gsum nas sku gsung thugs
NK019(dza)007:2455: kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub thams cad 'od dang
NK019(dza)007:2456: 'od zer gyi rnam par rang rang dang dngos grub
NK019(dza)007:2457: kyi rdzas rnams la thim par bsam zhing /
NK019(dza)007:2460: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na rnams bazla'o //
NK019(dza)007:2462: bsgrub bya'i dngos grub 'phel zhing rgyas pa'am dbang du
NK019(dza)007:2463: bya ba'i phyir rgyas pa dang dbang gi sbyin sreg
NK019(dza)007:2464: gang rigs byed par bshad pa ltar lag len bde
NK019(dza)007:2466: gsum pa gnad la dbab ste bskul ba la /
NK019(dza)007:2468: dngos grub bskul ba'i rim pa rnams //
NK019(dza)007:2469: spyir bskul ba dang gnad nas bskul //
NK019(dza)007:2470: nye bar bskul ba'i rim pa yin //
NK019(dza)007:2472: dang po lha tshogs thams cad rigs lngar bsdus nas spyir bskul ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:2473: spos btul zhing rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas /
NK019(dza)007:2475: nga ni dpal ldan rdo rje 'chang //
NK019(dza)007:2476: thugs kyi 'khor lo rab bskor zhing //
NK019(dza)007:2478: nyid kyi bka' bzhin spyan 'dren na //

NK019(dza)007:2480: dam tshig tshul bzhin mi gshegs na //
NK019(dza)007:2481: grub mchog dngos grub mi stsol na //
NK019(dza)007:2482: sku gsung thugs dang 'gal bar mchi //
NK019(dza)007:2483: dam tshig mchog la dgongs nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:2484: thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //

NK019(dza)007:2528: las kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2530: gnyis pa dngos grub kyi snod rung du chags sgribs
NK019(dza)007:2531: med par sal ler gzigs pa'i phyir da ni dngos
NK019(dza)007:2532: grub stsol ba'i dus la bab bo zhes gnad nas
NK019(dza)007:2534: nam mkha'i mtha' klas chos kyi dbyings kyis khyab //
NK019(dza)007:2535: ma chags spyan mnga' ma bsgrib ye shes gsal //
NK019(dza)007:2536: kun nas kun tu dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2537: rdo rje'i zhag kyang tshang lags so //
NK019(dza)007:2538: bzlas brjod grangs kyang thems lags so //
NK019(dza)007:2539: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus 'di lags //
NK019(dza)007:2540: 'gro ba mang po bdag gis sgrol //
NK019(dza)007:2541: bla med byang chub bdag gis sgrub //
NK019(dza)007:2542: mthu chen mthu stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK019(dza)007:2543: dngos grub mchog stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK019(dza)007:2544: bdag gi las 'bras mchis par mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:2545: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum //
NK019(dza)007:2546: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK019(dza)007:2547: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK019(dza)007:2548: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK019(dza)007:2549: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2550: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:2552: gsum pa nye bar bskul ba la /
NK019(dza)007:2554: stsol ba po lha'i rkang thon nas bskul pa gnyis las /
NK019(dza)007:2557: mnyam pa'i don la ma skyes gnyis med phyir //
NK019(dza)007:2558: dngos grub stsol dang gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK019(dza)007:2559: rig dang ma rig sgyu ma'i khyad par gyis //
NK019(dza)007:2560: sgyu ma'i spyod yul mnyam par ma grub cing //
NK019(dza)007:2561: rgyal ba'i dgongs spyod klong du ma gyur pas //
NK019(dza)007:2562: log rtog srid pa'i zhen pa ma bzlog na //
NK019(dza)007:2563: mkhyen rab ting 'dzin dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2564: chags pa'i nad kyis gdungs pa'i sdug bsngal la //
NK019(dza)007:2565: bdud dang srin po zhe sdang glo bur gyis //
NK019(dza)007:2566: sgyu ma'i lus srog tshe la bar gcod na //
NK019(dza)007:2567: khro rgyal mthu yis zil gyis gnon pa'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:2568: rdzu 'phrul lam mchog dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2569: gsung rab rgya mtsho bdud rtsi'i char phab tshe //
NK019(dza)007:2570: bag chags skyon gyi dri mas rmongs pa las //
NK019(dza)007:2571: shes shing rtogs pa'i shes rab mi ldan na //
NK019(dza)007:2572: shes byar thogs med dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2573: 'bad pas btsal ba'i dus gsum dge bshes de //
NK019(dza)007:2574: srid la phan 'dogs ston pa'i dpal mgon las //
NK019(dza)007:2575: drin la lan ldon gang lags ma 'tshal na //
NK019(dza)007:2576: sems kyi mngon shes dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2577: rnam rtog zhen pa'i bag chags stug po yis //
NK019(dza)007:2578: dus gsum chos rnams mun pa'i rdzas ltar sgribs //
NK019(dza)007:2579: dus gsum dge bshes drin la lan slan phyir //
NK019(dza)007:2580: dus la rmongs pa'i sems can don bgyid na //
NK019(dza)007:2581: mngon shes drug gi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2582: rgyud drug rim gyis drang pa'i don slad du //
NK019(dza)007:2583: khams gsum ma lus khyab par 'gro ba'i tshe //
NK019(dza)007:2584: sems kyi gdos su bdag gi lus mchis na //
NK019(dza)007:2585: thogs med rkang mgyogs dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2586: dregs pas myos pa'i bar snang lha bran dang //
NK019(dza)007:2587: che bas 'gying ba'i mkha' 'gro mang po'i tshogs //
NK019(dza)007:2588: rdo rje'i gshog pas zil gyis gnon pa'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:2589: nam mkhar thogs med dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2590: log rtog mang pos shes rgyud g.yengs pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:2591: ston pas gsungs pa'i bka' brgyud ji snyed pa //
NK019(dza)007:2592: don dang yi ge brjod med ma bsam na //
NK019(dza)007:2593: mi brjed gzungs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2594: rang nyid rnam rtog las kyi dbang gyur cing //
NK019(dza)007:2595: sdug bsngal mang pos bcings pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
NK019(dza)007:2596: 'dul thabs mang pos 'gro ba'i don bgyid kyi //
NK019(dza)007:2597: rnam bzhi las kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2598: rang gi rnam rtog las kyi dbang gyur cing //
NK019(dza)007:2599: blang dor med pa'i don la thugs brtse'i phyir //
NK019(dza)007:2600: so so'i blo la ji ltar 'thad pa bzhin //
NK019(dza)007:2601: mthun 'jug thabs kyis 'gro ba 'dul lags kyis //
NK019(dza)007:2602: pra se na yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2603: dug gsum zhen pas 'khor ba'i gcong btab na //
NK019(dza)007:2604: 'tsho byed sman pa'i rgyal pos bcos su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2605: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub dam pa ste //
NK019(dza)007:2606: dngos grub rdzas la brten nas bdag la stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2607: skya rengs dang po'i dngos grub dus la bab //
NK019(dza)007:2608: khrag 'thung 'khor bcas dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2609: khams gsum dregs pa ma lus 'dus 'tshal gyis //
NK019(dza)007:2610: bcom ldan dpal chen dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2611: ye shes thabs kyis 'gro don kun bgyid kyi //
NK019(dza)007:2612: khro mo brgyad kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2613: dur khrod rol pas khams gsum dbang sdud kyi //
NK019(dza)007:2614: phra men brgyad kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2615: phrin las rnam bzhi 'gro ba'i don bgyid kyi //
NK019(dza)007:2616: khro bo bcu yi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2617: sprul pa mang pos sems can kun 'dul phyir //
NK019(dza)007:2618: yang sprul nying sprul dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2619: ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:2621: chos nyid bde ba chen po'i skur byung ba //
NK019(dza)007:2622: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2623: dur khrod dregs pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK019(dza)007:2624: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2625: ye shes 'bar ba brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2626: goo r+ai khro mo brgyad kyis dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2627: chos nyid mkha' ltar dag pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2628: sing+ha phra men brgyad kyis dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2629: tshad med bzhi rdzogs gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2630: rta gdong sgo ma bzhi yis dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2631: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang shed nas //
NK019(dza)007:2632: spor ma gsang yum tshogs bcas dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2633: dam tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2634: dbang phyug ma sring tshogs kyis dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2635: dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2636: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2637: phrin las myur mgyogs chen po'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2638: ma bdun sring bzhi'i tshogs kyis dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2639: sgrol byed rab tu 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2640: rdo rje king chen bco brgyad dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2641: zhe sdang 'bar ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2642: khro rgyal yab yum drug cus dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2643: ci bgyi bka' nyan las kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2644: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcus dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2645: las rnams yongs su grub pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2646: ye shes ma mo drug cus dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2647: sdom pa'i sa la gnas pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK019(dza)007:2648: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang tshogs kyis dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2650: / gnas mchog yang dag don gyi 'og min nas //
NK019(dza)007:2651: rgyal ba kun bzang yab yum dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2652: 'og min dbang phyug chen po'i gnas mchog nas //
NK019(dza)007:2653: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK019(dza)007:2654: rdo rje sems dpa' rigs lnga yab yum bcas //
NK019(dza)007:2655: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2656: lha klu gnod sbyin so so'i gnas mchog nas //
NK019(dza)007:2657: bcom ldan rigs gsum mgon pos dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2658: rgyan d+ha na ko sha'i gling phug tu //
NK019(dza)007:2659: rdor sems sprul pa dga' rab rdo rje dang //
NK019(dza)007:2660: rgyal po'i bu mo rin chen gsal sgron mar //
NK019(dza)007:2661: rdo rje sems dang gsang bdag dngos byon nas //
NK019(dza)007:2662: dbang bzhi rdzogs bskur rtog tshogs lhar ngo sprod //
NK019(dza)007:2663: dbang rtags phyag shing me long rnams gnyis byin //
NK019(dza)007:2664: rig 'dzin khri phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK019(dza)007:2665: de yi dngos grub dam pa cha gcig kyang //
NK019(dza)007:2666: de ring gsang ba'i gnas mchog chen po 'dir //
NK019(dza)007:2667: sgrub mchog skal ldan bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2668: rgya gar yul yi pha rol na //
NK019(dza)007:2669: o rgyan yul gyi tshur mtshams na //
NK019(dza)007:2670: ma ga d+ha yi brag phug tu //
NK019(dza)007:2671: rgyal po d+harma k+aa ya dang //
NK019(dza)007:2672: klu yi bu mo rgya mtsho yis //
NK019(dza)007:2673: dga' rab rdo rje spyan drangs nas //
NK019(dza)007:2674: tshom bu stong gi dkyil 'khor sgrubs //
NK019(dza)007:2675: khri phrag gcig ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK019(dza)007:2676: de yi dngos grub cha gcig kyang //
NK019(dza)007:2677: de ring gsang ba'i gnas 'di ru //
NK019(dza)007:2678: sgrub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2679: rgya gar yul gyi mar mtshams na //
NK019(dza)007:2680: za hor yul gyi yar mtshams su //
NK019(dza)007:2682: rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi dang //
NK019(dza)007:2683: sras mo n+ai lan+d+ha ra yis //
NK019(dza)007:2684: tshom bu lnga brgya'i dkyil 'khor sgrubs //
NK019(dza)007:2685: khri phrag gcig ni sangs rgyas pa //
NK019(dza)007:2686: de yi dngos grub cha gcig kyang //
NK019(dza)007:2687: de ring gsang ba'i gnas 'di ru //
NK019(dza)007:2688: sgrub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2689: rgya gar yul gyi mar mtshams na //
NK019(dza)007:2690: sing g+ha la yi yar mtshams su //
NK019(dza)007:2691: g.yu mtsho gling dgu'i brag phug tu //
NK019(dza)007:2692: sing rgyal u pa r+aa dza dang //
NK019(dza)007:2693: sras mo go ma de w+ai yis //
NK019(dza)007:2694: tshom bu lnga bcu'i dkyil 'khor sgrubs //
NK019(dza)007:2695: brgya phrag du ma sangs rgyas pa //
NK019(dza)007:2696: de yis dngos grub cha gcig kyang //
NK019(dza)007:2697: de ring gsang ba'i gnas 'di ru //
NK019(dza)007:2698: sgrub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2699: rgya gar yul dbus ma g+ha d+ha //
NK019(dza)007:2700: w+aa r+aa na s+ai'i gnas dag tu //
NK019(dza)007:2701: dge slong nyin byed seng ge dang //
