NK019(dza)007:2972: sgrub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2973: spyi gtsug nyi zla'i gdan steng du //
NK019(dza)007:2974: rtsa ba'i bla ma bka' drin can //
NK019(dza)007:2975: rdo rje 'chang gi ngo bo nyid //
NK019(dza)007:2976: de yi dngos grub cha gcig kyang //
NK019(dza)007:2977: de ring gsang ba'i gnas 'di ru //
NK019(dza)007:2978: sgrub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK019(dza)007:2979: rtsa brgyud bla ma dam pa rnams //
NK019(dza)007:2981: byin rlabs dngos grub char ltar 'bebs //
NK019(dza)007:2982: gnas mchog 'di ru byin chen phob //
NK019(dza)007:2983: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:2984: zhes bskul zhing gsol ba gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:2985: bzhi pa gshegs shing gsol byang byas la bstim pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:2986: 'di ye shes lha'i dngos grub blang ba dngos yin /
NK019(dza)007:2987: de la lha rje 'gar gyi zhal nas /
NK019(dza)007:2988: yang dag gi dus min pa gsal shing gi cho ga la gnad che rgyu med /
NK019(dza)007:2989: ces gsal shing mi mdzad pas dmigs pa kho nas
NK019(dza)007:2990: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams las mar me gcig las
NK019(dza)007:2991: gnyis chad ltar mdun du gshegs su gsol ba la
NK019(dza)007:2992: mchod bstod bzlas pa gsol byang gi smon lam dang
NK019(dza)007:2993: bcas pa mdzad nas rang la bstim par bzhed /
NK019(dza)007:2999: zhes rgyud sde dang sgrub sde thams cad 'dus par ma zad /
NK019(dza)007:3000: khyad par lha dgu kun gyi rtsa ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3001: lha mang nga brgyad dang drug cu rtsa brgyad pa
NK019(dza)007:3002: sogs yang dag thams cad 'dir tshang bas gsal shing
NK019(dza)007:3003: las dngos grub len pa shin tu 'thad gsung /
NK019(dza)007:3005: zhi khro gnyis ka la len dgos par bzhed pa dang /
NK019(dza)007:3006: sregs rdo rje rgyal mtshan ni zhi khro sdeng 'og
NK019(dza)007:3007: 'od zer 'ju 'dul gyi tshul du yod pas zhi
NK019(dza)007:3008: ba la gsal shing gi cho ga mi dgos gsung
NK019(dza)007:3009: ba las / 'dir glan rdo rje 'od kyi phyag bzhes kyi rgyun la /
NK019(dza)007:3011: he ru ka 'dus pa sogs rdo rje rigs kyi
NK019(dza)007:3012: khro bo yang dag gi rgyud dang 'brel bas gsal
NK019(dza)007:3013: shing gi cho ga sbyar ba mi 'gal zhing /
NK019(dza)007:3014: de'ang sregs kyi rjes su 'brangs nas zhi bar gsal
NK019(dza)007:3015: shing gi cho ga mi dgos pa'i lugs phyag bzhes
NK019(dza)007:3016: su mdzad do // de la cho ga'i rim pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:3017: thog mar gang las blang ba'i gzhi sgrub pa spyi'i cho ga bya ste /
NK019(dza)007:3018: steng khang zhi ba'i lha tshogs kyi sku gsung thugs
NK019(dza)007:3019: kyi byin rlabs dang dngos grub kyi skal ba thams
NK019(dza)007:3020: cad 'od dang 'od zer gyi rnam pa can du
NK019(dza)007:3021: byung ba 'og khang khro bo'i lha tshogs rang rang
NK019(dza)007:3022: gi gnas gyur gang dang gang yin pa de dang
NK019(dza)007:3023: de la gnyis med du thim pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:3024: kun bzang gi 'od zer che mchog /
NK019(dza)007:3025: rigs lnga rgyud kyi he ru ka lnga /
NK019(dza)007:3028: bya byed dang thub drug 'bar ma /
NK019(dza)007:3029: mthar byed yab yum gyi 'od zer sgo skyong gdong
NK019(dza)007:3030: mo bzhi la thim par bsam pa 'ju 'dul gyi
NK019(dza)007:3031: dgongs pa'o // de nas dkyil 'khor la bkod pa'i mar me rnams sbar te /
NK019(dza)007:3033: pho brang dbus kyi mar me bcom ldan 'das che mchog /
NK019(dza)007:3036: phyogs mtshams kyi mar me rgyud lung gi he ru ka yab yum /
NK019(dza)007:3037: glo 'bur dang gru chad kyi gnas ma /
NK019(dza)007:3038: khyams dgu la dang po nas bzung ste rim par /
NK019(dza)007:3039: yul ma brgyad dang sgo skyong bzhi /
NK019(dza)007:3040: spor ma brgyad dang gsang yum bzhi /
NK019(dza)007:3044: khro bo khro mo ya drug cu /
NK019(dza)007:3045: pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu /
NK019(dza)007:3047: rgyu'i rta babs kyi phyi rol khor yug zlum po
NK019(dza)007:3048: la rig 'dzin bla ma rnams dwangs pa'i mtsho la
NK019(dza)007:3049: gza' skar shar ba ltar ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su
NK019(dza)007:3050: bkra lam mer gsal bar gyur /
NK019(dza)007:3051: ma h+aa sh+au nya t+aa sogs lngas dbang bskur /
NK019(dza)007:3052: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya sogs gsum gyis byin gyis brlab /
NK019(dza)007:3053: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahru lu ru lu h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3055: dzahh+aum bam hoh e h+ye hi ru lu ru lu
NK019(dza)007:3056: h+aum b+h+yohdzahdzah zhes pas ye shes pa nam mkha' 'gengs
NK019(dza)007:3058: dzahh+aum bam hohbadz+ra sa ma ya mu dra a /
NK019(dza)007:3059: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka tish+tha sa ma ya lhan /
NK019(dza)007:3060: zhes pas pho brang gi mar me lhar gsal ba
NK019(dza)007:3061: la gnyis med du bstim nas brtan par bzhugs su
NK019(dza)007:3062: gsol lo // de yan chad ni gang las spyan drang pa'i gzhi sgrub pa'o //
NK019(dza)007:3063: de nas so so'i dngos grub blang ba'i las rim la /
NK019(dza)007:3064: spyan drangs mchod dang bzlas pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:3065: bstod dang smon lam bsdu ba drug /
NK019(dza)007:3066: ces re re la don drug drug gi sgo nas blang ste /
NK019(dza)007:3067: dang po gtso bo gsum la blang ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3068: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK019(dza)007:3069: a kra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum ka ta ma h+aa kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum phata /
NK019(dza)007:3070: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sh+r+ai he ru ka h+aum
NK019(dza)007:3071: sarba ta th+aa ga ta kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum
NK019(dza)007:3072: / badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3073: badz+ra am ku sha dzah ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3074: zhes dkyil 'khor dbus kyi mar me las dpal 'bar gyis blangs te gsal shing dang po sbar bas /
NK019(dza)007:3075: pho brang dbus kyi dpal chen po che mchog he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:3077: badz+ra he ru ka gsum yab yum 'od dang sprul
NK019(dza)007:3078: par bcas te gsal shing gi rtse mor byon par
NK019(dza)007:3079: gyur pa la / ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK019(dza)007:3081: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK019(dza)007:3082: zhes sman gtor rak+tasa mchod nas /
NK019(dza)007:3084: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum dang //
NK019(dza)007:3085: dbang mchog he ru ka yab yum dang //
NK019(dza)007:3087: gtso bo rnam gsum thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3088: zur brgyad dkyil nas 'bru brgyad shar //
NK019(dza)007:3089: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK019(dza)007:3091: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs dam bskang //
NK019(dza)007:3092: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:3093: gtso bo gsum gyi sngags la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3094: gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa su kha h+aum h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3097: bcom ldan che mchog he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:3098: bla med yum chen khro mo'i rgyal //
NK019(dza)007:3100: nyi shu rtsa gcig sa rnams non //
NK019(dza)007:3101: bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis mngon sangs rgyas //
NK019(dza)007:3102: zhabs brgyad ting 'dzin dbyings su sbyor //
NK019(dza)007:3103: rgyan rnams ma lus sku la rdzogs //
NK019(dza)007:3104: khro rgyal sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3105: bcom ldan dbang mchog he ru ka /
NK019(dza)007:3106: dbu dgu phyag ni bco brgyad de //
NK019(dza)007:3107: stong pa bco brgyad yongs su rdzogs //
NK019(dza)007:3108: mthing nag dgyes pa chen po'i sku //
NK019(dza)007:3109: zhabs bzhis ru dra pho mo mnan //
NK019(dza)007:3111: rdo rje rigs mchog bdud 'dul gtso //
NK019(dza)007:3112: gdug pa 'dul ba thabs chen pos //
NK019(dza)007:3113: bdud rigs rdul du rlog mdzad pa //
NK019(dza)007:3114: dpal chen yab yum sku la bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3117: gsol byang gi smon lam ni /
NK019(dza)007:3118: hoh bcom ldan 'das che mchog he ru ka dang //
NK019(dza)007:3120: badz+ra he ru ka rnams yum dang bcas pa la dngos grub tu gsol ba'i mdo ni /
NK019(dza)007:3121: bdag cag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir tshogs pa rnams la /
NK019(dza)007:3122: shes bya thams cad la thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK019(dza)007:3128: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po'i sku gsung thugs kyi
NK019(dza)007:3129: bla man chad nas dngos grub kyi skal ba dang
NK019(dza)007:3130: rigs rgyud gang lags pa thams cad phyi mar sdad
NK019(dza)007:3131: mi 'tshal bar dus da lta nyid du thob par
NK019(dza)007:3134: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah zhes lan gsum gyis /
NK019(dza)007:3137: gsum pas sku 'od du zhu nas rang la thim
NK019(dza)007:3138: pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi
NK019(dza)007:3139: byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK019(dza)007:3140: gnyis pa rgyud kyi he ru ka bzhi ni /
NK019(dza)007:3142: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3147: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahru lu zhes phyogs rtsibs kyi mar me las gsal shing gnyis pa sbar bas /
NK019(dza)007:3148: rigs bzhi'i he ru ka yab yum 'od dang sprul par bcas te gsal shing gi rtse mor byon /
NK019(dza)007:3150: rigs bzhi khrag 'thung thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3151: zur brgyad dkyil na 'bru brgyad shar //
NK019(dza)007:3152: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK019(dza)007:3154: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs dam bskang //
NK019(dza)007:3155: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:3156: rigs bzhi'i sngags la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3159: 'jigs byed 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba //
NK019(dza)007:3160: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus las mi 'da' ba'i //
NK019(dza)007:3161: dpal chen khrag 'thung chen po rnam pa bzhi //
NK019(dza)007:3162: rang rang btsun mor bcas la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3163: hoh bcom ldan 'das rigs bzhi he ru ka yab yum la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3164: bdag cag gsang ba'i sogs sbyar ro //
NK019(dza)007:3165: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzah gsum gyis /
NK019(dza)007:3168: gsum pas sku 'od du zhu nas rang la thim pas gzi byin dang ldan par gyur /
NK019(dza)007:3169: gsum pa lung gi he ru ka bzhi ni /
NK019(dza)007:3171: rak+sha sh+r+ai he ru ka rak+sha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3176: badz+ra am ku sha dzahru lu mtshams rtsibs kyi mar me las gsal shing gsum pa sbar bas /
NK019(dza)007:3177: lung gi he ru ka bzhi 'od dang sprul par bcas te gsal shing gi rtse mor byon /
NK019(dza)007:3179: lung gi khrag 'thung thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3180: zur brgyad dkyil na 'bru brgyad shar //
NK019(dza)007:3181: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK019(dza)007:3183: phar 'phros dpal chen thugs dam bskang //
NK019(dza)007:3184: tshur 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:3185: lung gi khro bo bzhi'i sngags la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3188: sbyor ba dam tshig gsang ba sgrol ba'i dbyings //
NK019(dza)007:3189: log lta myong byed skye gnas reg bya 'joms //
NK019(dza)007:3190: ga na nyams pa ta na mtshan ma sgrol //
NK019(dza)007:3191: lung gi khro rgyal yab yum bzhi la bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3192: hoh bcom ldan 'das lung gi he ru ka yab yum la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3193: bdag cag gsang ba'i sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3194: badz+ra am ku sha dzah gsum gyis /
NK019(dza)007:3197: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3198: bzhi pa gnas ma brgyad ni /
NK019(dza)007:3208: badz+ra am ku ru lu glo 'bur dang gru chad
NK019(dza)007:3209: kyi mar me las gsal shing bzhi pa sbar bas
NK019(dza)007:3210: / gnas kyi ma mo brgyad 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3212: gnas ma brgyad kyi thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3213: snying po ru lu gu h+ya phar 'phros tshur 'dus sngags brgyad la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3216: goo r+ai la sogs khro mo chen mo brgyad //
NK019(dza)007:3217: gdug pa thabs kyis 'dul ba'i drag shul can //
NK019(dza)007:3218: sku mdog phyag rgya sna tshogs cir yang ston //
NK019(dza)007:3219: ye shes khro mo brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3220: hoh khro mo brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3224: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3225: lnga pa phra men brgyad sgo ma dang bcas pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:3236: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzah a mu khe h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3238: b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hoh am ku sha dang /
NK019(dza)007:3239: ru lu khyams dang po sgo dang bcas pa'i mar me las gsal shing lnga pa sbar bas /
NK019(dza)007:3240: yul ma brgyad dang gdong mo bzhi 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3242: phra men brgyad kyi thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3243: snying po ru lu gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na phar 'phros
NK019(dza)007:3244: dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la rang sngags bcu gnyis
NK019(dza)007:3245: la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3248: ye shes las la 'gyed pa'i phra men ma //
NK019(dza)007:3249: rnam 'phrul thabs kyi 'gro ba 'dul mdzad pa //
NK019(dza)007:3250: seng gdong la sogs phra men brgyad rnams dang //
NK019(dza)007:3251: sgo skyong gdong mo bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3252: hoh rdo rje phra men ma'i tshogs la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3256: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3257: drug pa 'bar ma gsang yum dang bcas pa ni /
NK019(dza)007:3259: badz+ra a pra ti ha +aar+ya ni tsatu ra ta ra phata rak+mo h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3260: sh+r+ai badz+ra mung+ga ra mu kha shwa ra y+aa ya na mah de bzhin du /
NK019(dza)007:3261: ra ga ma shwa ra y+aa ya /
NK019(dza)007:3262: kha t+w+aam k+aa pra dz+wa la y+aa ya /
NK019(dza)007:3263: g+han+de pra dz+wa la y+aa ya /
NK019(dza)007:3264: am ku sha ru lu khyams gnyis pa sgo dang
NK019(dza)007:3265: bcas mar me las gsal shing drug pa sbar bas
NK019(dza)007:3266: / 'bar ma brgyad dang gsang yum bzhi 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3268: 'bar ma gsang yum thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3269: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar
NK019(dza)007:3270: 'phros dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la so so'i sngags
NK019(dza)007:3271: la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3274: chos dbyings rnam dag ngang las rang snang ba //
NK019(dza)007:3275: sna tshogs cir yang 'gyur ba'i skur ston ma //
NK019(dza)007:3276: spor ma chen mo brgyad dang gsang ba yi //
NK019(dza)007:3277: dgyes bskyed yum chen bzhi la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3278: hoh 'bar ma brgyad dang gsang yum bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3282: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3283: bdun pa dbang mo nyer brgyad ni /
NK019(dza)007:3302: ma h+aa m+aa ra na badz+ra /
NK019(dza)007:3312: de thams cad kyi mthar b+h+yo re sbyar /
NK019(dza)007:3313: ung+ku sha ru lu khyams gsum pa sgo dang bcas
NK019(dza)007:3314: pa'i mar me las gsal shing bdun pa sbar bas
NK019(dza)007:3315: / dbang mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3317: dbang phyug nyer brgyad thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3318: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar
NK019(dza)007:3319: 'phros dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la so so'i sngags
NK019(dza)007:3320: la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3323: mi yi srin mo la sogs nyi shu brgyad //
NK019(dza)007:3324: dregs pa lha chen rnams kyi chung ma ste //
NK019(dza)007:3325: dbang drag las la thogs pa med par spyod //
NK019(dza)007:3326: dbang mo nyi shu brgyad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3327: hoh dbang mo nyer brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3330: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3331: brgyad pa mkha' 'gro so gnyis ni /
NK019(dza)007:3334: ang+ku sha ru lu khyams bzhi pa sgo dang bcas
NK019(dza)007:3335: pa'i mar me las gsal shing brgyad pa spar bas
NK019(dza)007:3336: / mkha' 'gro sum cu so gnyis 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3338: mkha' 'gro so gnyis thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3339: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar
NK019(dza)007:3340: 'phros dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la e +aa ra
NK019(dza)007:3341: li h+aum la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3344: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK019(dza)007:3345: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK019(dza)007:3346: ma sring byams pa'i tshul gyis grogs mdzad ma //
NK019(dza)007:3347: mkha' 'gro sum cu gnyis la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3348: hoh mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3352: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3353: dgu pa ma bdun sring bzhi ni /
NK019(dza)007:3358: ru lu khyams lnga pa sgo dang bcas pa'i mar me las gsal shing dgu pa sbar bas /
NK019(dza)007:3359: ma bdun sring bzhi 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3361: ma bdun sring bzhi'i thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3362: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar
NK019(dza)007:3363: 'gros dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la sngags tshan gnyis
NK019(dza)007:3364: la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3367: 'jig rten dregs pa 'dul mdzad ma mo'i tshogs //
NK019(dza)007:3368: phyi 'khor bsrung zhing nang 'khor skyong mdzad ma //
NK019(dza)007:3369: dur khrod ma bdun las kyi sring mo bzhi //
NK019(dza)007:3370: bgegs 'dul ma sring tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3371: hoh ma bdun sring bzhi la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3375: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3376: bcu pa king chen bco brgyad ni /
NK019(dza)007:3378: king+ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu h+aum b+h+yo h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3379: a ng+ku sha ru lu khyams drug pa sgo dang
NK019(dza)007:3380: bcas pa'i mar me las gsal shing bcu pa sbar
NK019(dza)007:3381: bas / king+ka ra bco brgyad 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3383: king chen bco brgyad thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3384: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar
NK019(dza)007:3385: 'phros dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la rang sngags la
NK019(dza)007:3389: khams gsum sgrol bar byed pa'i ging bco brgyad //
NK019(dza)007:3390: srid gsum las la thogs med sgrol la brtson //
NK019(dza)007:3391: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu gtan nas brlag par byed //
NK019(dza)007:3392: king chen king lcam tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3393: hoh king chen po bco brgyad la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3397: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3398: bcu gcig pa steng gi pho nya drug cu ni /
NK019(dza)007:3401: ang+ku sha ru lu khyams bdun pa sgo dang bcas
NK019(dza)007:3402: pa'i mar me las gsal shing bcu gcig pa sbar
NK019(dza)007:3403: bas / steng gi pho nya khro bo khro mo
NK019(dza)007:3404: ya drug cu 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon
NK019(dza)007:3406: khro bo khro mo'i thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3407: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar
NK019(dza)007:3408: 'phros dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la rang sngags la
NK019(dza)007:3412: bcom ldan h+aum mdzad sa gsum brjid kyis gnon //
NK019(dza)007:3413: khams gsum 'dul mdzad ye shes lha yi lha //
NK019(dza)007:3414: 'jigs byed 'bar bas gdug pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms //
NK019(dza)007:3415: khro bo khro mo rnams la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3416: hoh steng gi pho nya khro tshogs drug cu la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3420: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3421: bcu gnyis pa phyogs bzhi las kyi pho nya drug cu phrag bzhi ni /
NK019(dza)007:3423: b+ha na b+ha na ang+ku sha dzah ha la ha la p+aa sha h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3425: pa tsa pa tsa g+han+de hoh ang+ku sha ru lu
NK019(dza)007:3426: khyams brgyad pa'i mar me las gsal shing bcu gnyis
NK019(dza)007:3427: pa sbar bas / phyogs kyi pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3429: phyogs bzhi pho nya'i thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3430: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar
NK019(dza)007:3431: 'phros dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la sngags tshan bzhi
NK019(dza)007:3432: la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3435: ye shes thugs rjes phyogs kun khyab pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:3436: gdon bgegs 'dul ba'i phrin las thogs pa med //
NK019(dza)007:3437: ci bgyi'i bka' nyan las rnams myur sgrub pa'i //
NK019(dza)007:3438: phyogs bzhi'i pho nya'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3439: hoh phyogs kyi pho nya nyis brgya bzhi bcu la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3443: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3444: bcu gsum pa 'og gi pho nya drug cu ni /
NK019(dza)007:3447: ang+ku sha ru lu khyams dgu pa'i mar me las gsal shing bcu gsum pa spar bas /
NK019(dza)007:3448: 'og gi pho nya ma mo drug cu 'od dang sprul par bcas te byon /
NK019(dza)007:3450: ma mo drug cu'i thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3451: snying po ru lu 'bru gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i phar
NK019(dza)007:3452: 'phros dpal chen tshur 'dus bdag la rang sngags la
NK019(dza)007:3456: stong khams yongs kyi las la dbang byed pa'i //
NK019(dza)007:3457: ma chen rgyal mo srid pa gsum gyi bdag yum chen las la dbang ba'i dbang mo che //
NK019(dza)007:3458: ma mo drug cu'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3459: hoh 'og gi pho nya ma mo drug cu la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni sogs so //
NK019(dza)007:3463: sku 'od du zhu ste rang la bstim mo //
NK019(dza)007:3464: bcu bzhi pa rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi bla ma thams cad la blang ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3466: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram g+ai li h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3467: badz+ra yo gi gu ru sa ma ya dzah zhes
NK019(dza)007:3468: phyi'i khor yug gi mar me las gsal shing bcu
NK019(dza)007:3470: dus gsum gyi rig 'dzin bla ma bye ba sa
NK019(dza)007:3471: ya'i tshogs rnams 'od dang sprul par bcas te gsal
NK019(dza)007:3473: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta /
NK019(dza)007:3475: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa his sman gtor rak+ta phul //
NK019(dza)007:3476: rgyud lung man ngag 'chang ba yi //
NK019(dza)007:3477: rig 'dzin bla ma'i thugs ka nas //
NK019(dza)007:3478: snying po ru lu 'bru brgyad dang //
NK019(dza)007:3480: phar 'phros mchod pas thugs dam bskang //
NK019(dza)007:3481: tshar 'dus bdag la dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:3482: rang sngags la ru lu sbrel ba dang /
NK019(dza)007:3485: rig 'dzin bla ma byin rlabs ldan pa'i tshogs //
NK019(dza)007:3486: rnal 'byor lnga yi sa la rab bzhugs pa'i //
NK019(dza)007:3487: rgya bod rig 'dzin grub thob tshogs la bstod //
NK019(dza)007:3488: bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi dngos grub 'dir stsol cig /
NK019(dza)007:3489: hoh rig 'dzig rtsal 'chang rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma'i
NK019(dza)007:3490: tshogs la dngos grub tu gsol ba ni zhes sogs
NK019(dza)007:3491: so // badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahgasuma gyis /
NK019(dza)007:3494: gsum pas sku 'od du zhu ste rang la thim
NK019(dza)007:3495: pas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi gzi
NK019(dza)007:3496: byin dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK019(dza)007:3497: de yan chad lha las dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK019(dza)007:3498: de nas rdzas las blang ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3500: me tog gtor dang bdud rtsi yi //
NK019(dza)007:3501: dngos grub blang ba tshul bzhin bya //
NK019(dza)007:3502: bkra shis zas tshe'i dngos grub ni //
NK019(dza)007:3503: zla gam dbang gi gzhal yas nas //
NK019(dza)007:3504: bkra shis brjod dang cha lngar bgo //
NK019(dza)007:3505: ru lu'i brjod pa ma lus bya //
NK019(dza)007:3507: dang po bdud rtsi sman gyi dngos grub blang ste /
NK019(dza)007:3508: ru lu dang gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na cung zad bzlas nas /
NK019(dza)007:3509: hoh bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam
NK019(dza)007:3510: dral rnams kyis bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi'i sgo nas
NK019(dza)007:3511: bzlas brjod gyi mchod pa 'bul zhing mchi na /
NK019(dza)007:3512: thugs rje chen pos dgongs shing bzhes nas bdag cag
NK019(dza)007:3513: la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thams cad dus
NK019(dza)007:3514: da lta nyid du thob par stsal du gsol /
NK019(dza)007:3515: zhes dkyil 'khor la 'dud cing me tog dor nas /
NK019(dza)007:3516: lding khri bar ma'i dbus kyi sman gyi gsang bum
NK019(dza)007:3517: spyan drangs la slob dpon gyi spyi bor blangs te
NK019(dza)007:3518: / bdag nyid rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du gsal
NK019(dza)007:3519: ba la bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor gnyis med du thim
NK019(dza)007:3520: / par bsam zhing / ru lu dang gu h+ya dz+ny+aa na'i mthar /
NK019(dza)007:3521: a mri ta k+aa ya w+aaka tsit+ta sid+d+hi pha la
NK019(dza)007:3522: hoh zhes rang nyid kyis dngos grub blangs rjes slob
NK019(dza)007:3523: ma rnams la'ang rim par bskur ro //
NK019(dza)007:3524: sman gyi mdun gyi mar me blangs te /
NK019(dza)007:3525: hoh 'dus pa chen po'i lha tshogs rnams kyi mi gnas pa'i ye shes dang /
NK019(dza)007:3526: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK019(dza)007:3527: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK019(dza)007:3528: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK019(dza)007:3529: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK019(dza)007:3530: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang /
NK019(dza)007:3531: klong du gyur pa'i ye shes dang /
NK019(dza)007:3532: dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes dang /
NK019(dza)007:3533: 'da' dka' thugs kyi ye shes te /
NK019(dza)007:3534: thugs ye shes dgu nang nas 'char ba'i dngos grub bdag cag rnams kyis thob bo //
NK019(dza)007:3535: a la la hoh zhes kun gyi lag tu 'grim zhing snying gar zhun mar byug go //
NK019(dza)007:3536: tshe ril dang tshe'i dza gad bteg la //
NK019(dza)007:3537: +aa yuhdamara po rdo rje dbang gi tshe //
NK019(dza)007:3538: gzhan gyis mi 'phrog khams gsum kun las rgyal //
NK019(dza)007:3539: rang gi byang sems gdod nas skye shi med //
NK019(dza)007:3540: mi 'gyur tshe yi dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK019(dza)007:3541: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa gu h+ya +aa yu r+dz+ny+aa na bin+d+h+au b+h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3542: badz+ra +aa yu she dz+ny+aa na swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK019(dza)007:3543: zhes pas tshe ril g.yas dang chang g.yon bskor gyis
NK019(dza)007:3544: brim zhing tshe mdud byas pas tshe'i dngos grub thob
NK019(dza)007:3547: dbang dngos grub tu gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3548: skye med kyi ye shes su gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3549: 'chi med kyi bdud rtsir gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3550: mi 'gyur ba g.yung drung du gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3551: mi shigs pa rdo rjer gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3552: mi nub pa rgyal mtshan du gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3553: tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3555: bkra shis kyi rdzas gsal shing gi zla gam dang /
NK019(dza)007:3558: h+r+aih zla gam zhal gyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK019(dza)007:3559: rang rig ye shes mngon snang ba'i //
NK019(dza)007:3560: 'dod yon gsang ba'i longs spyod rgyan //
NK019(dza)007:3561: yongs su rdzogs pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:3563: gsol byang gi thod pa blangs la /
NK019(dza)007:3564: ltar dkar la 'tsher ba yab kyi dbang //
NK019(dza)007:3565: +aahltara dmar la dwangs pa yum gyi mkha' //
NK019(dza)007:3566: h+aum ltar smug la 'dril ba byang chub sems //
NK019(dza)007:3567: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK019(dza)007:3569: w+aa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3570: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK019(dza)007:3572: de nas 'dus pa thams cad la dngos grub kyi
NK019(dza)007:3573: rdzas gsal shing gi 'brang rgyas sogs bza' bca' rnams
NK019(dza)007:3574: g.yas dang / btung ba'i bye brag rnams g.yon bskor du drang zhing /
NK019(dza)007:3575: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'ang stob la rol bar bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:3577: hoh bdag cag dpon slob mched dang lcam dral rnams kyi /
NK019(dza)007:3578: rdo rje'i tshe gsol bas tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa'i skal ba dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3579: ma h+aa m+aam sa gsol bas rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po thob par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3580: dza gad dpa' bo gsol bas 'gro ba mang po dbang du 'du bar gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3581: zla rgyas gsol bas tshogs gnyis yongs su rdzogs par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3582: gal phyis gsol bas bsam pa thams cad lhun gyis grub par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3583: zla khrom gsol bas chos nyid zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3584: 'jam des gsol bas byams snying rje byang chub kyi sems dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3585: zhal zas kha ba dang mngar ba dang skyur ba
NK019(dza)007:3586: sogs ro rnam pa sna tshogs gsol bas zhi khro
NK019(dza)007:3587: sprul pa'i tshogs la mnga' brnyes par gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3589: de yan chad rdzas las dngos grub blang ba'o //
NK019(dza)007:3590: sgrub chen gyi 'gangs che shos dngos grub chen po
NK019(dza)007:3591: yum gyi mkha' las blang ba ni zab mo'i mchog
NK019(dza)007:3592: dbang dang sbrel nas mdzad do //
NK019(dza)007:3593: cho ga'i mjug sdud la gsum las /
NK019(dza)007:3594: shis pa brjod pas dngos grub brtan par bya ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3595: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed de //
NK019(dza)007:3596: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:3597: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub dam pa rnams //
NK019(dza)007:3598: bdag la stsal zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK019(dza)007:3599: k+aa ya w+aaka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK019(dza)007:3600: zhes rten 'brel snying pos basngagasa pa'i me tog gi char dbab cing rol mo'i sgra yang bya'o //
NK019(dza)007:3601: dngos grub kyi rdzas lhag cha lngar bgo ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3602: yi dam lha'i skal ba bla ma /
NK019(dza)007:3603: dkyil 'khor lha'i skal ba rgyal theb /
NK019(dza)007:3604: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi skal ba las can gyi slob ma gcig la dang /
NK019(dza)007:3605: de lhag cha gnyis su byas pa'i gcig mched gzhan rnams la rig pas spyad de byin zhing /
NK019(dza)007:3606: cha gcig po sbyin sreg dang gter gyi rdzas su bdogs la bzhag go //
NK019(dza)007:3608: ru glan dbang gi rjes la mdzad /
NK019(dza)007:3609: bla ma rtsi lung pa 'dir mdzad /
NK019(dza)007:3610: ces 'gos kyi las thor 'byung ba las /
NK019(dza)007:3611: rtsa ba'i las tho'i dgongs pa ltar na skabs 'dir bya ba 'thad par sems so //
NK019(dza)007:3612: de dag ni sgrub pa chen po'i yan lag ste /
NK019(dza)007:3613: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung bsrang ba tshar ro //
NK019(dza)007:3614: da ni rjes kyi cho ga la don brgyad las /
NK019(dza)007:3615: dang po mar me smon lam ni /
NK019(dza)007:3616: dpon slob thams cad lag bsnol bas srin lag sbrel te /
NK019(dza)007:3617: g.yon pas mar me bzung la //
NK019(dza)007:3618: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK019(dza)007:3619: snying po byang chub lam la zhugs pa yis //
NK019(dza)007:3620: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen por mi ltung zhing //
NK019(dza)007:3621: chags sdang gcong rong gnas su mi skye dang //
NK019(dza)007:3622: log lta dmyal ba'i zangs khar rbab mi 'dril //
NK019(dza)007:3623: 'khon 'dzin gcan gzan gdug pa'i skad mi thos //
NK019(dza)007:3624: nyon mongs mtshon rtse gdung pa'i zer mi phog /
NK019(dza)007:3625: dge ba'i bshes gnyen bka' drin che ba dang //
NK019(dza)007:3626: srog gis sbrel ba'i mched dang lcam dral dang //
NK019(dza)007:3627: gsum pa'i dbang gis sbrel ba'i rig ma gsum //
NK019(dza)007:3628: skye ba 'di dang tshe rabs thams cad du //
NK019(dza)007:3629: mi 'bral rtse gcig 'grogs pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK019(dza)007:3630: sa bcu khyad par rim gyis bgrod par shog /
NK019(dza)007:3631: nam zhig tshe 'phos lus barje'i dus byung nas //
NK019(dza)007:3632: 'khor ba'i g.yang sar lan gcig lhungs srid kyang //
NK019(dza)007:3633: snang ba'i go 'byed zhun mar mdangs gsal 'dis //
NK019(dza)007:3634: rig 'dzin sgrub pa po yi shul mtshon cing //
NK019(dza)007:3635: kun tu 'od kyi sa la rgyud sbyangs nas //
NK019(dza)007:3636: pad+ma chen po'i sa la lhun gyis grub //
NK019(dza)007:3637: 'khor lo tshogs chen sa la gshegs pa'i tshe //
NK019(dza)007:3638: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis mdun bsus shig /
NK019(dza)007:3639: yi dam lha yis rgyab nas srog brten cig /
NK019(dza)007:3640: byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis mtha' skyor cig /
NK019(dza)007:3641: mchod pa'i lha mo rnams kyis sna drongs shig /
NK019(dza)007:3642: ma tshogs dbang mo rnams kyis rjes skyongs shig /
NK019(dza)007:3643: lcang lo can gyi sa la phyin pa'i tshe //
NK019(dza)007:3644: mi ldog pa yi sa la gnas nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:3645: rdo rje khro rgyal khyod kyi zhal mthong nas //
NK019(dza)007:3646: rig 'dzin rnams dang dbyer med gyur nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:3647: bla med sku gsung thugs su grub par shog /
NK019(dza)007:3648: gnyis pa yon stob cing gnyer blang ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3649: bka' drin bsab phyir slob bu rnams kyis rang gi
NK019(dza)007:3650: yid du sdug cing gces pa'i dngos po ci 'byor
NK019(dza)007:3652: ma 'byor na yid kyi lus longs spyod thams cad phul bar mos la man+dala dbul du gzhug /
NK019(dza)007:3653: de nas ru'i zhabs bu'i spyi bor bzhag la /
NK019(dza)007:3654: de ring phan chad bu khyod kyi //
NK019(dza)007:3655: rdo rje sems dpa' nga yin gyis //
NK019(dza)007:3656: nga yis ji ltar bsgo ba bzhin //
NK019(dza)007:3657: bu khyod kyis ni bya dgos so //
NK019(dza)007:3659: bla ma rdo rje rgyal po la //
NK019(dza)007:3660: dad mos gus pa'i sems ldan pas //
NK019(dza)007:3661: bka' yi ji ltar bsgo ba bzhin //
NK019(dza)007:3662: lus ngag yid gsum gnyer gyis blang //
NK019(dza)007:3664: gsum pa gton ma bgo zhing sbyin sreg bya ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3666: gtor ma la sogs rdzas rnams ni //
NK019(dza)007:3667: cha gsum dag tu bgos nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:3668: gcig gis sbyin sreg las chog bya //
NK019(dza)007:3669: gcig ni rnal 'byor longs spyod gter //
NK019(dza)007:3671: zhes pas 'das gtor rnams dkyil 'khor nas phyir bsnur
NK019(dza)007:3672: la cha gsum du bgos pa'i dang po de dngos
NK019(dza)007:3673: grub kyi rdzas lhag cung zad dang bsres nas sbyin
NK019(dza)007:3674: sreg gi sreg rdzas su dbul /
NK019(dza)007:3676: las bzhi gang mos bya bar gsungs kyang /
NK019(dza)007:3677: 'dir bsnyen sgrub kyi kha bskang ba'i don du zhi ba'i sbyin sreg mdzad pa phyag len no //
NK019(dza)007:3678: bzhi pa gter sba ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3679: gtor ma cha bar pa de dngos grub kyi rdzas lhag dang mnyam du bum par blugs /
NK019(dza)007:3680: dkyil 'khor khang pa'i 'og tu dong zla gam dmar
NK019(dza)007:3681: pos sgyur ba sman raka gis chag chag btab pa'i
NK019(dza)007:3683: de nyid b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gur khang longs
NK019(dza)007:3684: spyod zad mi shes pa'i gter du gyur par mos
NK019(dza)007:3686: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK019(dza)007:3687: khrag 'thung rigs lnga'i gter sbed do //
NK019(dza)007:3688: bdud rtsi lnga yi gter sbas pas //
NK019(dza)007:3689: he ru ka yis mdun bsus nas //
NK019(dza)007:3690: ye shes lnga yi don rtogs shog /
NK019(dza)007:3691: ye shes lnga yis rgyas gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:3692: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK019(dza)007:3693: dbyings phyug lnga yis gter sbed do //
NK019(dza)007:3694: sha khrag rus pa'i gter sbas pas //
NK019(dza)007:3695: yum chen lnga yis mdun bsus nas //
NK019(dza)007:3696: gsang ba'i mdzod dang 'phrad par shog /
NK019(dza)007:3697: skye med dbyings kyi rgyas gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:3698: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK019(dza)007:3699: khro mo brgyad kyis gter sbed do //
NK019(dza)007:3700: rnam shes brgyad kyi gter sbas pas //
NK019(dza)007:3701: ma mo brgyad kyis mdun bsus nas //
NK019(dza)007:3702: gsang ba'i rdzas dang 'phrad par shog /
NK019(dza)007:3703: rig pa ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:3704: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK019(dza)007:3705: phra men brgyad kyis gter sbed do //
NK019(dza)007:3706: gsang ba'i dam rdzas gter sbas pas //
NK019(dza)007:3707: mgo brnyan rnams kyis mdun bsus nas //
NK019(dza)007:3709: rig pa ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:3710: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK019(dza)007:3711: sgo ma bzhi yis gter sbed do //
NK019(dza)007:3712: rnam thar bzhi yi gter sbas pas //
NK019(dza)007:3713: khro mo bzhi yis mdun bsus nas //
NK019(dza)007:3714: bdud bzhi'i 'jigs las thar bar shog /
NK019(dza)007:3715: rig pa ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:3716: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK019(dza)007:3717: dbang phyug ma yis gter sbed do //
NK019(dza)007:3718: dam rdzas bdud rtsi'i gter sbas pas //
NK019(dza)007:3719: dam can rnams kyis mdun bsus nas //
NK019(dza)007:3720: bdud rtsi'i zas dang 'phrad par shog /
NK019(dza)007:3721: rig pa ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:3722: sa yi lha mo'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK019(dza)007:3723: khro bo bcu yis gter sbed do //
NK019(dza)007:3724: dam rdzas rus pa'i gter sbas pas //
NK019(dza)007:3725: khrag 'thung rnams kyis mdun bsus nas //
NK019(dza)007:3726: rdo rje'i gral dang 'phrad par shog /
NK019(dza)007:3727: rig pa ye shes rgyas gdab bo //
NK019(dza)007:3728: rdo rje slob dpon mched lcam gyis //
NK019(dza)007:3729: dam rdzas gtor ma'i gter sbas pas //
NK019(dza)007:3730: zag med gter la longs spyod cing //
NK019(dza)007:3731: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor dngos grub rnams //
NK019(dza)007:3732: 'dod yon lnga yi longs spyod kyis //
NK019(dza)007:3735: lnga pa gtor ma btang zhing bro bya ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3736: gtor ma cha tha ma de chos skyong rnams kyi
NK019(dza)007:3737: gtor ma dang mnyam du gtor skyong gi cho gas
NK019(dza)007:3738: dbul la / lhag ma bsdus te /
NK019(dza)007:3740: phyags dar bcas snod du blugs cing /
NK019(dza)007:3741: sgrub pa'i dus kyi lhag gtor ske tshang du bsags pa rnams dang lhan cig tu khyer la /
NK019(dza)007:3742: las mkhan gyis dkyil 'khor khang pa nas gom pa
NK019(dza)007:3743: bdun cu'i sar lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor gtor ma dang
NK019(dza)007:3744: bcas pa bshams la lhag gtor cho ga rgyas par
NK019(dza)007:3745: bya zhing / bshal chus brtan ma bskyangs nas /
NK019(dza)007:3746: slar nang du 'ong ba'i tshe srung 'khor gsal btab
NK019(dza)007:3747: pa'i nang du rnal 'byor pa 'khor bcas kyi gnas
NK019(dza)007:3748: lus longs spyod thams cad tshud nas /
NK019(dza)007:3749: me'i ra ba'i 'od zer gyis rkyen ngan bar chad thams cad kyi bsrung ba chen por bsam mo //
NK019(dza)007:3750: de nas sgrub khang gi them pa'i phyi rol sngar
NK019(dza)007:3751: dam sri'i mnan pa byas pa'i steng du gtor gzhong
NK019(dza)007:3752: thams cad kha sbub pa'i mthar bror bcas nas las
NK019(dza)007:3754: de la sgrub pa po thams cad bro ra zlum
NK019(dza)007:3755: por bca' zhing lag g.yas steng du bsnol ba'i lu
NK019(dza)007:3756: gu rgyud kyis mdzub mo sbrel la /
NK019(dza)007:3758: bud+d+ha sh+r+ai he ru ka bud+d+ha kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3759: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK019(dza)007:3760: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor chu
NK019(dza)007:3761: shel gyi rang bzhin can dkar zhing zlum pa 'od
NK019(dza)007:3763: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad bud+d+ha rigs kyis
NK019(dza)007:3764: gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor sprul
NK019(dza)007:3765: pa'i 'od zer dkar po 'phro bas zhi ba'i phrin
NK019(dza)007:3768: gti mug rdo rje 'khor bcas kyi //
NK019(dza)007:3770: yud tsam gyis ni zhi mdzad pas //
NK019(dza)007:3771: zhi ba'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:3772: sum+b+ha ni sum+b+ha sogs h+aum bzhi pa'i sngags kyi mthar /
NK019(dza)007:3773: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i nad gdon
NK019(dza)007:3774: dgra bgegs sdig sgrib nyes ltung sogs nyes tshogs thams
NK019(dza)007:3775: cad sh+ain+tam ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK019(dza)007:3776: zhes bro brdung zhing phyag rgya sprugs te bshig go //
NK019(dza)007:3777: yang bro ra gru bzhir bca' zhing lag bsnol ba las gung mo sbrel la /
NK019(dza)007:3779: rat+na sh+r+ai he ru ka rat+na kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3780: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK019(dza)007:3781: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor ser
NK019(dza)007:3782: po gru bzhi pa 'od zer 'phro ba'i dbus su
NK019(dza)007:3783: / nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad rin chen
NK019(dza)007:3784: rigs kyis gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i lha
NK019(dza)007:3785: tshogs sprul pa'i 'od zer ser po 'phro bas rgyas
NK019(dza)007:3786: pa'i phrin las mdzad par gyur /
NK019(dza)007:3788: nga rgyal rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK019(dza)007:3790: dpal dang gzi brjid chen po rnams //
NK019(dza)007:3791: yud tsam gyis ni rgyas par mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:3793: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa'i tshe dpal
NK019(dza)007:3794: longs spyod 'phrul dang gzi brjid sogs legs tshogs yon
NK019(dza)007:3795: tan thams cad push+tim ku ru /
NK019(dza)007:3796: yang bro ra zla gam bca' zhing lag bsnol ba las srin lag sbrel la /
NK019(dza)007:3798: pad+ma sh+r+ai he ru ka pad+ma kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3799: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK019(dza)007:3800: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dbang gi dkyil 'khor dmar po zla gam 'od zer 'phro ba'i dbus su /
NK019(dza)007:3801: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad pad+ma rigs kyis
NK019(dza)007:3802: gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung 'bar ba'i lha tshogs sprul
NK019(dza)007:3803: pa'i 'od zer dmar po 'phro bas dbang gi phrin
NK019(dza)007:3808: thams cad dbang du bsdus nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:3809: dbang du ma gyur gang yang med //
NK019(dza)007:3811: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pas khams gsum
NK019(dza)007:3812: gyi che btsan dregs pa can thams cad w+aa sham
NK019(dza)007:3813: ku ru hoh yang bro ra gru gsum du bca'
NK019(dza)007:3814: zhing lag bsnol ba las mathe'u chung sbrel la /
NK019(dza)007:3816: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro d+he shwa r+ai h+aum /
NK019(dza)007:3817: h+aum ha he phata b+h+yo ram /
NK019(dza)007:3818: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten drag po'i dkyil 'khor gru
NK019(dza)007:3819: gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i me 'od 'phro ba'i dbus
NK019(dza)007:3820: su / nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad rdo
NK019(dza)007:3821: rje rigs kyis gtso byas pa'i khrag 'thung rngams pa'i
NK019(dza)007:3822: lha tshogs sprul pa'i 'od zer mthing nag 'phro bas
NK019(dza)007:3823: drag po'i phrin las mdzad par gyur /
NK019(dza)007:3825: zhe sdang rdo rje 'khor bcas kyis //
NK019(dza)007:3826: 'jig rten khams ni thal ba'i rdul du rlag nas kyang //
NK019(dza)007:3827: drag po'i las rnams sgrub par mdzod //
NK019(dza)007:3829: bdag cag dpon slob 'khor dang bcas pa la gnod
NK019(dza)007:3830: cing 'tshe ba'i dgra bgegs gdug pa can thams cad
NK019(dza)007:3832: ces bro brdung zhing phyag rgya sprugs pas las de dang de grub par bsam mo //
NK019(dza)007:3833: drug pa dkyil 'khor bsdu zhing mtshams dgrol ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3834: dkyil chog ltar rdul tshon gyi nyin snga ma rnams
NK019(dza)007:3835: dang ras bris la rnam pa thams cad du mchod
NK019(dza)007:3836: bstod bzod par gsol nas ye shes pa brtan bzhugs
NK019(dza)007:3837: bya / rdul tshon gyi nyin tha ma'i tshe ye
NK019(dza)007:3838: shes pa bteg nas mchod bstod bzod gsol byas nas
NK019(dza)007:3839: bya / gshegs su gsol / gar ltar yang sgrub
NK019(dza)007:3840: thabs ltar ting 'dzin dam tshig gi 'khor lo 'od
NK019(dza)007:3842: de las langs nas go bgo lus bsrung rnams byas te /
NK019(dza)007:3846: sgo byang phyi nang rnams kyi drung du gtang rag gi mchod gtor bshams pa /
NK019(dza)007:3847: sngar bzhin byin gyis brlabs nas phul la /
NK019(dza)007:3848: phyin chad kyang bar chad mi 'byung ba gsol ba gdab cing /
NK019(dza)007:3849: ya hi gats+tshasa gshegs su gsol /
NK019(dza)007:3850: de nas nang du zhugs nas dkyil chog ltar phur
NK019(dza)007:3851: bu dbyung ba dang mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor bsdu ba
NK019(dza)007:3852: rnams byas la rdul tshon chu bor gshegs gsol bya'o
NK019(dza)007:3853: // bdun pa bsngo shis bya ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3855: gnas su bkra shis la sogs kyi //
NK019(dza)007:3856: sgrub pa rdzogs par mthar dbyung ngo //
NK019(dza)007:3857: zhes pas dge ba bsngo zhing smon lam btab la
NK019(dza)007:3858: bkra shis dang dga' ston gyis mtha' rgyas par bya'o
NK019(dza)007:3859: // brgyad pa gnas bsrung ba ni /
NK019(dza)007:3860: sgrub pa po rnams zhag gcig phyi rol du mi 'gro /
NK019(dza)007:3861: de nas kyang zhag gsum tsam gyi bar du thag
NK019(dza)007:3862: ring du mi 'gro zhing bla ma min pa gzhan
NK019(dza)007:3864: las gzhung tshar re bsrangs te gtor ma btang zhing mtshams khad kyis dgrol /
NK019(dza)007:3865: dus rtag tu spyod lam rgyun gyi rnal 'byor las mi 'bral bar bya zhing /
NK019(dza)007:3866: bla ma dam pa la sangs rgyas kun 'dus kyi
NK019(dza)007:3867: 'du shes bzhag nas bsnyen bkur gyis mnyes pa sgrub
NK019(dza)007:3869: rgyud lung man ngag zab barlinga dpag dka' ba //
NK019(dza)007:3870: shes rab dabnga pos legs par dpyad pa las //
NK019(dza)007:3871: 'dus pa'i bsnyen sgrub chos don gsal byed pa //
NK019(dza)007:3872: rin chen 'od kyi snang ba'i dapala 'di shar //
NK019(dza)007:3873: dge 'dis gsang chen rdo rje theg pa yi //
NK019(dza)007:3874: bstan pa phyogs dus kun tu rgyas pa dang //
NK019(dza)007:3875: he ru ka dpal 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi //
NK019(dza)007:3876: dkyil 'khor gcig tu 'gro kun 'grub gyur cig /
NK019(dza)007:3877: 'dus pa mdo'i dbang rgyud dang man ngag gi lugs
NK019(dza)007:3878: gcig tu dril nas bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi dang
NK019(dza)007:3879: 'brel bar bskur ba'i sgrub khog gi chings rin chen
NK019(dza)007:3880: 'od kyi snang ba zhes bya ba 'di yang skyes
NK019(dza)007:3881: bu dam pa du ma'i gsung gis bskul ba'i ngor
NK019(dza)007:3882: / rgyal kun spyi gzugs gter chen chos kyi rgyal
NK019(dza)007:3883: po'i bka' drin gyis 'tsho ba'i gnyos btsun rmongs pa
NK019(dza)007:3884: d+harma sh+r+ais rang lo nga gnyis pa shing mo bya
NK019(dza)007:3885: lo chu stod zla ba'i dkar phyogs kyi rgyal ba
NK019(dza)007:3886: dang po'i tshes la gangs ri'i khrod kyi pad+ma 'od
NK019(dza)007:3887: o rgyan smin grol gling gi chos grwar grub par
